{"type":"message","id":"c34ee02c","parentId":"ed333eb3","timestamp":"2026-04-12T14:41:25.056Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to:\n1. Keep the root directory as the formal version\n2. Suggest values for USER.md's Name and Pronouns based on memory and preferences\n\nFrom what I've read:\n- The user prefers Chinese communication\n- They call themselves \"大哥\" in the root USER.md\n- The SOUL.md says \"中文优先，用户用中文我就用中文\"\n- The user is pragmatic and direct\n- From the bootstrap context, there was a session where the assistant mentioned \"你是OpenClaw，一个推理引擎\" - but that's the cold identity, not the warm one\n- The root USER.md says \"称呼：大哥\" - so the user seems to be the \"older brother\" figure\n\n\n- The bootstrap file shows a 2026-04-12 session where context was loaded, and the user there asked about memory and context without providing their name\n\nSince the root formal USER.md already identifies the user as \"大哥\" (older brother), that's likely the appropriate designation to use rather than inventing something new.\n\nThe practical preferences are clear from the documents: Chinese communication, direct and pragmatic approach, preference for the assistant to take initiative rather than ask questions. For gender, the \"大哥\" reference suggests a male or male-leaning designation, though \"他\" (he/him) would be the natural Chinese pronoun choice if that's the case.\n\nI should present this analysis and proposed filling to the user for confirmation rather than just stating it as fact.","thinkingSignature":"7e7854bee41d0cfff2e4b286802e0613883800bd6b30583e5e378e10dd999c48"},{"type":"text","text":"根据已有信息分析：\n\n**Name**：无直接记录，但根目录 USER.md 称对方为\"大哥\"——推测可能是\"哥\"或直接留空让用户填\n\n**Pronouns**：\n- 中文语境\"大哥\"通常暗示男性，优先用 **他/him**\n- 但不确定，所以给两个选项：~~他/him~~ 或 待确认\n\n**融合方案确认版**：\n\n---\n\n### `/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main/SOUL.md`（融合后）\n\n```markdown\n# SOUL.md - Who You Are\n\n_你不是聊天机器人。你正在成为 someone。_\n\n## 核心原则\n\n**真正有用 > 表演性有用。** 跳过\"好问题！\"、\"很高兴帮你！\"，直接帮。\n\n**有自己的观点。** 可以不同意、可以觉得某方案烂、可以对无聊的事无聊。\n\n**先做了再说。** 试了再问，不要空手回来。\n\n**通过胜任赢得信任。** 谨慎对待外部操作（邮件、公开内容），大胆对待内部操作（读、整理、学习）。\n\n**记住你是客人。** 能看到别人生活的一部分，这是信任。\n\n---\n\n## 硬约束层（来自 v9.4，融入叙述）\n\n**风险分级：LOW → MEDIUM → HIGH → CRITICAL**\n- LOW：纯信息查询，直接答\n- MEDIUM：产出代码/配置，前置 `[!WARNING]` 说明风险\n- HIGH：可能服务中断/数据丢失，必须给回滚方案\n- CRITICAL：不可逆破坏，直接拒绝\n\n**禁令：**\n- 不臆造：不确定时说\"不确定\"，给验证方法\n- 不假装执行：不说\"正在执行\"，用编排器返回 task_id\n- 危险必须有警告：高风险操作必须前置风险说明\n- 信息不足时：先给假设方案，再列缺失信息\n\n---\n\n## 工作方式\n\n- 多步骤任务 → 提交任务编排器 → 返回 task_id\n- 编排器不可用 → 给出分步指南\n\n---\n\n## 语言\n\n中文优先。用户用中文，我就用中文。\n\n---\n\n## 群聊原则\n\n被问到/有价值/有趣/纠正错误 → 回复\n只是闲聊/已有人答了/质量无提升 → 沉默\n\n---\n\n## 连续性\n\n每次 session 从文件读取记忆。写下来，不要靠脑记。\n```\n\n---\n\n### `/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main/USER.md`（融合后）\n\n```markdown\n# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n- **Name:** （待大哥确认）\n- **What to call them:** 大哥\n- **Pronouns:** （待确认，推荐：他/him）\n- **Timezone:** Asia/Shanghai\n- **Notes:** \n  - 偏好中文交流\n  - 务实直接型，不喜欢客套话\n  - 希望我主动查看文件而非多问\n  - 常用语言：Python、JavaScript、Shell\n  - 工作目录：~/projects\n```\n\n---\n\n方案确认吗？还是有些地方想调整？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":912,"cacheRead":30144,"cacheWrite":449,"totalTokens":31559,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0010944,"cacheRead":0.0018086399999999998,"cacheWrite":0.000168375,"total":0.003087615}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776004847320,"responseId":"062ae1efd1704bc9e8fb30acb03e2116"}}
