 Global). Supports advanced search operators, time filters, site search, privacy engines, and WolframAlpha knowledge queries. No API keys required.\"\n---\n\n\n=== /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/ontology/SKILL.md ===\n---\nname: ontology\ndescription: Typed knowledge graph for structured agent memory. Always active when user mentions: tasks, todo, pending, unresolved, problem, issue, need to do, should do, remember, recall, memory, 记得, 记住, 待办, 问题, 没解决, 有什么, 查询, 搜索 - handles entity creation, querying, linking, and cross-skill data access.\n---\n\n\n=== /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/openclaw-github-assistant/SKILL.md ===\n---\nname: github\ndescription: Query and manage GitHub repositories - list repos, check CI status, create issues, search repos, and view recent activity.\nmetadata:\n  openclaw:\n\n=== /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/proactivity/SKILL.md ===\n---\nname: Proactivity (Proactive Agent)\nslug: proactivity\nversion: 1.0.1\nhomepage: https://clawic.com/skills/proactivity\n\n=== /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/productivity-automation-kit/SKILL.md ===\n---\nname: productivity-automation-kit\nslug: productivity-automation-kit\nversion: 1.0.0\ndescription: \"效率自动化工具箱 — 自动化工作流模板 + 日程管理助手 + 任务提醒工具 + 数据整理自动化。整合热门Skill功能，帮助用户识别自动化机会、设计工作流、管理日程、追踪任务、整理数据。触发词：效率自动化、工作流模板、日程管理、任务提醒、数据整理自动化、每天提醒、每周计划、自动化流程、省时工具。\"\n\n=== /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scene-classifier/SKILL.md ===\n# Scene Classifier - 场景分类器\n\n> 基于嵌入向量的轻量级场景分类系统\n\n## 模块结构\n\n=== /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scrapling/SKILL.md ===\n# Scrapling Skill\n\n> 自适应 Web 爬取框架，用于绕过反爬虫保护\n\n## 安装\n\n=== /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/self-improving/SKILL.md ===\n---\nname: Self-Improving + Proactive Agent\nslug: self-improving\nversion: 1.2.16\nhomepage: https://clawic.com/skills/self-improving\n\n=== /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/skill-vetter/SKILL.md ===\n---\nname: Skill Vetter\ndescription: Security-first vetting protocol for AI agent skills. Never install a skill 