n't exist, (4) An external API or tool fails, (5) Claude realizes its knowledge is outdated or incorrect, (6) A better approach is discovered for a recurring task. Also review learnings before major tasks.\"\n\n=== /home/ai/.openclaw/skills/task_orchestrator/SKILL.md ===\n# Task Orchestrator 技能\n\n> 全自动任务编排：评分路由 + 上下文保护 + 子代理进度上报","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776005693190}}
