  \"enabled\": true\n  },\n  \"sceneClassifier\": {\n    \"url\": \"http://127.0.0.1:3104\",\n    \"enabled\": true\n  },\n  \"plugins\": {\n    \"openclaw-cc-bridge\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"model\": \"minimax-m2.5\",\n      \"allowedTools\": [\"Bash\", \"Read\", \"Edit\", \"Write\", \"Glob\", \"Grep\", \"WebFetch\", \"WebSearch\", \"Mildred\", \"Task*\"],\n      \"env\": {\n        \"ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL\": \"https://zhenze-huhehaote.cmecloud.cn/api/coding/v1\",\n        \"ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN\": \"J99ouXWKXO8Zg5tLqv92YVsPNFhwuZc-z6z2ioeg7VE\",\n        \"ANTHROPIC_MODEL\": \"minimax-m2.5\"\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"models\": {\n    \"providers\": {\n      \"ollama\": {\n        \"baseUrl\": \"http://172.23.96.1:11434\",\n        \"models\": [{\"id\": \"qwen2.5:14b\", \"name\": \"本地-qwen2.5-14b\"}]\n      },\n      \"deepseek\": {\n        \"apiKey\": \"sk-8e6102d12a394cd1822ee2503d54c137\",\n        \"baseUrl\": \"https://api.deepseek.com\",\n        \"models\": [{\"id\": \"deepseek-chat\", \"name\": \"云端-DeepSeek-Chat\"}]\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"commands\": {\"native\": \"auto\", \"nativeSkills\": \"auto\", \"restart\": true, \"ownerDisplay\": \"raw\"},\n  \"gateway\": {\"mode\": \"local\", \"auth\": {\"mode\": \"token\", \"token\": \"__OPENCLAW_REDACTED__\"}}\n}","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776005698711}}
{"type":"message","id":"69d3dfbb","parentId":"37b2dd51","timestamp":"2026-04-12T14:55:43.322Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a complete picture. Let me give a comprehensive skills review.\n\nKey findings:\n1. OpenClaw has a `plugins.openclaw-cc-bridge` enabled, which uses minimax-m2.5 model\n2. v8 scoring engine at 3103 is enabled\n3. sceneClassifier at 3104 is enabled\n4. No explicit skills.enabled list in the config - skills are loaded from skill directories\n\nLet me now summarize the skills in a clear categorization:\n\n**系统技能（OpenClaw 内置）**\n\n\n- `self-improvement` - catches failures and corrections to improve continuously\n- `coding-agent` - delegates coding tasks to Codex or Claude Code via background process\n- `gemini` - handles one-shot Q&A and summarization\n- `healthcheck` - audits security and configures risk tolerance for OpenClaw deployments\n- `node-connect` - diagnoses connection issues between OpenClaw nodes and pairing failures on companion apps\n- `session-logs` - searches and analyzes session logs using jq\n- `tmux` - controls tmux sessions remotely by sending keystrokes and scraping output\n- `weather` - retrieves current weather and forecasts\n- `feishu-doc`, `feishu-drive`, `feishu-perm`, `feishu-wiki` - manage Feishu document operations, cloud storage, permissions, and wiki navigation\n- `clawhub` - searches, installs, updates, and publishes agent skills from clawhub.com\n- `mcporter` - works with MCP servers and tools directly\n- `openai-whisper` - handles local speech-to-text using Whisper without an API key\n- `video-frames` - extracts frames or short clips from videos\n- `gh-issues` - fetches GitHub issues and spawns sub-agents to implement fixes and open PRs\n\nI'm also looking at workspace skills that appear to be more experimental or specific to the current setup.\n\nNow I'm reviewing the skills available in the workspace, which include agent orchestration for managing multi-agent teams, automation workflows, various Claude Code-related skills covering architecture and security, a critical interceptor for blocking dangerous operations, and an advanced long-term memory system. There are also skills for managing GitHub interactions, detecting intent, maintaining memory, searching across multiple engines, handling ontology, and deploying to Vercel.\n\nAdditionally, there's a scene classifier for categorizing scenes, a web scraping framework, a self-improvement loop, a skill vetting system for security reviews, a spec-driven development approach, and a task orchestrator for automated task management. I'm also noting that a couple of skills like clawdbot-filesystem and task-orchestrator-v7 seem to be duplicates of others already listed.\n\nLooking at the full picture, there are some genuine redundancies here—the v8 classifier and scorer skills appear to be superseded by the scene-classifier and task_orchestrator, and task-orchestrator-v7 is just an older version of task_orchestrator. The Claude Code skills (architecture, commands, security, telemetry, tools) were learned from source code analysis and are primarily knowledge-based rather than operational. Beyond that, there's a distinction between core system skills that are always available and workspace skills that may or may not be currently active.","thinkingSignature":"039ebbdb942f30610edc24b743981bf56bd71cbe5c0e9b023d3d5ca98620cdb8"},{"type":"text","text":"技能梳理结果汇报：\n\n---\n\n**系统技能**（OpenClaw 内置，始终可用）\n\n| 技能 | 用途 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `self-improvement` | 捕获错误/纠正，持续改进 | ✅ |\n| `coding-agent` | 委托 Codex/Claude Code 执行编码任务 | ✅ |\n| `gh-issues` | GitHub issues → PR 修复流程 | ✅ |\n| `github` | GitHub 仓库管理、CI、issue | ✅ |\n| `session-logs` | 搜索分析 session 日志 | ✅ |\n| `tmux` | 远程控制 tmux 会话 | ✅ |\n| `weather` | 天气查询 | ✅ |\n| `clawhub` | 从 clawhub.com 安装技能 | ✅ |\n| `mcporter` | MCP 服务器工具调用 | ✅ |\n| `summarize` | URL/文件/视频内容摘要 | ✅ |\n| `video-frames` | 视频帧提取 | ✅ |\n| `openai-whisper` | 本地语音转文字 | ✅ |\n| `healthcheck` | 安全审计与加固 | ✅ |\n| `node-connect` | 节点连接诊断 | ✅ |\n\n---\n\n**飞书集成技能**\n\n| 技能 | 用途 |\n|------|------|\n| `feishu-doc` | 文档读写 |\n| `feishu-drive` | 云盘文件管理 |\n| `feishu-perm` | 权限管理 |\n| `feishu-wiki` | 知识库导航 |\n\n---\n\n**workspace 技能**（按来源分四类）\n\n**A. 核心工作流**\n| 技能 | 用途 | 备注 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `task_orchestrator` | 任务评分路由+上下文保护+子代理上报 | ⚠️ v7版是重复 |\n| `scene-classifier` | 9种场景分类（嵌入向量+规则） | ⚠️ v8_classifier/scorer 是降级备用 |\n| `self-improving` | 自我改进心跳系统 | ✅ |\n| `proactivity` | 主动性 Agent（心跳+信号） | ✅ |\n| `superpowers` | Spec-first TDD 开发工作流 | 🔶 需确认是否在用 |\n\n**B. Claude Code 源码学习产出**（知识型）\n| 技能 | 来源 |\n|------|------|\n| `claude-code-architecture` | 源码分析 |\n| `claude-code-tools` | 源码分析 |\n| `claude-code-commands` | 源码分析 |\n| `claude-code-security` | 源码分析 |\n| `claude-code-telemetry` | 源码分析 |\n| `claude-code-codingplan` | API 配置 |\n\n**C. 垂直场景**\n| 技能 | 用途 |\n|------|------|\n| `agent-team-orchestration` | 多 Agent 团队编排 |\n| `automation-workflows` | 自动化工作流设计 |\n| `github-manager` | GitHub 全功能管理 |\n| `productivity-automation-kit` | 效率工具箱 |\n| `vercel-deploy` | Vercel 部署 |\n| `intent-enhancer` | 意图检测增强 |\n| `classifier-health` | 分类器健康检查+熔断 |\n| `scrapling` | Web 抓取 |\n\n**D. 知识系统**\n| 技能 | 用途 |\n|------|------|\n| `ontology` | 知识图谱 |\n| `elite-longterm-memory` | 长期记忆系统 |\n| `memory-keeper` | 记忆维护自动化 |\n| `skill-vetter` | 技能安全审查 |\n\n---\n\n**重复/可清理**\n| 技能 | 建议 |\n|------|------|\n| `task-orchestrator-v7` | 删除，v8 是升级版 |\n| `v8_classifier` / `v8_scorer` | 备用降级，可保留但 scene-classifier 主用 |\n| `clawdbot-filesystem` | 第三方，与我无关 |\n\n---\n\n**实际配置中启用的**\n从 config.yml 看：`openclaw-cc-bridge`（codingplan/minimax-m2.5）、v8 评分、sceneClassifier\n\n---\n\n总体判断：**技能很多，但大部分是\"知识型技能\"——告诉你怎么设计，而不是主动执行**。真正主动工作的是 `self-improving`、`proactivity`、`task_orchestrator` 这几个核心调度系统。\n\n要清理重复技能吗？还是先推进别的事？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":50639,"output":1616,"cacheRead":15172,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67427,"cost":{"input":0.015191699999999999,"output":0.0019391999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0009103199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.018041219999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776005698723,"responseId":"062ae542901e24dc57af6b8dc9f60b07"}}
