{"type":"message","id":"28f7e3a0","parentId":"b8ebd81d","timestamp":"2026-04-12T14:59:55.585Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me identify duplicates:\n\n1. `task_orchestrator` vs `task-orchestrator-v7` - v7 was already deleted, only `task_orchestrator` remains now\n2. `v8_classifier` vs `scene-classifier` - both exist, scene-classifier is the main one per memory logs\n3. `v8_scorer` - standalone scorer, but v8 scoring is handled by the scoring service at port 3103\n4. `self-improving` in workspace/skills vs `self-improving` in ~/.openclaw/skills - these are different, one is the full skill, one is the system skill\n\n\n5. `openclaw-github-assistant` vs `github-manager` - both GitHub-related but serve different purposes\n6. `agent-team-orchestration` vs `productivity-automation-kit` - not direct duplicates, though `productivity-automation-kit` does mention team collaboration\n\nSo the main duplicates are `v8_classifier` and `v8_scorer` which are backup systems for the scene classification and scoring services already running. I should check the memory logs to confirm what these were set up for.\n\nLooking at the records, scene-classifier was deployed as the main classifier at port 3104, while v8_classifier and v8_scorer in the skills directory were created as fallback options using skill-based invocation when the service isn't available. The v8_scorer skill would invoke the scoring service at 3103 as a backup mechanism.\n\nSince clawdbot-filesystem is now removed, I can focus on identifying the remaining duplicate pair.","thinkingSignature":"6351ed6e3f6cdc79b7f9b25a6771cbe23285a2e86d2dd74f9fcc0ae7c7cc18d7"},{"type":"text","text":"目录层面没有同名的重复。但有以下重叠：\n\n**直接重复**\n| 项目 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| `v8_classifier/` + `scene-classifier/` | 同一个东西的两套入口，scene-classifier 是主用，v8_classifier 是备用降级 |\n| `v8_scorer/` | 备用降级，调用 3103 评分服务 |\n\n**功能重叠**\n| 项目 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| `openclaw-github-assistant` + `github-manager` | 都是 GitHub 管理，assistant 是轻量查询，manager 是全功能 |\n| `self-improving` (workspace) + `self-improving-agent` (~/.openclaw/skills) | workspace 版是详细技能文档，openclaw 内置版是执行层 |\n\n建议：\n- `v8_classifier` 和 `v8_scorer` 可以合并到 scene-classifier 作为子模块，或者保留作降级\n- GitHub 相关的 `github-manager` 够了，`openclaw-github-assistant` 可以删\n\n要删哪些？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":55686,"output":563,"cacheRead":15172,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71421,"cost":{"input":0.0167058,"output":0.0006755999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0009103199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.018291719999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776005976590,"responseId":"062ae657b9891844687d35d44a202edf"}}
