{"type":"message","id":"924d8ed0","parentId":"69832965","timestamp":"2026-04-12T15:09:22.317Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No results for 3105 - it's not listening. So 3105 is completely gone.Now let me give the summary to the user:1. **Port 3100**: Orphaned IPv6 listening socket - a previous process (probably a Node.js app) has died but the kernel still holds the port. The inode is 24308. This is a zombie port that needs to be cleared.2. **Port 3105**: No process is listening. The proxy/agent was shut down (as noted in the 4/11 memory).So I should report:- 3100 = orphaned zombie port, process is gone but kernel holds it- 3105 = nothing running, the proxy service was shut down at some point\n\nI should recommend either removing the port or figuring out what service was supposed to be there.","thinkingSignature":"f9fa5c719942841a57c855efe2dc08e6d744b0ce47b67b90e64953366fc543e9"},{"type":"text","text":"**3100**：孤立端口（orphan socket）\n\n- 在 `/proc/net/tcp6` 里找到，inode 24308，但 `ss -tlnp` 显示无进程绑定\n- 原因：之前的进程已崩溃/被kill，但内核还没释放这个端口\n- 状态：**僵尸端口**，需要手动清理\n\n**3105**：无任何监听\n\n- 确认没有任何进程在监听 3105\n- 4/10 部署的智能代理在那之后就被关掉了，再没重启过\n\n---\n\n**3100 清理方法**：重启相关服务或重启容器才能释放，否则会一直占着端口。\n\n**3105 要不要重新部署？** 还是先把 v8_classifier/v8_scorer 合并方案做了再说？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":71002,"output":328,"cacheRead":15172,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86502,"cost":{"input":0.0213006,"output":0.00039359999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0009103199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02260452}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776006550116,"responseId":"062ae89570056aab5c4a3bb6e89bd8d5"}}
