{"type":"message","id":"9fd2a662","parentId":"e0b76fda","timestamp":"2026-04-12T15:10:05.992Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to know what 3105 was used for. Let me check the memory files and logs from April 10 to understand what the 3105 proxy/agent was doing.","thinkingSignature":"a9488eaab14935a1f02d780b2e498a79048e2221f7b287d0f071ec8e3ccd3cd3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dadclph0x9c1_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-04-10.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":82,"cacheRead":15172,"cacheWrite":69646,"totalTokens":84954,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.00009839999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0009103199999999999,"cacheWrite":0.02611725,"total":0.02714217}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776006597939,"responseId":"062ae8c53646ffe684bd530cc0c493c2"}}
{"type":"message","id":"25d502ea","parentId":"9fd2a662","timestamp":"2026-04-12T15:10:06.065Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_dadclph0x9c1_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-04-10 工作日志\n\n## v8 任务编排器升级\n\n- 完成评分引擎升级：从 v7 8因子 → v8 6因子\n  - 因子：logic, risk, duration, resource, uncertainty, dependency\n  - 加入了组合规则（duration+dependency 触发 MEGA_TASK）\n- 已替换 `~/.openclaw/v8/src/scoring/scoring.js`\n\n## 场景分类器部署\n\n- 从 workspace 复制 scene-classifier 到 v8 目录\n- 端口配置为 3104\n- 添加了熔断降级逻辑（连续3次失败打开熔断，30秒后恢复）\n- 已配置 systemd 开机自启\n\n## Skills 创建\n\n- `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/v8_classifier/` - 调用 3104 分类服务\n- `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/v8_scorer/` - 调用 3103 评分服务\n\n## 代理服务 3105\n\n- 创建 `~/.openclaw/proxy/` 目录\n- 实现了 v8Client 客户端（分类+评分）\n- 端口 3105 运行代理服务\n- 支持闲聊模板直接回复（非任务不走 LLM）\n- 支持任务评分后转发 Gateway\n\n## 双入口架构\n\n- **3102**：原 Gateway（简单对话）\n- **3105**：v8 代理（智能分类+评分）\n- 两个入口并存，客户端可选择连接\n\n## 遗留问题\n\n- Control UI (3110) 认证问题：需要通过 localStorage 设置 token\n- 3102/3105 端口切换需要手动管理，避免冲突\n# 2026-04-10 工作日志\n\n## v8 任务编排器升级\n\n- 完成评分引擎升级：从 v7 8因子 → v8 6因子\n  - 因子：logic, risk, duration, resource, uncertainty, dependency\n  - 加入了组合规则（duration+dependency 触发 MEGA_TASK）\n- 已替换 `~/.openclaw/v8/src/scoring/scoring.js`\n\n## 场景分类器部署\n\n- 从 workspace 复制 scene-classifier 到 v8 目录\n- 端口配置为 3104\n- 添加了熔断降级逻辑（连续3次失败打开熔断，30秒后恢复）\n- 已配置 systemd 开机自启\n\n## Skills 创建\n\n- `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/v8_classifier/` - 调用 3104 分类服务\n- `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/v8_scorer/` - 调用 3103 评分服务\n\n## 代理服务 3105\n\n- 创建 `~/.openclaw/proxy/` 目录\n- 实现了 v8Client 客户端（分类+评分）\n- 端口 3105 运行代理服务\n- 支持闲聊模板直接回复（非任务不走 LLM）\n- 支持任务评分后转发 Gateway\n\n## 双入口架构\n\n- **3102**：原 Gateway（简单对话）\n- **3105**：v8 代理（智能分类+评分）\n- 两个入口并存，客户端可选择连接\n\n## 遗留问题\n\n- Control UI (3110) 认证问题：需要通过 localStorage 设置 token\n- 3102/3105 端口切换需要手动管理，避免冲突\n\n---\n\n## 2026-04-10 下午更新\n\n### 3102 智能代理升级完成\n\n- 代理服务迁移到 3102 端口\n- 安装 http-proxy-middleware 实现 UI 转发\n- 现在 3102 同时拥有：完整网页 UI + 智能分类评分\n- 架构：用户 → 3102 代理 → 3104 分类 → 3103 评分 → 3108 Gateway\n\n### 新增模块\n\n- `~/.openclaw/v8/src/scoring/rule-tuner.js` - 评分规则自动调优\n- `~/.openclaw/v8/src/scoring/weight-learner.js` - 评分权重自适应学习\n- `~/.openclaw/v8/src/observability/strategy-analyzer.js` - 策略分析报告生成\n- 分类器热更新 API：/rules, /reload-rules, /update-rules\n\n### Context API 部署\n\n- 端口 3106\n- 功能：对话历史存储 + Token 监控 + 自动摘要压缩\n- 集成到代理中，每次消息自动存储上下文\n\n### 当前端口状态\n\n| 端口 | 服务 |\n|------|------|\n| 3102 | 智能代理（含分类评分+UI转发） |\n| 3103 | v8 评分引擎 |\n| 3104 | 场景分类器 |\n| 3106 | Context API |\n| 3108 | Gateway |\n| 3110 | Control UI |\n\n### 框架能力总结\n\n- ✅ 场景分类：9种意图识别\n- ✅ 任务评分：6因子 + 组合规则\n- ✅ 策略路由：DIRECT/STEP/SUBAGENT/PARALLEL/MEGA\n- ✅ 上下文保护：自动压缩（80%阈值）\n- ✅ 评分调优：rule-tuner + weight-learner\n- ✅ 策略分析：strategy-analyzer\n- ✅ 分类器热更新"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776006606055}}
{"type":"message","id":"0cd42ab2","parentId":"25d502ea","timestamp":"2026-04-12T15:10:21.619Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the full picture. 3105 was the v8 intelligent proxy/agent that had scene classification + scoring built in. But according to the afternoon update on 4/10, it got merged into 3102 (the gateway port). So 3105 was the standalone version that was later deprecated when the gateway took over its functionality.\n\nSo currently:\n- 3102 = Smart proxy (with scene classification + scoring + UI forwarding) + Gateway\n- 3105 = Obsolete, was the standalone smart proxy before it was merged into 3102\n\nThe 3105 skill files still exist in ~/.openclaw/skills/ and ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/, but the actual service is not running.","thinkingSignature":"349d215a52453975500ebfd82e975ea475148d1676e9e5c695e766bc0e841e11"},{"type":"text","text":"**3105 的来龙去脉：**\n\n它是 4/10 部署的**智能代理服务**（v8 Client），核心功能：\n- 自动识别消息是闲聊还是任务\n- 任务自动走评分（3103）+ 分类（3104）\n- 非任务（闲聊）直接模板回复，不调 LLM，省 token\n\n**但当天下午就被合并进 3102 了**——3102 现在同时跑着 Gateway 网页 UI + 智能分类评分。3105 作为独立进程就被废弃了。\n\n所以现在：\n- **3102**：Gateway + 智能代理，二合一 ✅\n- **3105**：已废弃，空占端口\n\nskill 目录里的 `v8_classifier` / `v8_scorer` 就是给这个代理用的客户端代码。\n\n要不要清理 skill 目录里这些 3105 相关的废弃客户端代码？还是先做别的？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":70880,"output":335,"cacheRead":15172,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86387,"cost":{"input":0.021263999999999998,"output":0.00040199999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0009103199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.022576319999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776006606068,"responseId":"062ae8cd42c4d708f71b4426c037027f"}}
