{"type":"message","id":"bebfc5bc","parentId":"45a06017","timestamp":"2026-04-12T15:15:44.627Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_dpvxnk2s325q_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"const express = require('express');\nconst { v4: uuidv4 } = require('uuid');\nconst { scoreTask } = require('../scoring/scoring');\n\nfunction createApiRouter(taskStore, scheduler, healthChecker, security, metrics, config) {\n  const router = express.Router();\n\n  // 限流中间件\n  router.use('/task', (req, res, next) => {\n    const ip = req.ip || req.connection.remoteAddress;\n    if (!security.checkRateLimit(ip)) {\n      return res.status(429).json({ error: 'Rate limit exceeded', retryAfter: 1 });\n    }\n    next();\n  });\n\n  // POST /api/score\n  router.post('/score', async (req, res) => {\n    try {\n      const { prompt, context } = req.body;\n      const result = await scoreTask(prompt, context);\n      res.json(result);\n    } catch (err) {\n      res.status(500).json({ error: err.message });\n    }\n  });\n\n  // POST /api/task\n  router.post('/task', async (req, res) => {\n    try {\n      const { id, command, args, cwd, env, timeout, priority, metadata, type, skillName, skillParams } = req.body;\n\n      // 技能任务不需要 command\n      if (type === 'skill' && skillName) {\n        const task = {\n          id: id || uuidv4(),\n          type,\n          skillName,\n          skillParams: skillParams || {},\n          command: 'internal-skill',\n          args: [],\n          timeout: timeout || 7200,\n          priority: priority || 0,\n          metadata\n        };\n        const result = await taskStore.enqueue(task);\n        metrics.inc('tasks_submitted');\n        return res.status(202).json({\n          id: result.id,\n          status: 'pending',\n\n[81 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776006944619}}
{"type":"message","id":"35487201","parentId":"bebfc5bc","timestamp":"2026-04-12T15:16:00.561Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the scoring API:\n- Endpoint: `POST http://127.0.0.1:3103/api/score`\n- Body: `{ prompt, context }` (prompt is the user message text, context is optional additional info)\n- Response: `{ score, factors, recommendedStrategy, timeout, _raw }`\n\nLet me now create the v8_scorer skill. I'll make a simple HTTP client skill that calls the 3103 scoring API.","thinkingSignature":"1a2e833567eeca622d9bcdcf0b01cabaa643998efd10618435373525ba1b4e89"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_oqn7xrnevqi8_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/skills/v8_scorer/SKILL.md","content":"---\nname: v8_scorer\ndescription: Call the v8 scoring engine at port 3103 to evaluate task complexity. Use when you need to score a task to determine execution strategy (DIRECT/STEP/SUBAGENT/PARALLEL/MEGA). Input: { prompt: string, context?: object }. Output: { score, factors, recommendedStrategy, timeout }.\nversion: 1.0.0\n---\n\n# v8_scorer\n\n调用 v8 评分引擎（端口 3103）评估任务复杂度。\n\n## API\n\n```\nPOST http://127.0.0.1:3103/api/score\nContent-Type: application/json\nBody: { \"prompt\": \"<user message>\", \"context\": {} }\n```\n\n## 响应格式\n\n```json\n{\n  \"score\": <0-100>,\n  \"factors\": {\n    \"logic\": <0-2>,\n    \"risk\": <0-2>,\n    \"duration\": <0-2>,\n    \"resource\": <0-2>,\n    \"uncertainty\": <0-2>,\n    \"dependency\": <0-2>\n  },\n  \"recommendedStrategy\": \"DIRECT | STEP_ARCHIVE | SPAWN_SUBAGENT | PARALLEL_SHARDS | MEGA_TASK\",\n  \"timeout\": <seconds>,\n  \"_raw\": { ... }\n}\n```\n\n## 策略路由\n\n| 分数 | 策略 | 超时 |\n|------|------|------|\n| ≤20 | DIRECT | 30s |\n| 21-40 | STEP_ARCHIVE | 60s |\n| 41-60 | SPAWN_SUBAGENT | 60-180s |\n| 61-80 | PARALLEL_SHARDS | 120-160s |\n| >80 | MEGA_TASK | 7200s |\n\n## 评分因子说明\n\n- **logic**: 逻辑复杂度（条件分支、循环、递归）\n- **risk**: 风险等级（危险命令、不可逆操作）\n- **duration**: 预估执行时长\n- **resource**: 资源需求（CPU/IO/内存）\n- **uncertainty**: 不确定性（需求模糊、技术风险）\n- **dependency**: 依赖复杂度（外部依赖、工具链）\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":74877,"output":608,"cacheRead":15172,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90657,"cost":{"input":0.0224631,"output":0.0007296,"cacheRead":0.0009103199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02410302}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776006944628,"responseId":"062aea2057361b97c6ff3ab72311431e"}}
