{"type":"message","id":"f355a2c1","parentId":"3d266e7a","timestamp":"2026-04-12T15:16:15.126Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The classifier at 3104 works too. Let me also create the v8_classifier skill.","thinkingSignature":"3c673e58dae5062b98e50f879421449f16a73f52354fff396d71731ec9c5f755"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1otaq3g8ufre_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/skills/v8_classifier/SKILL.md","content":"---\nname: v8_classifier\ndescription: Call the scene classifier at port 3104 to classify user intent into 9 scene types. Use when you need to understand the intent behind a user message (chitchat, task, fault_recovery, etc.). Input: { text: string }. Output: { scene, confidence, intercepted }.\nversion: 1.0.0\n---\n\n# v8_classifier\n\n调用场景分类器（端口 3104）识别用户意图。\n\n## API\n\n```\nPOST http://127.0.0.1:3104/classify\nContent-Type: application/json\nBody: { \"text\": \"<user message>\" }\n```\n\n## 响应格式\n\n```json\n{\n  \"scene\": \"chitchat | task_multi_step | fault_recovery | vague_request | novice_user | expert_user | high_risk_automated | task_status_query | cancel_task\",\n  \"confidence\": <0.0-1.0>,\n  \"intercepted\": true | false,\n  \"meta\": \"...\",\n  \"[LLM响应]\": \"...\"\n}\n```\n\n## 9 种场景类型\n\n| 场景 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| chitchat | 闲聊，无需任务执行 |\n| task_multi_step | 多步骤任务 |\n| fault_recovery | 故障恢复 |\n| vague_request | 意图模糊 |\n| novice_user | 新手用户 |\n| expert_user | 专家用户 |\n| high_risk_automated | 高风险自动化 |\n| task_status_query | 任务状态查询 |\n| cancel_task | 取消任务 |\n\n## 降级逻辑\n\n- 超时 300ms → 降级到规则分类器\n- 连续 3 次失败 → 打开熔断，30 秒后恢复\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":75677,"output":439,"cacheRead":15172,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91288,"cost":{"input":0.0227031,"output":0.0005268,"cacheRead":0.0009103199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02414022}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776006964225,"responseId":"062aea34cb40ac4