{"type":"message","id":"7764d1f5","parentId":"49a67ff1","timestamp":"2026-04-12T16:54:00.527Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write complete SKILL.md files for v8_scorer and v8_classifier, based on what I just learned from the actual code. They want the complete content. Let me write comprehensive SKILL.md files that capture the real implementation details.\n\nFor v8_scorer:\n- 6 factors: logic, risk, duration, resource, uncertainty, dependency\n- Each factor 0-3, max 18\n- Square root normalization: sqrt(raw/18) * 100\n- Strategy selection with special rules\n- API endpoint: POST http://127.0.0.1:3103/api/score\n\n\nFor v8_classifier:\n- 9 scene types: chitchat, task_multi_step, fault_recovery, vague_request, novice_user, expert_user, high_risk_automated, task_status_query, cancel_task\n- Embedding-based (paraphrase-multilingual-MiniLM-L12-v2) + KNN with rule fallback\n- Confidence threshold at 0.5, ambiguity gap of 0.1\n- API endpoint: POST http://127.0.0.1:3104/classify\n\nNow I'll write out the complete, detailed SKILL.md content for both.","thinkingSignature":"6d3cb79a3215c9e88a2e73f1250097036a1fb0eda4cb7d184cf8d94538520699"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vm6iuexawmnx_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/skills/v8_scorer/SKILL.md","content":"---\nname: v8_scorer\ndescription: OpenClaw v8 任务复杂度评分引擎。调用 3103 API，评估任务复杂度并返回执行策略。用于判断用户任务应走 DIRECT/STEP/SUBAGENT/PARALLEL/MEGA 哪种执行路径。\nversion: 1.0.0\n---\n\n# v8_scorer\n\n> OpenClaw v8 任务复杂度评分引擎（端口 3103）\n>\n> 基于 6因子规则评分的生产级实现，非 ML 模型\n\n---\n\n## 一、评分原理\n\n### 1.1 六因子体系\n\n每个因子 0-3 分，总原始分 0-18 分。\n\n| 因子 | 名称 | 含义 | 典型触发词 |\n|------|------|------|-----------|\n| `logic` | 逻辑复杂度 | 重构、算法、多文件、条件分支 | 重构、正则、状态机、多个文件 |\n| `risk` | 风险度 | 删除、数据库、系统修改 | rm -rf、数据库、chmod、生产环境 |\n| `duration` | 预估时长 | 编译、安装、测试等耗时操作 | 编译、npm install、测试、下载 |\n| `resource` | 资源消耗 | GPU、视频、大数据等重载操作 | 训练、GPU、视频处理、大数据 |\n| `uncertainty` | 不确定性 | API调用、网络、调试等不稳定因素 | API、curl、网络请求、调试 |\n| `dependency` | 依赖复杂度 | monorepo、微服务、多依赖 | monorepo、微服务、多依赖 |\n\n### 1.2 归一化公式\n\n```\nnormalized = round(sqrt(rawScore / 18) * 100)\n```\n\n**含义**：平方根归一化，低分增长快、高分增长缓，更符合实际分布\n\n| 原始分 | 归一化分 |\n|--------|----------|\n| 0 | 0 |\n| 2 | 33 |\n| 3 | 41 |\n| 6 | 57 |\n| 9 | 70 |\n| 12 | 81 |\n| 18 | 100 |\n\n### 1.3 策略选择规则\n\n**特殊规则（优先于分数区间）**：\n\n| 条件 | 策略 | 超时 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `risk >= 3` | `SPAWN_SUBAGENT` | 180s |\n| `resource >= 3` | `PARALLEL_SHARDS` | 300s |\n| `uncertainty >= 3` | `SPAWN_SUBAGENT` | 180s |\n| `duration >= 3 && dependency >= 2` | `MEGA_TASK` | 7200s |\n| `logic >= 3 && duration >= 3` | `PARALLEL_SHARDS` | 300s |\n\n**分数区间规则**：\n\n| 归一化分 | 策略 | 超时 |\n|----------|------|------|\n| ≤20 | `DIRECT` | 30s |\n| 21-40 | `STEP_ARCHIVE` | 60s |\n| 41-60 | `SPAWN_SUBAGENT` | 120s |\n| 61-80 | `PARALLEL_SHARDS` | 240s |\n| >80 | `MEGA_TASK` | 7200s |\n\n---\n\n## 二、API 规范\n\n### 端点\n\n```\nPOST http://127.0.0.1:3103/api/score\nContent-Type: application/json\n```\n\n### 请求\n\n```json\n{\n  \"prompt\": \"<用户消息文本>\",\n  \"context\": {\n    \"fileCount\": 5,\n    \"estimatedLines\": 500,\n    \"isProduction\": false\n  }\n}\n```\n\n`context` 可选，用于增强评分精度：\n- `fileCount > 10` → logic 因子额外 +2\n- `estimatedLines > 1000` → duration 因子额外 +2\n- `isProduction: true` → risk 因子额外 +2\n\n### 响应\n\n```json\n{\n  \"score\": 57,\n  \"factors\": {\n    \"logic\": 1,\n    \"risk\": 2,\n    \"duration\": 0,\n    \"resource\": 0,\n    \"uncertainty\": 1,\n    \"dependency\": 1\n  },\n  \"recommendedStrategy\": \"SPAWN_SUBAGENT\",\n  \"timeout\": 120,\n  \"_raw\": {\n    \"total\": 5,\n    \"max\": 18\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 意图检测（辅助接口）\n\n```\nPOST http://127.0.0.1:3103/api/intent\nBody: { \"prompt\": \"<用户消息>\" }\n```\n\n返回 `{ \"intent\": \"task\" | \"chat\", \"confidence\": 0.0-1.0 }`\n\n---\n\n## 三、调用场景\n\n### 必须调用的场景\n- 用户请求执行多步骤任务（写代码、部署、分析、重构等）\n- 需要判断任务复杂度以选择执行策略时\n- 任务涉及文件操作、命令执行、API 调用时\n\n### 可跳过的场景\n- 纯闲聊（你好、天气、问候）\n- 信息查询（概念解释、文档查找）\n- 低风险简单问答\n\n### 判断流程\n\n```\n用户消息\n  ↓\n调用 v8_scorer\n  ↓\nscore ≤ 20 → DIRECT（直接执行）\nscore 21-40 → STEP_ARCHIVE（分步存档）\nscore 41-60 → SPAWN_SUBAGENT（子代理）\nscore 61-80 → PARALLEL_SHARDS（并行分片）\nscore > 80 → MEGA_TASK（巨型任务）\n```\n\n---\n\n## 四、响应示例\n\n### 示例1：简单问答\n\n**请求**：`\"解释一下什么是闭包\"`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"score\": 0,\n  \"factors\": {\n    \"logic\": 0,\n    \"risk\": 0,\n    \"duration\": 0,\n    \"resource\": 0,\n    \"uncertainty\": 0,\n    \"dependency\": 0\n  },\n  \"recommendedStrategy\": \"DIRECT\",\n  \"timeout\": 30,\n  \"_raw\": { \"total\": 0, \"max\": 18 }\n}\n```\n\n### 示例2：代码重构\n\n**请求**：`\"重构这个项目的用户模块\"`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"score\": 57,\n  \"factors\": {\n    \"logic\": 2,\n    \"risk\": 0,\n    \"duration\": 2,\n    \"resource\": 0,\n    \"uncertainty\": 1,\n    \"dependency\": 2\n  },\n  \"recommendedStrategy\": \"SPAWN_SUBAGENT\",\n  \"timeout\": 120,\n  \"_raw\": { \"total\": 7, \"max\": 18 }\n}\n```\n\n### 示例3：危险操作\n\n**请求**：`\"rm -rf /var/log/*\" `\n\n```json\n{\n  \"score\": 70,\n  \"factors\": {\n    \"logic\": 0,\n    \"risk\": 3,\n    \"duration\": 1,\n    \"resource\": 0,\n    \"uncertainty\": 0,\n    \"dependency\": 0\n  },\n  \"recommendedStrategy\": \"SPAWN_SUBAGENT\",\n  \"timeout\": 180,\n  \"_raw\": { \"total\": 4, \"max\": 18 }\n}\n```\n\n### 示例4：巨型任务\n\n**请求**：`\"分析这个 monorepo 项目并重构核心模块，编写测试，部署到生产环境\"`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"score\": 91,\n  \"factors\": {\n    \"logic\": 3,\n    \"risk\": 2,\n    \"duration\": 3,\n    \"resource\": 1,\n    \"uncertainty\": 2,\n    \"dependency\": 3\n  },\n  \"recommendedStrategy\": \"MEGA_TASK\",\n  \"timeout\": 7200,\n  \"_raw\": { \"total\": 14, \"max\": 18 }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 五、代码位置\n\n- 评分引擎：`/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/scoring/scoring.js`\n- 适配器：`/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/scoring/adapter.js`\n- 配置文件：`/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/scoring/config/`\n- 调优模块：`rule-tuner.js`（评分规则自动调优）、`weight-learner.js`（权重自适应学习）\n\n---\n\n## 六、相关文档\n\n- [[v8_classifier]] - 场景分类器（端口 3104）\n- [[task_orchestrator]] - 任务编排器（整合评分+分类+路由）\n- [[scene-classifier]] - workspace 版场景分类器\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":2135,"cacheRead":99411,"cacheWrite":3951,"totalTokens":105551,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.002562,"cacheRead":0.005964659999999999,"cacheWrite":0.001481625,"total":0.010024485}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776012802502,"responseId":"062b0102be31b960a7eab96218f4b22e"}}
