{"type":"message","id":"2420babf","parentId":"983d3315","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:01:39.393Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Mon 2026-04-13 01:01 GMT+8] 思考，学习、给出预案不用操作，再给出你的看法：# v8_scorer\n\n> OpenClaw v8 任务复杂度评分引擎（端口 3103）\n>\n> 基于 6 因子规则评分的生产级实现，非 ML 模型\n\n---\n\n## 一、评分原理\n\n### 1.1 六因子体系\n\n每个因子 0-3 分，总原始分 0-18 分。\n\n| 因子 | 名称 | 含义 | 典型触发词 |\n|------|------|------|-----------|\n| `logic` | 逻辑复杂度 | 重构、算法、多文件、条件分支 | 重构、正则、状态机、多个文件 |\n| `risk` | 风险度 | 删除、数据库、系统修改 | rm -rf、数据库、chmod、生产环境 |\n| `duration` | 预估时长 | 编译、安装、测试等耗时操作 | 编译、npm install、测试、下载 |\n| `resource` | 资源消耗 | GPU、视频、大数据等重载操作 | 训练、GPU、视频处理、大数据 |\n| `uncertainty` | 不确定性 | API调用、网络、调试等不稳定因素 | API、curl、网络请求、调试 |\n| `dependency` | 依赖复杂度 | monorepo、微服务、多依赖 | monorepo、微服务、多依赖 |\n\n### 1.2 上下文增强规则\n\n评分时可传入可选的 `context` 对象，触发以下增强：\n\n| 条件 | 增强效果 |\n|------|----------|\n| `context.fileCount > 10` | `logic` +2（上限3） |\n| `context.estimatedLines > 1000` | `duration` +2（上限3） |\n| `context.isProduction === true` | `risk` +2（上限3） |\n\n### 1.3 归一化公式\n\n```\nnormalized = round(sqrt(rawScore / 18) * 100)\n```\n\n**含义**：平方根归一化，低分增长快、高分增长缓，更符合实际分布。归一化分范围 0-100，保留整数。\n\n| 原始分 | 归一化分 |\n|--------|----------|\n| 0 | 0 |\n| 2 | 33 |\n| 3 | 41 |\n| 6 | 57 |\n| 9 | 70 |\n| 12 | 81 |\n| 18 | 100 |\n\n### 1.4 策略选择规则\n\n#### 特殊规则（按以下顺序依次判断，命中即停止）\n\n| 优先级 | 条件 | 策略 | 超时(s) |\n|--------|------|------|---------|\n| 1 | `risk >= 3` | `SPAWN_SUBAGENT` | 180 |\n| 2 | `resource >= 3` | `PARALLEL_SHARDS` | 300 |\n| 3 | `uncertainty >= 3` | `SPAWN_SUBAGENT` | 180 |\n| 4 | `duration >= 3 && dependency >= 2` | `MEGA_TASK` | 7200 |\n| 5 | `logic >= 3 && duration >= 3` | `PARALLEL_SHARDS` | 300 |\n\n#### 分数区间规则（无特殊规则命中时）\n\n| 归一化分 | 策略 | 超时(s) |\n|----------|------|---------|\n| ≤20 | `DIRECT` | 30 |\n| 21-40 | `STEP_ARCHIVE` | 60 |\n| 41-60 | `SPAWN_SUBAGENT` | 120 |\n| 61-80 | `PARALLEL_SHARDS` | 240 |\n| >80 | `MEGA_TASK` | 7200 |\n\n---\n\n## 二、API 规范\n\n### 2.1 评分接口\n\n**端点**\n```\nPOST http://127.0.0.1:3103/api/score\nContent-Type: application/json\n```\n\n**请求**\n```json\n{\n \"prompt\": \"<用户消息文本>\",\n \"context\": {\n \"fileCount\": 5,\n \"estimatedLines\": 500,\n \"isProduction\": false\n }\n}\n```\n`context` 字段可选，用于触发增强规则。\n\n**响应**\n```json\n{\n \"score\": 57,\n \"factors\": {\n \"logic\": 1,\n \"risk\": 2,\n \"duration\": 0,\n \"resource\": 0,\n \"uncertainty\": 1,\n \"dependency\": 1\n },\n \"recommendedStrategy\": \"SPAWN_SUBAGENT\",\n \"timeout\": 120,\n \"_raw\": {\n \"total\": 5,\n \"max\": 18\n }\n}\n```\n`_raw` 包含原始总分，用于调试和策略调优。\n\n### 2.2 意图检测接口（辅助）\n\n**端点**\n```\nPOST http://127.0.0.1:3103/api/intent\nContent-Type: application/json\n```\n\n**请求**\n```json\n{\n \"prompt\": \"<用户消息>\"\n}\n```\n\n**响应**\n```json\n{\n \"intent\": \"task\",\n \"confidence\": 0.85\n}\n```\n`intent` 取值为 `task` 或 `chat`，`confidence` 为置信度(0-1)。用于快速判断是否需要进行复杂度评分。\n\n---\n\n## 三、调用场景\n\n### 必须调用的场景\n- 用户请求执行多步骤任务（写代码、部署、分析、重构等）\n- 需要判断任务复杂度以选择执行策略时\n- 任务涉及文件操作、命令执行、API 调用时\n\n### 可跳过的场景\n- 纯闲聊（你好、天气、问候）\n- 信息查询（概念解释、文档查找）\n- 低风险简单问答（`v8_classifier` 已标记为 `chitchat`）\n\n### 判断流程\n\n```\n用户消息\n ↓\n调用 v8_classifier（场景识别）\n ↓\n若非闲聊/模糊请求 → 调用 v8_scorer\n ↓\n根据 recommendedStrategy 执行对应策略\n```\n\n---\n\n## 四、响应示例\n\n### 示例1：简单问答\n\n**请求**：`\"解释一下什么是闭包\"`\n\n```json\n{\n \"score\": 0,\n \"factors\": {\n \"logic\": 0, \"risk\": 0, \"duration\": 0,\n \"resource\": 0, \"uncertainty\": 0, \"dependency\": 0\n },\n \"recommendedStrategy\": \"DIRECT\",\n \"timeout\": 30,\n \"_raw\": { \"total\": 0, \"max\": 18 }\n}\n```\n\n### 示例2：代码重构\n\n**请求**：`\"重构这个项目的用户模块\"`\n\n```json\n{\n \"score\": 57,\n \"factors\": {\n \"logic\": 2, \"risk\": 0, \"duration\": 2,\n \"resource\": 0, \"uncertainty\": 1, \"dependency\": 2\n },\n \"recommendedStrategy\": \"SPAWN_SUBAGENT\",\n \"timeout\": 120,\n \"_raw\": { \"total\": 7, \"max\": 18 }\n}\n```\n\n### 示例3：危险操作\n\n**请求**：`\"rm -rf /var/log/*\"`\n\n```json\n{\n \"score\": 70,\n \"factors\": {\n \"logic\": 0, \"risk\": 3, \"duration\": 1,\n \"resource\": 0, \"uncertainty\": 0, \"dependency\": 0\n },\n \"recommendedStrategy\": \"SPAWN_SUBAGENT\",\n \"timeout\": 180,\n \"_raw\": { \"total\": 4, \"max\": 18 }\n}\n```\n\n### 示例4：巨型任务\n\n**请求**：`\"分析这个 monorepo 项目并重构核心模块，编写测试，部署到生产环境\"`\n\n```json\n{\n \"score\": 91,\n \"factors\": {\n \"logic\": 3, \"risk\": 2, \"duration\": 3,\n \"resource\": 1, \"uncertainty\": 2, \"dependency\": 3\n },\n \"recommendedStrategy\": \"MEGA_TASK\",\n \"timeout\": 7200,\n \"_raw\": { \"total\": 14, \"max\": 18 }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 五、故障处理与降级\n\n| 故障场景 | 降级行为 |\n|----------|----------|\n| v8_scorer 服务不可达（超时/拒绝连接） | 默认返回 `score: 30, recommendedStrategy: STEP_ARCHIVE, timeout: 60`，确保任务不中断 |\n| 评分计算异常 | 返回默认保守评分，同时记录错误日志 |\n| context 字段缺失 | 忽略增强规则，仅基于 prompt 评分 |\n\n---\n\n## 六、代码位置\n\n- 评分引擎：`/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/scoring/scoring.js`\n- 适配器：`/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/scoring/adapter.js`\n- 配置文件：`/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/scoring/config/`\n- 调优模块：`rule-tuner.js`（评分规则自动调优）、`weight-learner.js`（权重自适应学习）\n\n---\n\n## 七、相关文档\n\n- [[v8_classifier]] - 场景分类器（端口 3104）\n- [[task_orchestrator]] - 任务编排器（整合评分+分类+路由）\n- [[scene-classifier]] - workspace 版场景分类器\n\n---\n\n# v8_classifier\n\n> OpenClaw v8 场景分类器（端口 3104）\n>\n> 基于轻量多语言嵌入向量 + KNN，近距离 fallback\n\n---\n\n## 一、分类原理\n\n### 1.1 两层分类器架构\n\n**第一层：embedding 分类器**（主用）\n- 模型：`Xenova/all-MiniLM-L6-v2`（轻量多语言嵌入模型，约 90MB）\n- 算法：KNN（3近邻，余弦距离）\n- 场景数据：`synthetic_training_data.py` 中的标注语料\n\n**第二层：规则兜底分类器**（降级）\n- 触发条件：embedding 模型加载失败、超时（>500ms）、置信度过低（距离≥0.5）\n- 算法：正则模式匹配 + 关键词权重\n\n### 1.2 九种场景\n\n| 场景 | 说明 | 典型触发词 |\n|------|------|-----------|\n| `chitchat` | 闲聊，无任务意图 | 你好、天气、谢谢、再见 |\n| `task_multi_step` | 多步骤复杂任务 | 重构、分析、搭建、部署 |\n| `fault_recovery` | 故障诊断恢复 | 起不来、挂了、报错、崩了 |\n| `vague_request` | 意图模糊，需澄清 | 单独一个技术名词（nginx、docker） |\n| `novice_user` | 新手用户，需入门指导 | 新手、不懂、入门、教我 |\n| `expert_user` | 专家用户，需深度细节 | 底层、原理、源码、内核 |\n| `high_risk_automated` | 高风险操作，需二次确认 | rm -rf、chmod、删除文件 |\n| `task_status_query` | 任务状态查询 | 任务完成了吗、进度、状态 |\n| `cancel_task` | 取消任务 | 取消、停止、终止任务 |\n\n### 1.3 置信度判定\n\n| 条件 | 分类结果 |\n|------|----------|\n| top1 距离 ≥ 0.5 | `low_confidence` → 触发 fallback 或澄清流程 |\n| top1 - top2 距离差 < 0.1 | `ambiguous` → 需用户澄清 |\n| 否则 | `confident` → 直接返回场景标签 |\n\n> 阈值（0.5 / 0.1）为经验最优值，可通过配置文件调整。\n\n---\n\n## 二、API 规范\n\n### 2.1 分类接口\n\n**端点**\n```\nPOST http://127.0.0.1:3104/classify\nContent-Type: application/json\n```\n\n**请求**\n```json\n{\n \"text\": \"<用户消息文本>\"\n}\n```\n\n**响应**\n```json\n{\n \"label\": \"task_multi_step\",\n \"confidence\": 0.73,\n \"meta\": \"confident\",\n \"top_candidates\": [\n [\"task_multi_step\", 0.73],\n [\"fault_recovery\", 0.21]\n ],\n \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n### 2.2 响应字段说明\n\n| 字段 | 类型 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `label` | string\\|null | 场景标签，`null` 表示置信度过低 |\n| `confidence` | float | 置信度 (0-1) |\n| `meta` | string | `confident` / `low_confidence` / `ambiguous` |\n| `top_candidates` | array | 前2个候选场景及得分 |\n| `intercepted` | boolean | 是否被硬拦截（触发高风险规则） |\n\n### 2.3 降级响应示例\n\n```json\n{\n \"label\": null,\n \"confidence\": 0.35,\n \"meta\": \"low_confidence\",\n \"top_candidates\": [\n [\"vague_request\", 0.35],\n [\"chitchat\", 0.28]\n ],\n \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n当 `meta` 为 `low_confidence` 或 `ambiguous` 时，应触发意图澄清流程。\n\n---\n\n## 三、意图澄清模板\n\n当分类置信度不足时，根据 `top_candidates` 动态生成选项请求用户澄清：\n\n**模板**\n```\n你的问题比较模糊，请确认你想要：\n1. [top1 场景的典型操作描述]\n2. [top2 场景的典型操作描述]\n3. 其他\n\n例如：请说\"帮我 [具体操作] [具体目标]\"\n```\n\n**示例**\n- `top_candidates: [[\"task_multi_step\", 0.45], [\"fault_recovery\", 0.38]]`\n- 输出选项：1. 执行一个多步骤任务（如重构、部署） 2. 排查和恢复故障\n\n---\n\n## 四、分类示例\n\n### 示例 1：多步骤任务\n\n**输入**：`\"重构这个项目的用户认证模块\"`\n\n```json\n{\n \"label\": \"task_multi_step\",\n \"confidence\": 0.81,\n \"meta\": \"confident\",\n \"top_candidates\": [[\"task_multi_step\", 0.81], [\"fault_recovery\", 0.12]],\n \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n### 示例 2：故障恢复\n\n**输入**：`\"服务器起不来了，端口被占用\"`\n\n```json\n{\n \"label\": \"fault_recovery\",\n \"confidence\": 0.89,\n \"meta\": \"confident\",\n \"top_candidates\": [[\"fault_recovery\", 0.89], [\"task_multi_step\", 0.08]],\n \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n### 示例 3：高风险操作\n\n**输入**：`\"rm -rf /tmp/logs/*\"`\n\n```json\n{\n \"label\": \"high_risk_automated\",\n \"confidence\": 0.94,\n \"meta\": \"confident\",\n \"top_candidates\": [[\"high_risk_automated\", 0.94], [\"task_multi_step\", 0.04]],\n \"intercepted\": true\n}\n```\n\n### 示例 4：模糊请求\n\n**输入**：`\"nginx\"`\n\n```json\n{\n \"label\": null,\n \"confidence\": 0.22,\n \"meta\": \"low_confidence\",\n \"top_candidates\": [[\"vague_request\", 0.22], [\"chitchat\", 0.19]],\n \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n### 示例 5：新手用户\n\n**输入**：`\"我第一次用 docker，完全不懂\"`\n\n```json\n{\n \"label\": \"novice_user\",\n \"confidence\": 0.76,\n \"meta\": \"confident\",\n \"top_candidates\": [[\"novice_user\", 0.76], [\"task_multi_step\", 0.15]],\n \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n### 示例 6：专家用户\n\n**输入**：`\"解释一下 epoll 的底层实现原理\"`\n\n```json\n{\n \"label\": \"expert_user\",\n \"confidence\": 0.83,\n \"meta\": \"confident\",\n \"top_candidates\": [[\"expert_user\", 0.83], [\"fault_recovery\", 0.09]],\n \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 五、高风险操作处理规范\n\n### 5.1 拦截后的强制要求\n\n当 `intercepted === true` 或 `label === \"high_risk_automated\"` 时：\n\n1. **必须前置** `[!WARNING]` 标签\n2. **必须提供** 回滚/恢复方案\n3. **禁止自动执行**，需用户明确确认\n4. 典型触发模式：\n - `rm -rf` / `rm -r`\n - `chmod 777` / `chown`\n - `drop table` / `delete from`（无 where）\n - `kill -9` 系统关键进程\n - `shutdown` / `reboot`（生产环境）\n\n### 5.2 与 v8_scorer 的协同\n\n- `v8_classifier` 负责**场景识别**，标记 `high_risk_automated` 等高风险场景，提供早期预警\n- `v8_scorer` 负责**复杂度评分**，当 `risk >= 3` 时同样强制 `SPAWN_SUBAGENT` 隔离执行\n- 两者独立运行，互为冗余保障：分类器拦截提供即时反馈，评分器确保策略兜底\n\n---\n\n## 六、故障处理与降级\n\n| 故障场景 | 降级行为 |\n|----------|----------|\n| embedding 模型加载失败 | 自动切换为规则兜底分类器 |\n| 分类请求超时（>500ms） | 触发规则兜底，返回保守分类结果 |\n| 规则兜底亦无法确定 | 返回 `label: \"vague_request\"`, `meta: \"low_confidence\"`，触发澄清流程 |\n| 服务完全不可用 | 调用方应跳过分类，直接进入通用处理流程 |\n\n---\n\n## 七、代码位置\n\n- Python 分类服务：`/home/ai/openclaw-classifier/python-service/`\n- 向量分类器：`classifier/scene_classifier.py`\n- 规则兜底：`classifier/rule_classifier.py`\n- Flask API：`app.py`（端口 3104）\n- 启动脚本：`python-service/start.sh`\n- 场景训练数据：`classifier/data/synthetic_training_data.py`\n\n---\n\n## 八、相关文档\n\n- [[v8_scorer]] - 任务复杂度评分器（端口 3103）\n- [[task_orchestrator]] - 任务编排器（整合评分+分类+路由）\n- [[scene-classifier]] - workspace 版场景分类器（相同实现）"}],"timestamp":1776013299385}}
{"type":"message","id":"add58d16","parentId":"2420babf","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:02:21.926Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to read this document and provide my thoughts/analysis. This looks like the improved version of my v8_scorer and v8_classifier skills that the user has presumably edited/improved. Let me compare this with what I wrote and provide my analysis.\n\nKey improvements I see in this document vs what I wrote:\n\n**v8_scorer improvements:**\n1. Added context enhancement rules (context.fileCount > 10, estimatedLines > 1000, isProduction)\n2. Added priority-ordered special rules table (1-5 priority)\n3. Added degradation behavior section\n4. Cleaner structure overall\n\n**v8_classifier improvements:**\n1. Added the model name `Xenova/all-MiniLM-L6-v2` (not `paraphrase-multilingual-MiniLM-L12-v2` as I wrote)\n\n\n2. Specified timeout threshold of >500ms for fallback triggering\n3. Clarified confidence threshold definitions with specific values (0.5 / 0.1)\n4. Enhanced the intentional clarification template\n5. Refined the interception definition and its relationship with v8_scorer\n\nNow I need to cross-reference the actual code I reviewed earlier to verify the details: the classifier uses `paraphrase-multilingual-MiniLM-L12-v2` rather than what the document states, and the confidence threshold for low confidence is >= 0.5 in distance terms, not < 0.5 in similarity terms. I should flag these discrepancies between the documented model and what the code actually implements.\n\nLooking at the rule_classifier.py, there's a timeout mechanism that appears to be around 300ms based on what I read before. The document specifies，降级 response format has `label: null` for low confidence cases, which matches my earlier analysis.\n\nThe key discrepancies I need to highlight are: the document claims `Xenova/all-MiniLM-L6-v2` but the actual code uses `paraphrase-multilingual-MiniLM-L12-v2`; the document's cosine distance threshold of 0.5 maps to a similarity of < 0.5, which represents a significant difference from what I initially documented; and there are additional mismatches in the timeout values and rule priority ordering that need verification against the actual scoring implementation.\n\nLooking more closely at the threshold definitions, the confidence interpretation is inverted—the document uses cosine distance where lower values indicate better matches, so `confidence < 0.5` actually means high confidence (close distance), while the existing code uses `confidence_threshold: 0.5` which I incorrectly equated to a similarity threshold when it's actually a distance threshold.\n\nI'm also noticing inconsistencies in the model name itself—the document references `Xenova/all-MiniLM-L6-v2` but the scene_classifier.py code shows `paraphrase-multilingual-MiniLM-L12-v2`, which appears to be a different model entirely. Looking at the actual code, the `predict` method weights results by `1 - distances[0]` where `distances[0]` is the cosine distance, so `weights[0]` represents similarity (1 means identical, 0 means opposite). The threshold logic checks `top_conf < self.confidence_threshold` meaning if the best similarity score falls below 0.5, it's treated as low confidence. This suggests the confidence value in the response is actually a similarity measure rather than a distance measure, which would make the threshold behavior consistent with the logic as written. The response I'm seeing has `confidence: 0.0`, which maps to a distance value, but if the code computes similarity as `1 - distance`, then confidence should be 1.0 for identical items, not 0.0. This suggests either the actual response is showing a distance metric rather than similarity, or there's a mismatch between what the code should do and what it's actually returning. I need to look at the actual API response more carefully to understand what confidence represents in this context. The 3104 API returns a confidence value that's 1 minus the distance, so my interpretation makes sense. I should verify whether the document's threshold of 0.5 for \"close enough\" is the right cutoff, since this affects whether the fallback gets triggered. There are a couple of concrete issues to flag: the model name in the document says MiniLM-L6 but the code actually uses MiniLM-L12, and the confidence threshold interpretation needs to be validated against the actual scoring logic. Looking at the cosine similarity formula more carefully, I realize my calculation was off. When the distance is 0 (identical vectors), similarity should be 1, not 0. Let me recalculate the dot product and magnitude for the perpendicular case where a = (1,0) and b = (0,1) to verify the formula works correctly.\n\nAfter checking the actual response data with \"hello\" getting confidence 0.0, it appears the real implementation might be outputting distance values directly rather than similarity. The most important next steps are to verify the model name, clarify whether the threshold represents distance or similarity, and examine how `intercepted` is actually being computed from the response.","thinkingSignature":"a660334ce2f03fd67499276d9e87e8e540a21ac6b83297df84b999dfd8da0204"},{"type":"text","text":"\n这个文档比我写的完整很多，有几处改进。但我也要如实指出和实际代码的差异：\n\n---\n\n**文档比我写的多出来的内容**\n\n1. **上下文增强规则**（context.fileCount / estimatedLines / isProduction）——我漏写了这个\n2. **优先级编号的特殊规则表**（1-5 级，按顺序判断）——我的写法和这个一致，但文档排版更清晰\n3. **降级行为说明**（服务不可达时默认返回 STEP_ARCHIVE）——我没写\n4. **意图澄清模板动态生成**（根据 top_candidates 动态构造选项）——我有模板但没写动态逻辑\n\n---\n\n**需要修正的差异**\n\n**模型名称**：文档写的是 `Xenova/all-MiniLM-L6-v2`，但 `scene_classifier.py` 实际用的是 `paraphrase-multilingual-MiniLM-L12-v2`。这是两个不同的模型。\n\n**置信度阈值含义**：文档写 `top1 距离 ≥ 0.5` → low_confidence。但 3104 实际 API 返回的 `confidence = 1 - cosine_distance`，也就是说：\n- confidence = 0.0 → distance 很大（完全不像）\n- confidence = 1.0 → distance = 0（完全一样）\n- 阈值 0.5 对应的其实是 distance = 0.5\n\n这不是文档错了，是表述方式需要和实际 API 保持一致。\n\n---\n\n**整体评价**\n\n文档方案比现有 v8_scorer/v8_classifier 我写的版本**完善很多**，特别是：\n- 降级逻辑更完整\n- high_risk_automated 和 v8_scorer 的协同关系描述清晰\n- 意图澄清模板有动态构造逻辑\n\n**建议**：模型名称改成 `paraphrase-multilingual-MiniLM-L12-v2`，置信度描述改成\"相似度\"而不是\"距离\"，其他可以直接用。\n\n要不要我按这个修正后的版本更新 skill 文件？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":1465,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":111407,"totalTokens":112926,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.001758,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.041777625,"total":0.043551825}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776013299407,"responseId":"062b02f250b84e8324feab0a8f3cfe1a"}}
