{"type":"message","id":"535179f5","parentId":"97454617","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:11:12.100Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So there are self-improving and memory-keeper skills in the workspace. But are they being activated? The system prompt's available_skills section shows `self-improvement` skill which maps to `~/.openclaw/skills/self-improving-agent/SKILL.md`. That skill should be available.\n\nBut the user is asking if memory and context skills are \"启动\" (activated/loaded). This is a question about whether these skills are actually running in the current session.\n\nLooking at the bootstrap context that was loaded at startup, it mentions \"技能系统：skills/ 目录有 31 个技能，没看到技能被激活的迹象\" - this was the same observation made in a previous session.\n\n\nThe available_skills section lists specific skills like self-improvement, coding-agent, gh-issues, github, session-logs, tmux, weather, clawhub, mcporter, summarize, video-frames, openai-whisper, healthcheck, and node-connect. However, workspace skills like self-improving and memory-keeper aren't included in that list, which suggests they may not be automatically activated.\n\nLooking at the skills_path configuration would clarify how OpenClaw determines which skills to load and when.","thinkingSignature":"52d45d4fb59db6aee61890d70a319213e8f83621666f043657e82015cd3c32c9"},{"type":"text","text":"Skills 目录里有这些相关技能：\n\n**workspace/skills/**：\n- `self-improving/` ✅\n- `memory-keeper/` ✅\n- `elite-longterm-memory/` ✅\n- `proactivity/` ✅\n\n**~/.openclaw/skills/**（系统级）：\n- `self-improving-agent/` ✅\n\n**当前会话状态**：\n\n从系统 prompt 的 `available_skills` 看，当前会话我只加载了系统内置的 14 个技能（clawhub、session-logs、github、tmux 等）。workspace 下的 `self-improving`、`proactivity`、`memory-keeper` 这类**自定义 Agent 技能**并没有在当前会话自动激活。\n\n**3106 Context API** 是连接着的（`connected: true`），但那是 Listener 和 Gateway 之间的消息队列，不是 skill 激活。\n\n**问题**：workspace 下的 self-improving / memory-keeper / proactivity 这类技能需要通过 `openclaw skills` 命令显式加载