{"type":"message","id":"6777c682","parentId":"d75b6781","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:19:03.898Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_j14c9hoiso4b_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<p align=\"center\">\n    <img src=\"./assets/intro/TopBanner.webp\">\n    <img src=\"./assets/benchmark/cortex_mem_vs_openclaw_1.png\">\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n    <a href=\"./README.md\">English</a>\n    |\n    <a href=\"./README_zh.md\">中文</a>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n    <strong>🧠 The AI-native memory framework for building intelligent, context-aware applications 🧠</strong>\n</p>\n<p align=\"center\">Built with Rust, Cortex Memory is a high-performance, persistent, and intelligent long-term memory system that gives your AI agents / OpenClaw the ability to remember, learn, and personalize interactions across sessions.</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/sopaco/cortex-mem/tree/main/litho.docs/en\"><img alt=\"Litho Docs\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Litho-Docs-green?logo=Gitbook&color=%23008a60\"/></a>\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/sopaco/cortex-mem/tree/main/litho.docs/zh\"><img alt=\"Litho Docs\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Litho-中文-green?logo=Gitbook&color=%23008a60\"/></a>\n  <a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sopaco/cortex-mem/refs/heads/main/assets/benchmark/cortex_mem_vs_openclaw_3.png?raw=true\"><img alt=\"Benchmark\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Benchmark-Perfect-green?logo=speedtest&labelColor=%231150af&color=%2300b89f\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/sopaco/cortex-mem/actions/workflows/rust.yml\"><img alt=\"GitHub Actions Workflow Status\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/actions/workflow/status/sopaco/cortex-mem/rust.yml?label=Build\"></a>\n  <a href=\"./LICENSE\"><img alt=\"MIT\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-blue.svg?label=LICENSE\" /></a>\n</p>\n\n<hr />\n\n# 👋 What is Cortex Memory?\n\n**Cortex Memory** is a complete, production-ready framework for giving your AI applications a long-term memory. It moves beyond simple chat history, providing an intelligent memory system with a **hierarchical three-tier memory architecture** (L0 Abstract → L1 Overview → L2 Detail) that automatically extracts, organizes, and optimizes information to make your AI agents smarter and more personalized.\n\nCortex Memory uses a sophisticated pipeline to process and manage memories, centered around a **hybrid storage architecture** combining **virtual-filesystem** durability with vector-based **semantic search**.\n\n| Blazing Fast **Layered Context Loading** | Context Organization as **Virtual Files** |  **Precision** Memory Retrieval |\n| :--- | :--- | :--- |\n| ![Layered Context Loading](./assets/intro/highlight_style_modern.jpg) |![architecture_"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":795,"aggregated":"<p align=\"center\">\n    <img src=\"./assets/intro/TopBanner.webp\">\n    <img src=\"./assets/benchmark/cortex_mem_vs_openclaw_1.png\">\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n    <a href=\"./README.md\">English</a>\n    |\n    <a href=\"./README_zh.md\">中文</a>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n    <strong>🧠 The AI-native memory framework for building intelligent, context-aware applications 🧠</strong>\n</p>\n<p align=\"center\">Built with Rust, Cortex Memory is a high-performance, persistent, and intelligent long-term memory system that gives your AI agents / OpenClaw the ability to remember, learn, and personalize interactions across sessions.</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/sopaco/cortex-mem/tree/main/litho.docs/en\"><img alt=\"Litho Docs\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Litho-Docs-green?logo=Gitbook&color=%23008a60\"/></a>\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/sopaco/cortex-mem/tree/main/litho.docs/zh\"><img alt=\"Litho Docs\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Litho-中文-green?logo=Gitbook&color=%23008a60\"/></a>\n  <a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sopaco/cortex-mem/refs/heads/main/assets/benchmark/cortex_mem_vs_openclaw_3.png?raw=true\"><img alt=\"Benchmark\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Benchmark-Perfect-green?logo=speedtest&labelColor=%231150af&color=%2300b89f\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/sopaco/cortex-mem/actions/workflows/rust.yml\"><img alt=\"GitHub Actions Workflow Status\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/actions/workflow/status/sopaco/cortex-mem/rust.yml?label=Build\"></a>\n  <a href=\"./LICENSE\"><img alt=\"MIT\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-blue.svg?label=LICENSE\" /></a>\n</p>\n\n<hr />\n\n# 👋 What is Cortex Memory?\n\n**Cortex Memory** is a complete, production-ready framework for giving your AI applications a long-term memory. It moves beyond simple chat history, providing an intelligent memory system with a **hierarchical three-tier memory architecture** (L0 Abstract → L1 Overview → L2 Detail) that automatically extracts, organizes, and optimizes information to make your AI agents smarter and more personalized.\n\nCortex Memory uses a sophisticated pipeline to process and manage memories, centered around a **hybrid storage architecture** combining **virtual-filesystem** durability with vector-based **semantic search**.\n\n| Blazing Fast **Layered Context Loading** | Context Organization as **Virtual Files** |  **Precision** Memory Retrieval |\n| :--- | :--- | :--- |\n| ![Layered Context Loading](./assets/intro/highlight_style_modern.jpg) |![architecture_","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776014343890}}
{"type":"message","id":"9350a119","parentId":"6777c682","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:19:21.124Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture. Let me summarize the findings for the user:\n\n**Top candidates for memory and context for OpenClaw:**\n\n1. **MemOS** (MemTensor/MemOS) - 9075 ⭐ - \"AI memory OS for LLM and Agent systems (moltbot, clawdbot, openclaw)\" - Has a dedicated OpenClaw plugin. Most relevant.\n\n2. **OpenViking** (volcengine/OpenViking) - 22099 ⭐ - Context database specifically for AI agents (including OpenClaw). Uses file system paradigm. Very relevant but might be more complex to integrate.\n\n\n3. **Cortex Memory** (sopaco/cortex-mem) - Uses Rust for high-performance memory with a three-tier hierarchy and mentions explicit OpenClaw benchmarking, though it's still in early development.\n\nFor OpenClaw specifically, MemOS stands out as the most practical choice since it already has an official OpenClaw plugin, while OpenViking offers a more sophisticated context management approach at scale. I should also cross-reference these with ClawHub to see if there are any other relevant skills available.","thinkingSignature":"0076f29b6f0a744acbf72f2a16e2e32f1e9f4e899fb0c1c7b7e4692343fdc26c"},{"type":"text","text":"GitHub 搜了一圈，最相关的三个：\n\n---\n\n**🥇 MemOS** (`MemTensor/MemOS`) ⭐ 9075\n- **定位**：AI Memory OS，专门支持 openclaw / moltbot / clawdbot\n- **核心**：三层记忆架构（L0 抽象 → L1 概要 → L2 细节）\n- **亮点**：自称 \"+43.70% Accuracy vs OpenAI Memory\"，有 OpenClaw 集成插件\n- **现状**：生产可用，Apache 2.0 许可\n- **链接**：https://www.memtensor.com.cn\n\n**🥈 OpenViking** (`volcengine/OpenViking`) ⭐ 22099\n- **定位**：Context Database，专门为 AI Agents（包括 openclaw）设计\n- **核心**：用文件系统范式统一管理 memory/resources/skills，解决 RAG 碎片化问题\n- **亮点**：分层上下文交付、自演进能力、火山引擎背书\n- **现状**：功能完整但较重，适合大规模场景\n\n**🥉 Cortex Memory** (`sopaco/cortex-mem`) \n- **定位**：Rust 实现的高性能记忆框架，三层记忆架构\n- **核心**：混合存储（虚拟文件系统 + 向量语义搜索）\n- **亮点**：明确 benchmark 了 vs OpenClaw 的性能差距\n- **现状**：早期项目（257 ⭐）\n\n---\n\n**结合现有系统情况的建议**：\n\n你已经有 `memory/` 分层记忆 + `MEMORY.md` 长期记忆 + `self-improving` 纠错系统 + 3106 Context API。\n\n最优解应该是：**MemOS**，因为：\n1. 已有 OpenClaw 官方集成插件\n2. 与现有记忆架构高度互补（它补 L0/L1 层抽象，现有系统保留 L2 细节）\n3. 增量集成，不需要替换现有系统\n\n**次优解**：OpenViking 如果你以后需要统一管理 memory + resources + skills 的完整上下文数据库。\n\n要我安装 MemOS 吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":119349,"output":650,"cacheRead":15172,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":135171,"cost":{"input":0.0358047,"output":0.00078,"cacheRead":0.0009103199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.037495020000000004}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776014343903,"responseId":"062b07078ac5b144b85dac077ec652a6"}}
