{"type":"message","id":"01fcbba2","parentId":"7e8723ac","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:22:14.704Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_t8flkrxd8x7o_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities-archive/claude-code-40-tools-complete-report.md\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities-archive/claude-code-ultimate-final-report.md\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities-archive/second-brain-report.md\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities-archive/research-wiki.md\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities-archive/claude-code-production-implementation-report.md\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities-archive/book-wiki.md\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities-archive/human-role.md\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities-archive/wiki-schema.md\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities-archive/implementation-report.md\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities-archive/naming-conventions.md"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":58,"aggregated":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities-archive/claude-code-40-tools-complete-report.md\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities-archive/claude-code-ultimate-final-report.md\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities-archive/second-brain-report.md\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities-archive/research-wiki.md\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities-archive/claude-code-production-implementation-report.md\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities-archive/book-wiki.md\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities-archive/human-role.md\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities-archive/wiki-schema.md\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities-archive/implementation-report.md\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities-archive/naming-conventions.md","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776014534692}}
{"type":"message","id":"02c99eab","parentId":"01fcbba2","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:22:14.712Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_t8flkrxd8x7o_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\ntitle: LLM Wiki Pattern\ntype: concept\nstatus: active\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [llm-wiki, knowledge-base, pattern]\n---\n\n# 📚 LLM Wiki Pattern\n\n> LLM 驱动的个人知识库模式\n\n## 核心理念\n\n**不采用 RAG 模式，而是编译 (Compilation)**\n\n| RAG | LLM Wiki |\n|-----|----------|\n| 每次查询重新发现 | 知识已编译、持续积累 |\n| 无积累 | 交叉引用已建立 |\n| 无法处理复杂综合问题 | 多文档综合已有答案 |\n\n## 三层架构\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ Raw Sources (不可变)                 │\n│ 文章、论文、对话、笔记               │\n└─────────────────────────────────────┘\n                   ↓ LLM 摄取\n┌─────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ Wiki (LLM 维护)                     │\n│ 实体页 + 概念页 + 交叉引用           │\n└─────────────────────────────────────┘\n                   ↓ LLM 维护\n┌─────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ Schema (CLAUDE.md / AGENTS.md)      │\n│ 页面格式、workflow、约定            │\n└─────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n## Operations\n\n### 1. Ingest (摄取)\n\n1. 放入新 source 到 raw/\n2. LLM 读取，提取关键信息\n3. 写 summary 到 wiki\n4. 更新相关 entity/concept 页 (10-15 个)\n5. 追加 log\n\n### 2. Query (查询)\n\n1. 读 index 找相关页\n2. 读取页面内容\n3. 合成答案\n4. 好答案可写回 wiki\n\n### 3. Lint (检查)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":52,"aggregated":"---\ntitle: LLM Wiki Pattern\ntype: concept\nstatus: active\nlast_updated: 2026-04-11\ntags: [llm-wiki, knowledge-base, pattern]\n---\n\n# 📚 LLM Wiki Pattern\n\n> LLM 驱动的个人知识库模式\n\n## 核心理念\n\n**不采用 RAG 模式，而是编译 (Compilation)**\n\n| RAG | LLM Wiki |\n|-----|----------|\n| 每次查询重新发现 | 知识已编译、持续积累 |\n| 无积累 | 交叉引用已建立 |\n| 无法处理复杂综合问题 | 多文档综合已有答案 |\n\n## 三层架构\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ Raw Sources (不可变)                 │\n│ 文章、论文、对话、笔记               │\n└─────────────────────────────────────┘\n                   ↓ LLM 摄取\n┌─────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ Wiki (LLM 维护)                     │\n│ 实体页 + 概念页 + 交叉引用           │\n└─────────────────────────────────────┘\n                   ↓ LLM 维护\n┌─────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ Schema (CLAUDE.md / AGENTS.md)      │\n│ 页面格式、workflow、约定            │\n└─────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n## Operations\n\n### 1. Ingest (摄取)\n\n1. 放入新 source 到 raw/\n2. LLM 读取，提取关键信息\n3. 写 summary 到 wiki\n4. 更新相关 entity/concept 页 (10-15 个)\n5. 追加 log\n\n### 2. Query (查询)\n\n1. 读 index 找相关页\n2. 读取页面内容\n3. 合成答案\n4. 好答案可写回 wiki\n\n### 3. Lint (检查)","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776014534704}}
{"type":"message","id":"dea00e58","parentId":"02c99eab","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:22:23.486Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see. There's an \"LLM Wiki Pattern\" that was implemented - a knowledge management system with:1. Raw Sources (immutable)2. Wiki (LLM maintained) - entities + concept pages + cross-references\n3. Schema (CLAUDE.md / AGENTS.md)And it has operations: Ingest, Query, Lint.The memory/entities directory has this documented. Let me read more to understand the full picture.\n\nBut the user is asking if I remember this task. The honest answer is: I can read the files and understand what was done, but I don't have the actual session memory of doing it. \n\nLet me check what the actual implementation status is.","thinkingSignature":"f50f4e58814c5109ce189619985c0bb693e75c599ae1f958ac1e9d827cb59877"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_w90qg3hg6o3p_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/ 2>/dev/null"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_w90qg3hg6o3p_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/llm-wiki.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l; wc -l /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/*.md 2>/dev/null | tail -5"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":120608,"output":260,"cacheRead":15172,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":136040,"cost":{"input":0.036182399999999997,"output":0.000312,"cacheRead":0.0009103199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.037404719999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776014534715,"responseId":"062b07c61524de8cdf74b3f9d4188548"}}
