{"type":"message","id":"26235d69","parentId":"5ed1bd69","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:22:28.475Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There's a full LLM Wiki implementation in the entities directory. Let me check what the actual state of this is - is it just documentation or is it actually implemented and running?","thinkingSignature":"08a03027738cbba39bfa04b5763fdd95d23283c214f68bc5c296585d17c9ef82"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_je56tetgj8uy_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/llm-wiki-implementation.md 2>/dev/null | head -60"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_je56tetgj8uy_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities-archive/ | grep wiki | head -10"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":121102,"output":133,"cacheRead":15172,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":136407,"cost":{"input":0.0363306,"output":0.0001596,"cacheRead":0.0009103199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03740052}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776014543589,"responseId":"062b07cfd8a1efb422d45dd4262af78e"}}
{"type":"message","id":"3c8bd753","parentId":"26235d69","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:22:28.563Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_je56tetgj8uy_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\ntitle: LLM Wiki Implementation\ntype: entity\nstatus: active\ntags: [implementation, guide]\n---\n\n# LLM Wiki 实现指南\n\n> 基于 LLM Wiki 原文的完整实现\n\n## 原文要点 vs 实现\n\n| 原文要点 | 实现 | 状态 |\n|----------|------|------|\n| 不是RAG,是增量构建 | Wiki 持久化 | ✅ |\n| 知识编译一次 | 实体页沉淀 | ✅ |\n| 10-15页更新 | 融合机制 | ✅ |\n| 维护归零 | auto-lint.sh | ✅ |\n| 人vsLLM职责 | 人思考,LLM执行 | ✅ |\n| 双屏工作 | obsidian.md | ✅ |\n| 问答写回 | query流程 | ✅ |\n| Memex | wiki-evolution.md | ✅ |\n\n## 架构\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│           Raw Sources (docs/)           │\n│    不可变文档, LLM 只读                 │\n└─────────────────┬───────────────────────┘\n                  │ Ingest\n                  ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│            Wiki (entities/)             │\n│    LLM 维护, 增量构建, 持久化           │\n└─────────────────┬───────────────────────┘\n                  │ Query\n                  ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│     Schema (SOUL.md, AGENTS.md)         │\n│    配置约束, 行为规范                   │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n## 操作流程\n\n### Ingest\n1. 添加新 source 到 docs/\n2. LLM 读取并提取\n3. 更新相关实体页 (10-15 页)\n4. 记录到 log.md\n\n### Query\n1. 用户提问\n2. LLM 搜索相关页面\n3. 合成答案\n4. (可选) 写回到 wiki\n\n### Lint (定期)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":48,"aggregated":"---\ntitle: LLM Wiki Implementation\ntype: entity\nstatus: active\ntags: [implementation, guide]\n---\n\n# LLM Wiki 实现指南\n\n> 基于 LLM Wiki 原文的完整实现\n\n## 原文要点 vs 实现\n\n| 原文要点 | 实现 | 状态 |\n|----------|------|------|\n| 不是RAG,是增量构建 | Wiki 持久化 | ✅ |\n| 知识编译一次 | 实体页沉淀 | ✅ |\n| 10-15页更新 | 融合机制 | ✅ |\n| 维护归零 | auto-lint.sh | ✅ |\n| 人vsLLM职责 | 人思考,LLM执行 | ✅ |\n| 双屏工作 | obsidian.md | ✅ |\n| 问答写回 | query流程 | ✅ |\n| Memex | wiki-evolution.md | ✅ |\n\n## 架构\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│           Raw Sources (docs/)           │\n│    不可变文档, LLM 只读                 │\n└─────────────────┬───────────────────────┘\n                  │ Ingest\n                  ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│            Wiki (entities/)             │\n│    LLM 维护, 增量构建, 持久化           │\n└─────────────────┬───────────────────────┘\n                  │ Query\n                  ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│     Schema (SOUL.md, AGENTS.md)         │\n│    配置约束, 行为规范                   │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n## 操作流程\n\n### Ingest\n1. 添加新 source 到 docs/\n2. LLM 读取并提取\n3. 更新相关实体页 (10-15 页)\n4. 记录到 log.md\n\n### Query\n1. 用户提问\n2. LLM 搜索相关页面\n3. 合成答案\n4. (可选) 写回到 wiki\n\n### Lint (定期)","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776014548556}}
