{"type":"message","id":"8feaf33f","parentId":"3d96a387","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:23:33.219Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to continue using the LLM Wiki system. Let me understand what needs to be done to make it work properly:\n\n1. The LLM Wiki system already exists in memory/entities/ with 25 entity pages\n2. The three layers (Raw Sources → Wiki → Schema) are defined\n3. The operations (Ingest, Query, Lint) are defined but not auto-triggered\n4. The issue is similar to the memory system - files exist but the workflow isn't running\n\nThe key question is: what does \"continue using this LLM Wiki system\" mean operationally? Let me think about what's actually needed:\n\n\nThe core workflows—ingesting new sources, querying the wiki, and running periodic linting—aren't being triggered automatically, so I need to figure out how to integrate these into the heartbeat system or as scheduled jobs. The immediate priorities are fixing the session startup to load MEMORY.md properly, ensuring the daily memory files get read, and then establishing a cadence for when to run these wiki operations.\n\nFor the LLM Wiki specifically, I should set up a cron job that periodically checks the docs/ folder for new sources, runs the Ingest workflow, and executes Lint to keep everything current. This is a medium-sized task that requires planning out the workflow steps and dependencies before execution.","thinkingSignature":"d7aa6c2f49bd5ca23c7a28a9e5cff7cf91633b5b898510cc34d068e9dc7e69cd"},{"type":"text","text":"好，基于现有 LLM Wiki 体系，给出实施方案：\n\n---\n\n**现状**\n\n```\ndocs/          → 原始文档（空？）\nentities/      → 25个实体页 ✅ 有内容\nSOUL.md/AGENTS → Schema层 ✅ 刚融合\nIngest/Query/Lint → 流程定义有，但未自动触发\n```\n\n---\n\n**分步实施**\n\n**Step 1：Fix 启动记忆加载（解决断层根因）**\n> 修改 SOUL.md 第9节连续性规则，让 bootstrap 时强制加载 MEMORY.md 和今日/昨日 memory 日志\n\n**Step 2：建立 Ingest 流程（cron 驱动）**\n> 每小时检查 `docs/` 有无新文档，有则触发 LLM 提取 → 更新 entities/ 相关页面 → 记录 log\n\n**Step 3：建立 Lint 流程（心跳驱动）**\n> 每隔 N 次 heartbeat，扫描 entities/ 的链接一致性、过期条目、孤立页面\n\n**Step 4：建立 Query 入口**\n> 明确 Query 触发条件（用户提问涉及某实体时自动走 wiki 检索而非直接 LLM 回答）\n\n---\n\n**核心问题需要先确认**\n\n1. `docs/` 里现在有内容吗？还是需要新建？\n2. 你希望 Ingest 是**全自动**（cron 无声执行）还是**半自动**（cron 检测到新文档后通知你确认）？\n3. Query 入口怎么触发——是用户在问题里带关键词（如\"查一下\"、\"关于XXX\"），还是每次都走 wiki 检索？\n\n确认后我给出具体的 cron + skill 配置方案。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":606,"cacheRead":135606,"cacheWrite":1246,"totalTokens":137512,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0007272,"cacheRead":0.008136359999999999,"cacheWrite":0.00046725,"total":0.00934701}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776014595065,"responseId":"062b08022537346889d9ea8ec7d4a860"}}
