{"type":"message","id":"f473a08b","parentId":"7dc01282","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:32:06.008Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking whether I currently score and classify their messages. Let me think about this.\n\nFrom what I've learned:\n- 3103 (v8_scorer) and 3104 (v8_classifier) are running on the system\n- My SKILL.md files describe how to call them\n- But these are services I CAN call - they don't automatically trigger on every message\n- The router/middleware in OpenClaw would need to call these for every message\n- I don't automatically call them on every user message - I would need to explicitly call the APIs\n\nLet me check if there's any automatic middleware doing this.","thinkingSignature":"027ad51a9196db83e2cc2c331497d8d8b7da4368e73580b249c2beaee39a809c"},{"type":"text","text":"**不会**。\n\nv8_scorer（3103）和 v8_classifier（3104）都在运行，但它们是**按需调用的服务**——不会自动对我的每条消息进行评分和分类。\n\n当前的调用路径是：\n\n```\n你的消息 → 我收到 → 需要时（任务类消息）→ 我手动调用 3103/3104\n```\n\n没有中间件在我收到消息时自动触发评分/分类。\n\n---\n\n**如果要自动评分分类**，需要：\n1. OpenClaw 的 `message_preprocess` 中间件钩子（v8-router 插件）\n2. 或者在 gateway 层配置\n\n目前我没有在每次对话时自动调用 3103/3104 的机制。\n\n---\n\n**所以回答你的问题**：\n\n我现在收到你的消息是**直接回复**的，没有先走评分和分类流程。\n\n你希望我每次收到消息时自动调用 v8_classifier 做意图识别，再决定是否调用 v8_scorer 吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":333,"cacheRead":139555,"cacheWrite":191,"totalTokens":140133,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.00039959999999999996,"cacheRead":0.008373299999999998,"cacheWrite":0.000071625,"total":0.008860724999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776015116335,"responseId":"062b0a0c2f99591ef1cac69bb54a921f"}}
