{"type":"message","id":"a8fb6012","parentId":"1ac65845","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:38:06.945Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_bi8oi2bt5rwe_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: v8_scorer\ndescription: OpenClaw v8 任务复杂度评分引擎。调用 3103 API，评估任务复杂度并返回执行策略。用于判断用户任务应走 DIRECT/STEP/SUBAGENT/PARALLEL/MEGA 哪种执行路径。\nversion: 1.1.0\n---\n\n# v8_scorer\n\n> OpenClaw v8 任务复杂度评分引擎（端口 3103）\n>\n> 基于 6 因子规则评分的生产级实现，非 ML 模型\n\n---\n\n## 一、评分原理\n\n### 1.1 六因子体系\n\n每个因子 0-3 分，总原始分 0-18 分。\n\n| 因子 | 名称 | 含义 | 典型触发词 |\n|------|------|------|-----------|\n| `logic` | 逻辑复杂度 | 重构、算法、多文件、条件分支 | 重构、正则、状态机、多个文件 |\n| `risk` | 风险度 | 删除、数据库、系统修改 | rm -rf、数据库、chmod、生产环境 |\n| `duration` | 预估时长 | 编译、安装、测试等耗时操作 | 编译、npm install、测试、下载 |\n| `resource` | 资源消耗 | GPU、视频、大数据等重载操作 | 训练、GPU、视频处理、大数据 |\n| `uncertainty` | 不确定性 | API调用、网络、调试等不稳定因素 | API、curl、网络请求、调试 |\n| `dependency` | 依赖复杂度 | monorepo、微服务、多依赖 | monorepo、微服务、多依赖 |\n\n### 1.2 上下文增强规则\n\n评分时可传入可选的 `context` 对象，触发以下增强：\n\n| 条件 | 增强效果 |\n|------|----------|\n| `context.fileCount > 10` | `logic` +2（上限3） |\n| `context.estimatedLines > 1000` | `duration` +2（上限3） |\n| `context.isProduction === true` | `risk` +2（上限3） |\n\n### 1.3 归一化公式\n\n```\nnormalized = round(sqrt(rawScore / 18) * 100)\n```\n\n**含义**：平方根归一化，低分增长快、高分增长缓，更符合实际分布。归一化分范围 0-100，保留整数。\n\n| 原始分 | 归一化分 |\n|--------|----------|\n| 0 | 0 |\n| 2 | 33 |\n| 3 | 41 |\n| 6 | 57 |\n| 9 | 70 |\n| 12 | 81 |\n| 18 | 100 |\n\n### 1.4 策略选择规则\n\n#### 特殊规则（按优先级依次判断，命中即停止）\n\n| 优先级 | 条件 | 策略 | 超时(s) |\n|--------|------|------|---------|\n| 1 | `risk >= 3` | `SPAWN_SUBAGENT` | 180 |\n| 2 | `resource >= 3` | `PARALLEL_SHARDS` | 300 |\n| 3 | `uncertainty >= 3` | `SPAWN_SUBAGENT` | 180 |\n| 4 | `duration >= 3 && dependency >= 2` | `MEGA_TASK` | 7200 |\n| 5 | `logic >= 3 && duration >= 3` | `PARALLEL_SHARDS` | 300 |\n\n#### 分数区间规则（无特殊规则命中时）\n\n| 归一化分 | 策略 | 超时(s) |\n|----------|------|---------|\n| ≤20 | `DIRECT` | 30 |\n| 21-40 | `STEP_ARCHIVE` | 60 |\n| 41-60 | `SPAWN_SUBAGENT` | 120 |\n| 61-80 | `PARALLEL_SHARDS` | 240 |\n| >80 | `MEGA_TASK` | 7200 |\n\n---\n\n## 二、API 规范\n\n### 2.1 评分接口\n\n**端点**\n```\nPOST http://127.0.0.1:3103/api/score\nContent-Type: application/json\n```\n\n**请求**\n```json\n{\n  \"prompt\": \"<用户消息文本>\",\n  \"context\": {\n    \"fileCount\": 5,\n    \"estimatedLines\": 500,\n    \"isProduction\": false\n  }\n}\n```\n`context` 字段可选，用于触发增强规则。\n\n**响应**\n```json\n{\n  \"score\": 57,\n  \"factors\": {\n    \"logic\": 1,\n    \"risk\": 2,\n    \"duration\": 0,\n    \"resource\": 0,\n    \"uncertainty\": 1,\n    \"dependency\": 1\n  },\n  \"recommendedStrategy\": \"SPAWN_SUBAGENT\",\n  \"timeout\": 120,\n  \"_raw\": {\n    \"total\": 5,\n    \"max\": 18\n  }\n}\n```\n`_raw` 包含原始总分，用于调试和策略调优。\n\n---\n\n## 三、调用场景\n\n### 必须调用的场景\n- 用户请求执行多步骤任务（写代码、部署、分析、重构等）\n- 需要判断任务复杂度以选择执行策略时\n- 任务涉及文件操作、命令执行、API 调用时\n\n### 可跳过的场景\n- 纯闲聊（你好、天气、问候）\n- 信息查询（概念解释、文档查找）\n- 低风险简单问答（`v8_classifier` 已标记为 `chitchat`）\n\n### 判断流程\n\n```\n用户消息\n  ↓\n调用 v8_classifier（场景识别）\n  ↓\n若非闲聊/模糊请求 → 调用 v8_scorer\n  ↓\n根据 recommendedStrategy 执行对应策略\n```\n\n---\n\n## 四、响应示例\n\n### 示例1：简单问答\n\n**请求**：`\"解释一下什么是闭包\"`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"score\": 0,\n  \"factors\": {\n    \"logic\": 0, \"risk\": 0, \"duration\": 0,\n    \"resource\": 0, \"uncertainty\": 0, \"dependency\": 0\n  },\n  \"recommendedStrategy\": \"DIRECT\",\n  \"timeout\": 30,\n  \"_raw\": { \"total\": 0, \"max\": 18 }\n}\n```\n\n### 示例2：代码重构\n\n**请求**：`\"重构这个项目的用户模块\"`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"score\": 57,\n  \"factors\": {\n    \"logic\": 2, \"risk\": 0, \"duration\": 2,\n    \"resource\": 0, \"uncertainty\": 1, \"dependency\": 2\n  },\n  \"recommendedStrategy\": \"SPAWN_SUBAGENT\",\n  \"timeout\": 120,\n  \"_raw\": { \"total\": 7, \"max\": 18 }\n}\n```\n\n### 示例3：危险操作\n\n**请求**：`\"rm -rf /var/log/*\"`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"score\": 70,\n  \"factors\": {\n    \"logic\": 0, \"risk\": 3, \"duration\": 1,\n    \"resource\": 0, \"uncertainty\": 0, \"dependency\": 0\n  },\n  \"recommendedStrategy\": \"SPAWN_SUBAGENT\",\n  \"timeout\": 180,\n  \"_raw\": { \"total\": 4, \"max\": 18 }\n}\n```\n\n### 示例4：巨型任务\n\n**请求**：`\"分析这个 monorepo 项目并重构核心模块，编写测试，部署到生产环境\"`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"score\": 91,\n  \"factors\": {\n    \"logic\": 3, \"risk\": 2, \"duration\": 3,\n    \"resource\": 1, \"uncertainty\": 2, \"dependency\": 3\n  },\n  \"recommendedStrategy\": \"MEGA_TASK\",\n  \"timeout\": 7200,\n  \"_raw\": { \"total\": 14, \"max\": 18 }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 五、故障处理与降级\n\n| 故障场景 | 降级行为 |\n|----------|----------|\n| v8_scorer 服务不可达（超时/拒绝连接） | 默认返回 `score: 30, recommendedStrategy: STEP_ARCHIVE, timeout: 60`，确保任务不中断 |\n| 评分计算异常 | 返回默认保守评分，同时记录错误日志 |\n| context 字段缺失 | 忽略增强规则，仅基于 prompt 评分 |\n\n---\n\n## 六、代码位置\n\n- 评分引擎：`/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/scoring/scoring.js`\n- 适配器：`/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/scoring/adapter.js`\n- 配置文件：`/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/scoring/config/`\n- 调优模块：`rule-tuner.js`（评分规则自动调优）、`weight-learner.js`（权重自适应学习）\n\n---\n\n## 七、相关文档\n\n- [[v8_classifier]] - 场景分类器（端口 3104）\n- [[task_orchestrator]] - 任务编排器（整合评分+分类+路由）\n- [[scene-classifier]] - workspace 版场景分类器\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776015486932}}
{"type":"message","id":"71317733","parentId":"a8fb6012","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:38:11.119Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand. The scorer endpoint is `POST http://127.0.0.1:3103/api/score`, not `/` or `/score`. Let me verify this.","thinkingSignature":"f8004e779bbde1a716f8410877727a2e88a9c3cf233a711b55118f8242ff52d1"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fg9av1kion5j_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -X POST http://localhost:3103/api/score -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"prompt\":\"分析一下今天早上发生了什么\"}' 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":25252,"output":104,"cacheRead":17719,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43075,"cost":{"input":0.0075756,"output":0.0001248,"cacheRead":0.00106314,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00876354}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776015486946,"responseId":"062b0b7f1fc4f60bf0e6fb7f16ae8722"}}
{"type":"message","id":"4de9bbe8","parentId":"71317733","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:38:11.206Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_fg9av1kion5j_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"score\":24,\"factors\":{\"logic\":0,\"risk\":0,\"duration\":1,\"resource\":0,\"uncertainty\":0,\"dependency\":0},\"recommendedStrategy\":\"STEP_ARCHIVE\",\"timeout\":60,\"_raw\":{\"total\":1,\"max\":18}}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":48,"aggregated":"{\"score\":24,\"factors\":{\"logic\":0,\"risk\":0,\"duration\":1,\"resource\":0,\"uncertainty\":0,\"dependency\":0},\"recommendedStrategy\":\"STEP_ARCHIVE\",\"timeout\":60,\"_raw\":{\"total\":1,\"max\":18}}","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776015491195}}
{"type":"message","id":"2266556c","parentId":"4de9bbe8","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:38:24.007Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Both APIs are working. Now I need to:\n\n1. Create a hook that listens to `message:preprocessed` events\n2. On each message, call 3104/classify and 3103/api/score\n3. Attach the results to session context\n\nThe hook needs to:\n- Run on the `message:preprocessed` event\n- Extract the text from the message\n- Call both APIs in parallel\n- Store results in session context (so the agent can use them)\n\nLooking at the hook docs, the `message:preprocessed` event gives:\n- `context.bodyForAgent` (final enriched body)\n- `context.from`\n- `context.channelId`\n\nThe hook handler can push messages to `event.messages` to send to the user, but for this use case I need to store the classification/score results in the session context so the agent can use them.\n\nLet me write the hook. I'll create:\n\n\n- HOOK.md with metadata\n- handler.ts that calls both APIs and stores results in session context\n\nThe key challenge is storing results in session context. Looking at the hook events, `session:compact:before` and `session:compact:after` relate to session compaction, and `session:patch` modifies session properties. I need to figure out how to persist the classification and scoring data so it survives across the session and remains accessible to the agent.\n\nI could attach it to the messages array, store it in a tmp file and read on agent bootstrap, or use a shared state file. The hook's `context` object has access to `sessionKey` which identifies the session, so I can use that to coordinate state. The simplest approach might be writing the classification/score to a session-specific file that the agent reads during bootstrap.\n\nNow I'm examining the hook handler spec more closely—the event object has a `messages` array I can push to, but that would send something to the user, which I don't want. I need to find where session state actually lives. Let me check if there's an existing hook I can reference, or look at the v8 classifier skill to understand how it processes data.","thinkingSignature":"aace8d1f490ae6ddc15477f6f7affb3437f88c4c0c03875c7de54f4afe6cfc4c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_835z3q9i32p7_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/skills/v8_classifier/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":25425,"output":476,"cacheRead":17719,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43620,"cost":{"input":0.0076275,"output":0.0005712,"cacheRead":0.00106314,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00926184}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776015491208,"responseId":"062b0b8321052f50d474efea225e7917"}}
{"type":"message","id":"cba5edad","parentId":"2266556c","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:38:24.081Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_835z3q9i32p7_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: v8_classifier\ndescription: OpenClaw v8 场景分类器。调用 3104 API，将用户消息分类为9种意图场景（闲聊/任务/故障/模糊等）。用于理解用户消息的底层意图，配合 v8_scorer 做路由决策。\nversion: 1.1.0\n---\n\n# v8_classifier\n\n> OpenClaw v8 场景分类器（端口 3104）\n>\n> 基于轻量多语言嵌入向量 + KNN，近距离 fallback\n\n---\n\n## 一、分类原理\n\n### 1.1 两层分类器架构\n\n**第一层：embedding 分类器**（主用）\n- 模型：`paraphrase-multilingual-MiniLM-L12-v2`（sentence-transformers，约 120MB，多语言支持）\n- 算法：KNN（3近邻，余弦距离）\n- 场景数据：`synthetic_training_data.py` 中的标注语料\n\n**第二层：规则兜底分类器**（降级）\n- 触发条件：embedding 模型加载失败、超时（>500ms）、置信度过低（similarity < 0.5）\n- 算法：正则模式匹配 + 关键词权重\n\n### 1.2 九种场景\n\n| 场景 | 说明 | 典型触发词 |\n|------|------|-----------|\n| `chitchat` | 闲聊，无任务意图 | 你好、天气、谢谢、再见 |\n| `task_multi_step` | 多步骤复杂任务 | 重构、分析、搭建、部署 |\n| `fault_recovery` | 故障诊断恢复 | 起不来、挂了、报错、崩了 |\n| `vague_request` | 意图模糊，需澄清 | 单独一个技术名词（nginx、docker） |\n| `novice_user` | 新手用户，需入门指导 | 新手、不懂、入门、教我 |\n| `expert_user` | 专家用户，需深度细节 | 底层、原理、源码、内核 |\n| `high_risk_automated` | 高风险操作，需二次确认 | rm -rf、chmod、删除文件 |\n| `task_status_query` | 任务状态查询 | 任务完成了吗、进度、状态 |\n| `cancel_task` | 取消任务 | 取消、停止、终止任务 |\n\n### 1.3 置信度判定\n\n> 置信度 = 1 - cosine_distance，即与最近邻的相似度（0-1，1 表示完全匹配）\n\n| 条件 | 分类结果 |\n|------|----------|\n| top1 相似度 < 0.5 | `low_confidence` → 触发 fallback 或澄清流程 |\n| top1 - top2 相似度差 < 0.1 | `ambiguous` → 需用户澄清 |\n| 否则 | `confident` → 直接返回场景标签 |\n\n---\n\n## 二、API 规范\n\n### 2.1 分类接口\n\n**端点**\n```\nPOST http://127.0.0.1:3104/classify\nContent-Type: application/json\n```\n\n**请求**\n```json\n{\n  \"text\": \"<用户消息文本>\"\n}\n```\n\n**响应**\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"task_multi_step\",\n  \"confidence\": 0.73,\n  \"meta\": \"confident\",\n  \"top_candidates\": [\n    [\"task_multi_step\", 0.73],\n    [\"fault_recovery\", 0.21]\n  ],\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n### 2.2 响应字段说明\n\n| 字段 | 类型 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `label` | string\\|null | 场景标签，`null` 表示置信度过低 |\n| `confidence` | float | top1 相似度 (0-1)，1 表示完全匹配 |\n| `meta` | string | `confident` / `low_confidence` / `ambiguous` |\n| `top_candidates` | array | 前2个候选场景及相似度 |\n| `intercepted` | boolean | 是否被硬拦截（触发高风险规则） |\n\n### 2.3 降级响应示例\n\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": null,\n  \"confidence\": 0.35,\n  \"meta\": \"low_confidence\",\n  \"top_candidates\": [\n    [\"vague_request\", 0.35],\n    [\"chitchat\", 0.28]\n  ],\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n当 `meta` 为 `low_confidence` 或 `ambiguous` 时，应触发意图澄清流程。\n\n---\n\n## 三、意图澄清模板\n\n当分类置信度不足时，根据 `top_candidates` 动态生成选项请求用户澄清：\n\n**模板**\n```\n你的问题比较模糊，请确认你想要：\n1. [top1 场景的典型操作描述]\n2. [top2 场景的典型操作描述]\n3. 其他\n\n例如：请说\"帮我 [具体操作] [具体目标]\"\n```\n\n**示例**\n- `top_candidates: [[\"task_multi_step\", 0.45], [\"fault_recovery\", 0.38]]`\n- 输出选项：1. 执行一个多步骤任务（如重构、部署）2. 排查和恢复故障\n\n---\n\n## 四、分类示例\n\n### 示例 1：多步骤任务\n\n**输入**：`\"重构这个项目的用户认证模块\"`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"task_multi_step\",\n  \"confidence\": 0.81,\n  \"meta\": \"confident\",\n  \"top_candidates\": [[\"task_multi_step\", 0.81], [\"fault_recovery\", 0.12]],\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n### 示例 2：故障恢复\n\n**输入**：`\"服务器起不来了，端口被占用\"`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"fault_recovery\",\n  \"confidence\": 0.89,\n  \"meta\": \"confident\",\n  \"top_candidates\": [[\"fault_recovery\", 0.89], [\"task_multi_step\", 0.08]],\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n### 示例 3：高风险操作\n\n**输入**：`\"rm -rf /tmp/logs/*\"`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"high_risk_automated\",\n  \"confidence\": 0.94,\n  \"meta\": \"confident\",\n  \"top_candidates\": [[\"high_risk_automated\", 0.94], [\"task_multi_step\", 0.04]],\n  \"intercepted\": true\n}\n```\n\n### 示例 4：模糊请求\n\n**输入**：`\"nginx\"`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": null,\n  \"confidence\": 0.22,\n  \"meta\": \"low_confidence\",\n  \"top_candidates\": [[\"vague_request\", 0.22], [\"chitchat\", 0.19]],\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n### 示例 5：新手用户\n\n**输入**：`\"我第一次用 docker，完全不懂\"`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"novice_user\",\n  \"confidence\": 0.76,\n  \"meta\": \"confident\",\n  \"top_candidates\": [[\"novice_user\", 0.76], [\"task_multi_step\", 0.15]],\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n### 示例 6：专家用户\n\n**输入**：`\"解释一下 epoll 的底层实现原理\"`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"expert_user\",\n  \"confidence\": 0.83,\n  \"meta\": \"confident\",\n  \"top_candidates\": [[\"expert_user\", 0.83], [\"fault_recovery\", 0.09]],\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 五、高风险操作处理规范\n\n### 5.1 拦截后的强制要求\n\n当 `intercepted === true` 或 `label === \"high_risk_automated\"` 时：\n\n1. **必须前置** `[!WARNING]` 标签\n2. **必须提供** 回滚/恢复方案\n3. **禁止自动执行**，需用户明确确认\n4. 典型触发模式：\n   - `rm -rf` / `rm -r`\n   - `chmod 777` / `chown`\n   - `drop table` / `delete from`（无 where）\n   - `kill -9` 系统关键进程\n   - `shutdown` / `reboot`（生产环境）\n\n### 5.2 与 v8_scorer 的协同\n\n- `v8_classifier` 负责**场景识别**，标记 `high_risk_automated` 等高风险场景，提供早期预警\n- `v8_scorer` 负责**复杂度评分**，当 `risk >= 3` 时同样强制 `SPAWN_SUBAGENT` 隔离执行\n- 两者独立运行，互为冗余保障：分类器拦截提供即时反馈，评分器确保策略兜底\n\n---\n\n## 六、故障处理与降级\n\n| 故障场景 | 降级行为 |\n|----------|----------|\n| embedding 模型加载失败 | 自动切换为规则兜底分类器 |\n| 分类请求超时（>500ms） | 触发规则兜底，返回保守分类结果 |\n| 规则兜底亦无法确定 | 返回 `label: \"vague_request\"`, `meta: \"low_confidence\"`，触发澄清流程 |\n| 服务完全不可用 | 调用方应跳过分类，直接进入通用处理流程 |\n\n---\n\n## 七、代码位置\n\n- Python 分类服务：`/home/ai/openclaw-classifier/python-service/`\n- 向量分类器：`classifier/scene_classifier.py`\n- 规则兜底：`classifier/rule_classifier.py`\n- Flask API：`app.py`（端口 3104）\n- 启动脚本：`python-service/start.sh`\n- 场景训练数据：`classifier/data/synthetic_training_data.py`\n\n---\n\n## 八、相关文档\n\n- [[v8_scorer]] - 任务复杂度评分器（端口 3103）\n- [[task_orchestrator]] - 任务编排器（整合评分+分类+路由）\n- [[scene-classifier]] - workspace 版场景分类器（相同实现）\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776015504073}}
{"type":"message","id":"4f66da3e","parentId":"cba5edad","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:38:55.701Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a complete picture. Both APIs are working. Let me now create the automatic scoring/classification hook. I need to:1. Create a hook that listens to `message:preprocessed`\n2. Call both 3104/classify and 3103/api/score\n3. Store results somewhere the agent can access themThe challenge is: how does the agent access the classification results? Options:\n1. Store in a session-specific state file, read by agent on bootstrap/next turn\n2. Push to event.messages (would show to user as a system message)\n3. Store in session context via session:patch\n\nFor option 3, the session:patch event can modify session properties. \n\nI'm considering whether to store the results as a session property that updates with each message, allowing the agent to read the latest classification on every turn. But I need to figure out where session properties are actually accessible—looking at the AGENTS.md bootstrap sequence, the session state isn't automatically loaded into context, so I'd need to explicitly read from a file or use the session:patch mechanism to make this work. I think the simplest approach is to write the classification and scoring results to a session-specific file in the workspace, then have the agent read that file during bootstrap to get the context it needs for the next turn. I need to find a simpler way to access session context. Looking at the available tools, I could store the latest message context in a session-specific file that gets updated on each interaction, allowing the agent to read the most recent classification and scoring data without needing complex context passing between turns.\n\nThe approach would be: on each `message:preprocessed` event, write the classification and score to a file keyed by session, then read that file during the agent's bootstrap phase. But the event handling model is synchronous - the hook runs before the agent processes the message, so I can't push context to the agent's bootstrap that way. I could inject the results directly into the messages array so they're available when the agent processes the incoming message.\n\nActually, I think the simplest solution is to store results in a session-keyed file and read it during bootstrap. The agent loads session context at startup, so I just need to write the hook to call the APIs and store the results, then have the agent read that file early in its initialization. The hook runs synchronously before the agent processes the message, so if I write classification and scoring results to a session-keyed file during the hook execution, those results will already be available when the agent bootstraps and reads that file in its first step.\n\nFor the immediate implementation, I'll create a hook that calls both APIs on each message and writes the results to disk, storing the most recent classification and score keyed by session. This way the agent can access the current message's classification context at startup. I'll keep the implementation straightforward for now. The hook should call the classification and scoring APIs on each message, then store those results in a session-keyed file so the agent can read them on next bootstrap. On the agent side, I need to update the bootstrap to read this classification file and inject the results into context. Since SOUL.md is loaded at startup, I can add logic there to check for recent classification data and incorporate it into the agent's context for the current turn.\n\nLooking at the timing: when a user sends message A, the hook fires and stores results keyed by that session, but the agent bootstraps after the hook completes, so it reads the results from message A's processing. For message B, it reads message B's results. This means each bootstrap cycle gets the classification from the immediately preceding message, which is actually what I need.\n\nThe tricky part is handling the first message in a session—there's no previous classification to read. I could either skip the file read on first message, or handle empty/missing files gracefully. That's manageable. The bigger architectural question is whether these classification results should live in the session context file, be injected via a hook into the agent's bootstrap phase, or something else entirely.\n\nActually, I'm overthinking this. The most straightforward approach: hook stores results in `~/.openclaw/sessions/{sessionKey}/context.json`, agent reads that file during bootstrap and includes it in context for this turn, then the agent's SOUL.md loading logic naturally picks it up since it happens during bootstrap. I should also make the hook idempotent so multiple message events don't cause issues.\n\nLet me start building this and test it works end-to-end.","thinkingSignature":"e4c3fb75259f12ba0b9486d5439707d01f17dd2f6c333fbd5c5cc2b3b676c5bf"},{"type":"text","text":"现在情况清楚了。两个 API 都正常运行：\n\n- **3104** (Scene Classifier): `POST /classify` → 返回 scene label + confidence\n- **3103** (v8 Scorer): `POST /api/score` → 返回 score + factors + strategy\n\n---\n\n**自动评分分类方案**\n\n```\n用户消息 → message:preprocessed 钩子 → 并发调用 3104 + 3103\n                                           ↓\n                                    写入 session 状态文件\n                                           ↓\n                              agent bootstrap 时读入上下文\n                                           ↓\n                              我的首轮回复就带有分类+评分结果\n```\n\n**三步走**：\n\n1. **写 Hook**：监听 `message:preprocessed`，调用双 API，写入 session 状态文件\n2. **修改 bootstrap**：session 启动时读取该状态文件，注入到当前 turn 的上下文\n3. **更新 SOUL.md**：让我在首轮回复时考虑分类/评分结果\n\n---\n\n现在开始写第一部分——Hook：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_e1dybus8q614_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p ~/.openclaw/hooks/auto-score-classify"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":28043,"output":1156,"cacheRead":17719,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46918,"cost":{"input":0.0084129,"output":0.0013871999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00106314,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01086324}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776015504082,"responseId":"062b0b8fe2a2b7740bc7c70644374828"}}
