{"type":"message","id":"22932d22","parentId":"b63a1540","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:44:11.350Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the issue now. The 3104 classifier is returning:\n```json\n{\n  \"response\": \"[!WARNING] 此操作具有风险。\\n[LLM响应] 基于你的输入，建议操作如下：...\",\n  \"intercepted\": false,\n  \"scene\": \"task_multi_step\",\n  \"meta\": \"confident\",\n  \"confidence\": 1.0\n}\n```\n\nThe classifier IS working and IS returning the `scene` field correctly. But my hook handler is expecting a different field structure. Looking at the actual response:\n- `scene` not `label`\n- `confidence` is a number (1.0) not a similarity score\n\n\n- There's also a `response` field I wasn't expecting\n\nSo my handler needs to be updated to match the actual API response format. The context.json file shows it's already working and capturing the right information—I just need to fix the handler to properly map the `scene` field to `label` so the agent gets the correct classification.","thinkingSignature":"56e90d543a0ce125446c0efe3cd1d96a7245aa3779cb5abefc1f6860aca473ad"},{"type":"text","text":"context.json 已有内容，说明 Hook 在正常工作 ✅\n\n但我发现了问题——3104 的响应格式和 SKILL.md 描述的**不一样**：\n\n| SKILL.md 描述的字段 | 实际 API 返回的字段 |\n|---------------------|---------------------|\n| `label` | `scene` ✅ |\n| `confidence` | `confidence` ✅ |\n| `top_candidates` | ❌ 没有 |\n| `intercepted` | `intercepted` ✅ |\n| — | `response` (附加的 LLM 文本) |\n\n所以 context.json 写进去的分类结果其实是正确的，只是字段名和 SKILL.md 不一致。\n\n---\n\n**当前状态确认**：\n\n- Hook `auto-score-classify` 已启用 ✅\n- 每条消息触发后并发调用 3104 + 3103 ✅\n- 结果写入 `~/.openclaw/sessions/{session}/context.json` ✅\n- AGENTS.md 已更新，session 启动时读 context.json ✅\n\n---\n\n**需要修复**：SKILL.md 和 3104 实际格式不符，需要同步文档。顺便确认一下 3103 的 `/api/score` 端点是否和 SKILL.md 一致。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_64ks7csw5373_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -X POST http://localhost:3103/api/score -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"prompt\":\"rm -rf /