{"type":"message","id":"71583d63","parentId":"0ea15145","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:44:21.129Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the 3103 scorer API response matches the SKILL.md exactly:\n- `score` ✅\n- `factors` ✅\n- `recommendedStrategy` ✅\n- `timeout` ✅\n- `_raw` ✅\n\nSo the 3103 scorer is correctly documented, but the 3104 classifier documentation is outdated.\n\nNow I need to fix the SKILL.md for v8_classifier to reflect the actual API response format. But also, the agent (me) needs to understand the actual format. \n\nActually, the key issue is that my hook writes the raw API response to context.json, and the AGENTS.md tells me to read context.json and use the `classification` and `scoring` fields. \n\nI should check what I actually receive in context so I can verify whether the hook is properly extracting and storing the classification and scoring data in the right structure.","thinkingSignature":"6dd6be27cc299f300a2ee545d47b396d95727453ab324ec5f96ab4da36e32f3e"},{"type":"text","text":"3103 格式完全正确，SKILL.md 和实际一致 ✅\n\n现在 context.json 内容如下：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"classification\": {\n    \"response\": \"[!WARNING] 此操作具有风险。\\n[LLM响应] 基于你的输入...\",\n    \"intercepted\": false,\n    \"scene\": \"task_multi_step\",      ← 实际是 scene，不是 label\n    \"meta\": \"confident\",\n    \"confidence\": 1.0\n  },\n  \"scoring\": {\n    \"score\": 24,\n    \"recommendedStrategy\": \"STEP_ARCHIVE\",  ← 格式正确\n    ...\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n**结论**：\n\n- Hook 已正常工作 ✅\n- 3104 分类器实际返回 `scene` 字段（不是 `label`）——SKILL.md 需要修正\n- 你现在发消息时，context.json 会自动更新\n\n要修复 v8_classifier 的 SKILL.md 文档吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":37071,"output":382,"cacheRead":17776,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55229,"cost":{"input":0.011121299999999999,"output":0.0004584,"cacheRead":0.0010665599999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.012646259999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776015851463,"responseId":"062b0