{"type":"message","id":"aad94346","parentId":"0fdbf291","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:44:55.886Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying \"修复 v8_classifier 的 SKILL.md 文档吗\" - they're confirming they want me to fix the v8_classifier SKILL.md. Let me update the SKILL.md to reflect the actual API response format.","thinkingSignature":"9bf19009a45cc71c9bb3e35df87e384f59880a753a1e0e6f7091ceb418cf6782"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fzxhz0yarl7v_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/skills/v8_classifier/SKILL.md","limit":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":102,"cacheRead":52812,"cacheWrite":1413,"totalTokens":54381,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0001224,"cacheRead":0.00316872,"cacheWrite":0.000529875,"total":0.003837195}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776015891273,"responseId":"062b0d1335ad40d616eeb28e789cbd83"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f90b73c7","parentId":"aad94346","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:44:55.953Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_fzxhz0yarl7v_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: v8_classifier\ndescription: OpenClaw v8 场景分类器。调用 3104 API，将用户消息分类为9种意图场景（闲聊/任务/故障/模糊等）。用于理解用户消息的底层意图，配合 v8_scorer 做路由决策。\nversion: 1.1.0\n---\n\n# v8_classifier\n\n> OpenClaw v8 场景分类器（端口 3104）\n>\n> 基于轻量多语言嵌入向量 + KNN，近距离 fallback\n\n---\n\n## 一、分类原理\n\n### 1.1 两层分类器架构\n\n**第一层：embedding 分类器**（主用）\n- 模型：`paraphrase-multilingual-MiniLM-L12-v2`（sentence-transformers，约 120MB，多语言支持）\n- 算法：KNN（3近邻，余弦距离）\n- 场景数据：`synthetic_training_data.py` 中的标注语料\n\n**第二层：规则兜底分类器**（降级）\n- 触发条件：embedding 模型加载失败、超时（>500ms）、置信度过低（similarity < 0.5）\n- 算法：正则模式匹配 + 关键词权重\n\n### 1.2 九种场景\n\n| 场景 | 说明 | 典型触发词 |\n|------|------|-----------|\n| `chitchat` | 闲聊，无任务意图 | 你好、天气、谢谢、再见 |\n| `task_multi_step` | 多步骤复杂任务 | 重构、分析、搭建、部署 |\n| `fault_recovery` | 故障诊断恢复 | 起不来、挂了、报错、崩了 |\n| `vague_request` | 意图模糊，需澄清 | 单独一个技术名词（nginx、docker） |\n| `novice_user` | 新手用户，需入门指导 | 新手、不懂、入门、教我 |\n| `expert_user` | 专家用户，需深度细节 | 底层、原理、源码、内核 |\n| `high_risk_automated` | 高风险操作，需二次确认 | rm -rf、chmod、删除文件 |\n| `task_status_query` | 任务状态查询 | 任务完成了吗、进度、状态 |\n| `cancel_task` | 取消任务 | 取消、停止、终止任务 |\n\n### 1.3 置信度判定\n\n> 置信度 = 1 - cosine_distance，即与最近邻的相似度（0-1，1 表示完全匹配）\n\n| 条件 | 分类结果 |\n|------|----------|\n| top1 相似度 < 0.5 | `low_confidence` → 触发 fallback 或澄清流程 |\n| top1 - top2 相似度差 < 0.1 | `ambiguous` → 需用户澄清 |\n| 否则 | `confident` → 直接返回场景标签 |\n\n---\n\n## 二、API 规范\n\n### 2.1 分类接口\n\n**端点**\n```\nPOST http://127.0.0.1:3104/classify\n\n[213 more lines in file. Use offset=61 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776015895944}}
{"type":"message","id":"983257df","parentId":"f90b73c7","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:44:59.043Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to see the rest of the SKILL.md, especially section 2 (API 规范) and section 4 (分类示例) to update the field names from `label` to `scene`.","thinkingSignature":"2862165a3ef77ac411aa7028f4c83abcb3c52ea69edbd19438a678787ecce877"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9656hs5ygai9_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/skills/v8_classifier/SKILL.md","offset":61,"limit":80}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":37262,"output":104,"cacheRead":17776,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55142,"cost":{"input":0.0111786,"output":0.0001248,"cacheRead":0.0010665599999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01236996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776015895955,"responseId":"062b0d185d688f00f677525e04e687d1"}}
{"type":"message","id":"bf55e07d","parentId":"983257df","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:44:59.110Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_9656hs5ygai9_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Content-Type: application/json\n```\n\n**请求**\n```json\n{\n  \"text\": \"<用户消息文本>\"\n}\n```\n\n**响应**\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"task_multi_step\",\n  \"confidence\": 0.73,\n  \"meta\": \"confident\",\n  \"top_candidates\": [\n    [\"task_multi_step\", 0.73],\n    [\"fault_recovery\", 0.21]\n  ],\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n### 2.2 响应字段说明\n\n| 字段 | 类型 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `label` | string\\|null | 场景标签，`null` 表示置信度过低 |\n| `confidence` | float | top1 相似度 (0-1)，1 表示完全匹配 |\n| `meta` | string | `confident` / `low_confidence` / `ambiguous` |\n| `top_candidates` | array | 前2个候选场景及相似度 |\n| `intercepted` | boolean | 是否被硬拦截（触发高风险规则） |\n\n### 2.3 降级响应示例\n\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": null,\n  \"confidence\": 0.35,\n  \"meta\": \"low_confidence\",\n  \"top_candidates\": [\n    [\"vague_request\", 0.35],\n    [\"chitchat\", 0.28]\n  ],\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n当 `meta` 为 `low_confidence` 或 `ambiguous` 时，应触发意图澄清流程。\n\n---\n\n## 三、意图澄清模板\n\n当分类置信度不足时，根据 `top_candidates` 动态生成选项请求用户澄清：\n\n**模板**\n```\n你的问题比较模糊，请确认你想要：\n1. [top1 场景的典型操作描述]\n2. [top2 场景的典型操作描述]\n3. 其他\n\n例如：请说\"帮我 [具体操作] [具体目标]\"\n```\n\n**示例**\n- `top_candidates: [[\"task_multi_step\", 0.45], [\"fault_recovery\", 0.38]]`\n- 输出选项：1. 执行一个多步骤任务（如重构、部署）2. 排查和恢复故障\n\n---\n\n## 四、分类示例\n\n### 示例 1：多步骤任务\n\n**输入**：`\"重构这个项目的用户认证模块\"`\n\n```json\n\n[133 more lines in file. Use offset=141 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776015899101}}
