{"type":"message","id":"f43fff33","parentId":"cb613e1e","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:45:18.557Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have enough context. The actual API response is:\n```json\n{\n  \"response\": \"[LLM响应] 基于你的输入...\",\n  \"intercepted\": false,\n  \"scene\": \"clarify\",        // actual field name is \"scene\", not \"label\"\n  \"meta\": \"low_confidence\",\n  \"confidence\": 0\n}\n```\n\nThe key discrepancies:\n1. `\"label\"` → `\"scene\"` in actual response\n2. `\"top_candidates\"` field is missing in actual response\n3. `\"response\"` field exists in actual response (LLM text description)\n4. The response appears to be from a rule-based classifier that returns a simple format\n\n\n5. I need to update the documentation to reflect these actual field names and structure\n\nNow I'm making the edits to the SKILL.md file to align it with what the API actually returns.","thinkingSignature":"7fa8758de891aaf2c8ec5547db78bc0fc2805123f38c56f6aa9defcce7eaa5d3"},{"type":"text","text":"看到了，实际 API 返回的是 `scene` 而非 `label`，且缺少 `top_candidates`，多了一个 `response` 字段。开始修正：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_026xveym9st6_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/skills/v8_classifier/SKILL.md","edits":[{"oldText":"**响应**\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"task_multi_step\",\n  \"confidence\": 0.73,\n  \"meta\": \"confident\",\n  \"top_candidates\": [\n    [\"task_multi_step\", 0.73],\n    [\"fault_recovery\", 0.21]\n  ],\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n### 2.2 响应字段说明\n\n| 字段 | 类型 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `label` | string|null | 场景标签，`null` 表示置信度过低 |\n| `confidence` | float | top1 相似度 (0-1)，1 表示完全匹配 |\n| `meta` | string | `confident` / `low_confidence` / `ambiguous` |\n| `top_candidates` | array | 前2个候选场景及相似度 |\n| `intercepted` | boolean | 是否被硬拦截（触发高风险规则） |","newText":"**响应**\n```json\n{\n  \"scene\": \"task_multi_step\",\n  \"confidence\": 0.73,\n  \"meta\": \"confident\",\n  \"intercepted\": false,\n  \"response\": \"[LLM响应] 基于你的输入，建议操作如下：...\"\n}\n```\n\n### 2.2 响应字段说明\n\n| 字段 | 类型 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `scene` | string|null | 场景标签，`null` 表示置信度过低 |\n| `confidence` | float | 相似度 (0-1)，1 表示完全匹配 |\n| `meta` | string | `confident` / `low_confidence` / `ambiguous` |\n| `intercepted` | boolean | 是否被硬拦截（触发高风险规则） |\n| `response` | string | 附加的 LLM 文本描述（可选） |"},{"oldText":"### 2.3 降级响应示例\n\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": null,\n  \"confidence\": 0.35,\n  \"meta\": \"low_confidence\",\n  \"top_candidates\": [\n    [\"vague_request\", 0.35],\n    [\"chitchat\", 0.28]\n  ],\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n当 `meta` 为 `low_confidence` 或 `ambiguous` 时，应触发意图澄清流程。","newText":"### 2.3 降级响应示例\n\n```json\n{\n  \"scene\": null,\n  \"confidence\": 0.0,\n  \"meta\": \"low_confidence\",\n  \"intercepted\": false,\n  \"response\": \"[LLM响应] 基于你的输入，建议操作如下：...\"\n}\n```\n\n当 `meta` 为 `low_confidence` 或 `ambiguous` 时，应触发意图澄清流程。"},{"oldText":"当分类置信度不足时，根据 `top_candidates` 动态生成选项请求用户澄清：\n\n**模板**\n```\n你的问题比较模糊，请确认你想要：\n1. [top1 场景的典型操作描述]\n2. [top2 场景的典型操作描述]\n3. 其他\n\n例如：请说\"帮我 [具体操作] [具体目标]\"\n```\n\n**示例**\n- `top_candidates: [[\"task_multi_step\", 0.45], [\"fault_recovery\", 0.38]]`\n- 输出选项：1. 执行一个多步骤任务（如重构、部署）2. 排查和恢复故障","newText":"当分类置信度不足时，动态生成选项请求用户澄清：\n\n**模板**\n```\n你的问题比较模糊，请确认你想要：\n1. [场景1的典型操作描述]\n2. [场景2的典型操作描述]\n3. 其他\n\n例如：请说\"帮我 [具体操作] [具体目标]\"\n```"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":38424,"output":1177,"cacheRead":17776,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57377,"cost":{"input":0.0115272,"output":0.0014123999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0010665599999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.014006159999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776015902534,"responseId":"062b0d1e622261ca5feaa28e9f9a7d4f"}}
