{"type":"message","id":"59a80c70","parentId":"9bea1937","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:47:54.261Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting! \"重构项目代码\" returns `task_multi_step` with confidence 1.0, which is correct. But \"帮我搭建一个docker环境\" returns `clarify` with confidence 0.0. Let me try more test cases to understand the pattern.\n\nThe issue might be that \"帮我搭建一个docker环境\" contains mixed intent - it could be interpreted as a request for setup guidance (like novice_user) or a task (task_multi_step). The \"clarify\" scene might be a fallback when the classifier can't confidently decide.\n\nLet me check if the issue is with this specific phrase.","thinkingSignature":"18b85b1844c6cd87f8dab0e5d2909c70a0c1cd28fb44ae027bb82e43af1f9466"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wli8mipzh2zp_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"for text in \"搭建docker环境\" \"docker环境搭建\" \"教我用docker\" \"安装docker\"; do\n  echo \"--- $text ---\"\n  curl -s -X POST http://localhost:3104/classify -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d \"{\\\"text\\\":\\\"$text\\\"}\" 2>/dev/null\n  echo \"\"\ndone","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":46525,"output":235,"cacheRead":17776,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64536,"cost":{"input":0.0139575,"output":0.00028199999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0010665599999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.015306059999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776016067748,"responseId":"062b0dc34d797c22d3f88de4295790ef"}}
