{"type":"message","id":"38f65d50","parentId":"eae2588b","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:49:33.588Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about switching to a different model for the classifier. Let me think about this option.\n\nThe current classifier uses `paraphrase-multilingual-MiniLM-L12-v2` which is a ~120MB multilingual model. It's a lighter model optimized for speed. For Chinese, it might not be the best.\n\nOptions:\n1. Switch to a better multilingual model (like paraphrase-multilingual-mpnet-base-v2 which is larger and more accurate)\n2. Switch to a Chinese-specific model\n3. Switch to an embedding model that's known to be better for Chinese (like text2vec-base-chinese or m3e)\n\n\n4. Upgrade to a larger MiniLM variant like paraphrase-multilingual-MiniLM-L12-v2 which offers better performance than the current version, or switch to m3e-base which is specifically optimized for Chinese tasks and available through Ollama or Hugging Face.","thinkingSignature":"9f25e3b0926c530ff32e4ffc2d7c3a40e13c6264186a3d9306c7ca267bf09d78"},{"type":"text","text":"可以换。看看当前用的是什么，再选替代方案：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ev4fkjof2ek7_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /home/ai/openclaw-classifier -name \"*.py\" 2>/dev/null | xargs grep -l \"paraphrase\\|MiniLM\\|model_name\\|sentence-transformers\" 2>/dev/null | head -5","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":280,"cacheRead":63669,"cacheWrite":943,"totalTokens":64946,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.000336,"cacheRead":0.0038201399999999996,"cacheWrite":0.000353625,"total":0.004525965}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776016165699,"responseId":"062b0e25b8914ac99849ca07a8912ae3"}}
