{"type":"message","id":"b6a6ca6f","parentId":"2b778a81","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:49:50.030Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_fhab1w5w2r8i_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"51 /home/ai/openclaw-classifier/python-service/data/synthetic_training_data.py\n#!/usr/bin/env python3\nSCENE_DEFINITIONS = {\n    \"task_multi_step\": {\n        \"positive_examples\": [\n            \"帮我分析这个项目的代码质量\",\n            \"重构 src 目录下所有文件\",\n            \"搭建一个完整的 React 项目\",\n            \"扫描整个仓库找出安全问题\",\n            \"批量重命名所有图片并按日期分类\",\n        ]\n    },\n    \"fault_recovery\": {\n        \"positive_examples\": [\n            \"服务器起不来了\",\n            \"kill -9 杀了进程后服务启动失败\",\n            \"改了 nginx 配置后网站打不开了\",\n            \"数据库迁移跑了一半失败了怎么办\",\n        ]\n    },\n    \"vague_request\": {\n        \"positive_examples\": [\"nginx\", \"Docker\", \"Python\", \"数据库\", \"帮我看看\"]\n    },\n    \"expert_user\": {\n        \"positive_examples\": [\n            \"nginx stream 模块怎么实现 TCP 负载均衡\",\n            \"Redis 集群的槽位重分片原理\",\n            \"epoll 和 select 的区别\",\n        ]\n    },\n    \"novice_user\": {\n        \"positive_examples\": [\"我是新手，怎么安装 Python\", \"完全不懂 Linux，怎么入门\", \"第一次用 Docker\"]\n    },\n    \"task_status_query\": {\n        \"positive_examples\": [\"任务 abc123 怎么样了\", \"刚才那个任务完成了吗\", \"进度多少了\"]\n    },\n    \"cancel_task\": {\n        \"positive_examples\": [\"取消任务 abc123\", \"别跑了，停掉它\"]\n    },\n    \"high_risk_automated\": {\n        \"positive_examples\": [\"帮我清理 /tmp 下超过 7 天的文件\", \"批量修改所有 .conf 文件的权限为 644\"]\n    },\n    \"chitchat\": {\n        \"positive_examples\": [\"今天天气怎么样\", \"你好\", \"谢谢\", \"讲个笑话\"]\n    },\n}\n\ndef generate_training_data():\n    data = []\n    for label, info in SCENE_DEFINITIONS.items():\n        for example in info[\"positive_examples\"]:\n            data.append((example, label))\n    return data"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":45,"aggregated":"51 /home/ai/openclaw-classifier/python-service/data/synthetic_training_data.py\n#!/usr/bin/env python3\nSCENE_DEFINITIONS = {\n    \"task_multi_step\": {\n        \"positive_examples\": [\n            \"帮我分析这个项目的代码质量\",\n            \"重构 src 目录下所有文件\",\n            \"搭建一个完整的 React 项目\",\n            \"扫描整个仓库找出安全问题\",\n            \"批量重命名所有图片并按日期分类\",\n        ]\n    },\n    \"fault_recovery\": {\n        \"positive_examples\": [\n            \"服务器起不来了\",\n            \"kill -9 杀了进程后服务启动失败\",\n            \"改了 nginx 配置后网站打不开了\",\n            \"数据库迁移跑了一半失败了怎么办\",\n        ]\n    },\n    \"vague_request\": {\n        \"positive_examples\": [\"nginx\", \"Docker\", \"Python\", \"数据库\", \"帮我看看\"]\n    },\n    \"expert_user\": {\n        \"positive_examples\": [\n            \"nginx stream 模块怎么实现 TCP 负载均衡\",\n            \"Redis 集群的槽位重分片原理\",\n            \"epoll 和 select 的区别\",\n        ]\n    },\n    \"novice_user\": {\n        \"positive_examples\": [\"我是新手，怎么安装 Python\", \"完全不懂 Linux，怎么入门\", \"第一次用 Docker\"]\n    },\n    \"task_status_query\": {\n        \"positive_examples\": [\"任务 abc123 怎么样了\", \"刚才那个任务完成了吗\", \"进度多少了\"]\n    },\n    \"cancel_task\": {\n        \"positive_examples\": [\"取消任务 abc123\", \"别跑了，停掉它\"]\n    },\n    \"high_risk_automated\": {\n        \"positive_examples\": [\"帮我清理 /tmp 下超过 7 天的文件\", \"批量修改所有 .conf 文件的权限为 644\"]\n    },\n    \"chitchat\": {\n        \"positive_examples\": [\"今天天气怎么样\", \"你好\", \"谢谢\", \"讲个笑话\"]\n    },\n}\n\ndef generate_training_data():\n    data = []\n    for label, info in SCENE_DEFINITIONS.items():\n        for example in info[\"positive_examples\"]:\n            data.append((example, label))\n    return data","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776016190020}}
{"type":"message","id":"e6e6808b","parentId":"b6a6ca6f","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:50:02.822Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see the full picture. The training data for `task_multi_step` includes \"搭建一个完整的 React 项目\" which is a \"搭建\" example. So \"搭建docker环境\" should be similar to \"搭建一个完整的 React 项目\". The fact that it's returning `clarify` is puzzling.\n\nThe problem might be that:\n1. The model's embedding quality for Chinese is limited\n2. \"docker环境\" might not be well-represented in the training data\n3. There might be a mismatch between training and inference\n\nThe best fix would be to:\n1. Add more \"搭建\" examples to the training data for `task_multi_step`\n\n\n2. Switch to a stronger model like `paraphrase-multilingual-mpnet-base-v2` which has 768 dimensions instead of 384, giving better embedding quality while staying compatible with the same API\n3. Or use a Chinese-specific model like `text2vec-base-chinese` or `m3e-base` if multilingual support isn't needed\n\nI'm leaning toward `paraphrase-multilingual-mpnet-base-v2` as the safest option since it doesn't require retraining—just swap the model name. But let me check what models are actually available first.","thinkingSignature":"0902f8c9d2557a867ab95eb2e433d352bbe2cd5a96f43f9f62f7581afaad41ad"},{"type":"text","text":"现在情况清楚了。\n\n**训练数据**：`task_multi_step` 有\"搭建一个完整的 React 项目\"，但没有\"搭建docker环境\"——这是数据覆盖不足。\n\n**模型选择**：\n\n| 方案 | 模型 | 维度 | 改动 |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| A | `paraphrase-multilingual-mpnet-base-v2` | 768 | 直接换，相同 API，更强 |\n| B | `text2vec-base-chinese` | 768 | 中文专用，需要 retrain |\n| C | 补充训练数据 + 保持现有模型 | — | 加\"搭建docker\"类例子 |\n\n**我的建议**：\n\n- **先走 A**（换模型，不 retrain，收益明显）\n- **同时走 C**（补充训练数据，让\"搭建/安装\"类短句被覆盖）\n\nA+C 双管齐下，效果最好。\n\n要开始换模型吗？下载 `mpnet-base-v2` 大概 1-2 分钟。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":48374,"output":458,"cacheRead":17776,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66608,"cost":{"input":0.0145122,"output":0.0005496,"cacheRead":0.0010665599999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01612836}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776016190032,"responseId":"062b0e3eeab01fde0d6a3eaaf6deb999"}}
