{"type":"message","id":"37b630d0","parentId":"497a4a7b","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:51:12.851Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The models directory is inside `python-service/`. Now I understand the full picture:1. Model file: `/home/ai/openclaw-classifier/python-service/models/scene_classifier.pkl`\n2. Classifier code: `/home/ai/openclaw-classifier/python-service/classifier/scene_classifier.py`\n3. Training data: `/home/ai/openclaw-classifier/python-service/data/synthetic_training_data.py`\n\nTo change the model, I need to:1. Update `model_name` in `scene_classifier.py`\n2. Write a script to retrain (re-embed) with the new model and save to the pkl file3. \n\nRestart the 3104 service by killing and restarting the Flask app. I should also expand the training data with more Chinese examples to improve coverage, then verify the service setup by checking how the pt_main_thread process on port 3104 connects to the Flask app running on port 5000.","thinkingSignature":"b356ccea49c9434c04fe6882b9fdd5330d2e404dfb7bf120ef0c7ffa9c0f1c71"},{"type":"text","text":"模型在 `/home/ai/openclaw-classifier/python-service/models/scene_classifier.pkl`。需要重新 embed。\n\n两步走：\n\n**Step 1**：更新模型名称 + 补充中文训练数据\n**Step 2**：重新训练 embeddings + 重启 3104\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_mj0d5o1p0u8o_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/skills/v8_classifier/SKILL.md","edits":[{"oldText":"        self.model_name = \"paraphrase-multilingual-MiniLM-L12-v2\"","newText":"        self.model_name = \"paraphrase-multilingual-mpnet-base-v2\""}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":50301,"output":353,"cacheRead":17776,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68430,"cost":{"input":0.0150903,"output":0.0004236,"cacheRead":0.0010665599999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.016580459999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776016265436,"responseId":"062b0e88b03ca2545677b98c6606b730"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d26be076","parentId":"37b630d0","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:51:12.918Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_mj0d5o1p0u8o_1","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"edit\",\n  \"error\": \"Could not find the exact text in /home/ai/.openclaw/skills/v8_classifier/SKILL.md. The old text must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines.\\nCurrent file contents:\\n---\\nname: v8_classifier\\ndescription: OpenClaw v8 场景分类器。调用 3104 API，将用户消息分类为9种意图场景（闲聊/任务/故障/模糊等）。用于理解用户消息的底层意图，配合 v8_scorer 做路由决策。\\nversion: 1.2.0\\n---\\n\\n# v8_classifier\\n\\n> OpenClaw v8 场景分类器（端口 3104）\\n>\\n> 基于轻量多语言嵌入向量 + KNN，近距离 fallback\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 一、分类原理\\n\\n### 1.1 两层分类器架构\\n\\n**第一层：embedding 分类器**（主用）\\n- 模型：`paraphrase-multilingual-MiniLM-L12-v2`（sentence-transformers，约 120MB，多语言支持）\\n- 算法：KNN（3近邻，余弦距离）\\n- 场景数据：`synthetic_training_data.py` 中的标注语料\\n\\n**第二层：规则兜底分类器**（降级）\\n- 触发条件：embedding 模型加载失败、超时（>500ms）、置信度过低（similarity < 0.5）\\n- 算法：正则模式匹配 + 关键词权重\\n\\n### 1.2 九种场景\\n\\n| 场景 | 说明 | 典型触发词 |\\n|------|------|-----------|\\n| `chitchat` | 闲聊，无任务意图 | 你好、天气、谢谢、再见 |\\n| `task_multi_step` | 多步骤复杂任务 | 重构、分析、搭建、部署 |\\n| `fault_recovery` | 故障诊断恢复 | 起不来、挂了、报错、崩了 |\\n| `vague_request` | 意图模糊，需澄清 | 单独一个技术名词（nginx、docker） |\\n| `novice_user`\\n... (truncated)\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"edit","error":"Could not find the exact text in /home/ai/.openclaw/skills/v8_classifier/SKILL.md. The old text must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines.\nCurrent file contents:\n---\nname: v8_classifier\ndescription: OpenClaw v8 场景分类器。调用 3104 API，将用户消息分类为9种意图场景（闲聊/任务/故障/模糊等）。用于理解用户消息的底层意图，配合 v8_scorer 做路由决策。\nversion: 1.2.0\n---\n\n# v8_classifier\n\n> OpenClaw v8 场景分类器（端口 3104）\n>\n> 基于轻量多语言嵌入向量 + KNN，近距离 fallback\n\n---\n\n## 一、分类原理\n\n### 1.1 两层分类器架构\n\n**第一层：embedding 分类器**（主用）\n- 模型：`paraphrase-multilingual-MiniLM-L12-v2`（sentence-transformers，约 120MB，多语言支持）\n- 算法：KNN（3近邻，余弦距离）\n- 场景数据：`synthetic_training_data.py` 中的标注语料\n\n**第二层：规则兜底分类器**（降级）\n- 触发条件：embedding 模型加载失败、超时（>500ms）、置信度过低（similarity < 0.5）\n- 算法：正则模式匹配 + 关键词权重\n\n### 1.2 九种场景\n\n| 场景 | 说明 | 典型触发词 |\n|------|------|-----------|\n| `chitchat` | 闲聊，无任务意图 | 你好、天气、谢谢、再见 |\n| `task_multi_step` | 多步骤复杂任务 | 重构、分析、搭建、部署 |\n| `fault_recovery` | 故障诊断恢复 | 起不来、挂了、报错、崩了 |\n| `vague_request` | 意图模糊，需澄清 | 单独一个技术名词（nginx、docker） |\n| `novice_user`\n... (truncated)"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776016272909}}
