{"type":"message","id":"7c9335f4","parentId":"5b43a0f7","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:52:13.101Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Wait, it only used 31 samples? That's because the training data only has 31 samples total. And it's using the OLD model since the SceneClassifier was already imported before we changed the file... wait, no - I changed the file on disk and then ran the script, so it should use the new model. But the output says \"Batches: 100%|██████████| 1/1 [00:00<?it/s]\" which is very fast for mpnet-base-v2. Let me verify the model was actually downloaded and used.\n\nActually, `paraphrase-multilingual-mpnet-base-v2` is a bigger model (768 dimensions vs 384 for MiniLM). \n\nThe download probably completed quickly since the models are cached. Let me verify it's actually using the new model by testing a query.","thinkingSignature":"5f78f3d42477268957d5a3e9270ce06317f88a87e9dd8bc19d1b1739a95bd987"},{"type":"text","text":"embed 完成，验证一下新模型效果：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wb7ngzsqfmoa_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/ai/openclaw-classifier/python-service && python3 -c \"\nimport os\nos.environ['HF_ENDPOINT'] = 'https://hf-mirror.com'\nfrom classifier.scene_classifier import SceneClassifier\n\nclf = SceneClassifier.load('models/scene_classifier.pkl')\nprint('Model:', clf.model_name)\n\ntests = ['搭建docker环境', 'docker环境搭建', '安装docker', '教我用docker', '重构项目代码', '服务器挂了']\nfor t in tests:\n    r = clf.predict(t)\n    print(f'{t:20} -> {r[\\\"label\\\"]} ({r[\\\"confidence\\\"]:.2f})')\n\" 2>&1","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":52108,"output":353,"cacheRead":17776,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70237,"cost":{"input":0.015632399999999998,"output":0.0004236,"cacheRead":0.0010665599999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01712256}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776016324519,"responseId":"062b0ec3c41e3e02712ae923fad3df9f"}}
