{"type":"message","id":"10c11921","parentId":"fac456b6","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:52:31.497Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Hmm, the results are mixed:- \"docker环境搭建\" -> vague_request (0.87) ✅\n- \"服务器挂了\" -> fault_recovery (0.87) ✅\n- \"重构项目代码\" -> task_multi_step (0.71) ✅\n\nBut:\n- \"搭建docker环境\" -> None (0.77) ❌ (should be task_multi_step)- \"安装docker\" -> None (0.73) ❌ (should be task_multi_step)\n- \"教我用docker\" -> None (0.72) ❌ (should be novice_user)\n\nThe model is better (higher confidence overall) but still doesn't perfectly classify the \"搭建/安装\" patterns. \n\nThe real issue is that the training data only has 31 samples across 9 classes—that's roughly 3-4 examples per class, which is too sparse to capture the full range of patterns. I need to expand the training set significantly, especially for task_multi_step where I should add examples like \"搭建docker环境\" and \"安装docker\".\n\nFor the other classes, I should also beef up their coverage: novice_user needs more diverse examples like \"docker入门\" and \"怎么学docker\", while vague_request examples like \"docker\" and \"nginx\" are already solid anchors since they're deliberately vague. Let me expand the training data with these additions.","thinkingSignature":"a0550d9ccd5897abb9643c73216025c6518caa4d32d2ef70299e50a991b36e1a"},{"type":"text","text":"模型已更新，但训练数据太少（31条 / 9类），\"搭建/安装\"类覆盖不足。先扩充训练数据再重新 embed：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7ygh9i0wmd1y_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/ai/openclaw-classifier/python-service/data/synthetic_training_data.py","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":52557,"output":357,"cacheRead":17776,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70690,"cost":{"input":0.0157671,"output":0.0004284,"cacheRead":0.0010665599999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01726206}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776016342299,"responseId":"062b0ed5dad06f168d5fcb047778d00f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a9232bf3","parentId":"10c11921","timestamp":"2026-04-12T17:52:31.623Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_7ygh9i0wmd1y_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\nSCENE_DEFINITIONS = {\n    \"task_multi_step\": {\n        \"positive_examples\": [\n            \"帮我分析这个项目的代码质量\",\n            \"重构 src 目录下所有文件\",\n            \"搭建一个完整的 React 项目\",\n            \"扫描整个仓库找出安全问题\",\n            \"批量重命名所有图片并按日期分类\",\n        ]\n    },\n    \"fault_recovery\": {\n        \"positive_examples\": [\n            \"服务器起不来了\",\n            \"kill -9 杀了进程后服务启动失败\",\n            \"改了 nginx 配置后网站打不开了\",\n            \"数据库迁移跑了一半失败了怎么办\",\n        ]\n    },\n    \"vague_request\": {\n        \"positive_examples\": [\"nginx\", \"Docker\", \"Python\", \"数据库\", \"帮我看看\"]\n    },\n    \"expert_user\": {\n        \"positive_examples\": [\n            \"nginx stream 模块怎么实现 TCP 负载均衡\",\n            \"Redis 集群的槽位重分片原理\",\n            \"epoll 和 select 的区别\",\n        ]\n    },\n    \"novice_user\": {\n        \"positive_examples\": [\"我是新手，怎么安装 Python\", \"完全不懂 Linux，怎么入门\", \"第一次用 Docker\"]\n    },\n    \"task_status_query\": {\n        \"positive_examples\": [\"任务 abc123 怎么样了\", \"刚才那个任务完成了吗\", \"进度多少了\"]\n    },\n    \"cancel_task\": {\n        \"positive_examples\": [\"取消任务 abc123\", \"别跑了，停掉它\"]\n    },\n    \"high_risk_automated\": {\n        \"positive_examples\": [\"帮我清理 /tmp 下超过 7 天的文件\", \"批量修改所有 .conf 文件的权限为 644\"]\n    },\n    \"chitchat\": {\n        \"positive_examples\": [\"今天天气怎么样\", \"你好\", \"谢谢\", \"讲个笑话\"]\n    },\n}\n\ndef generate_training_data():\n    data = []\n    for label, info in SCENE_DEFINITIONS.items():\n        for example in info[\"positive_examples\"]:\n            data.append((example, label))\n    return data"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":71,"aggregated":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\nSCENE_DEFINITIONS = {\n    \"task_multi_step\": {\n        \"positive_