{"type":"message","id":"02d5c301","parentId":"fa9f9ebe","timestamp":"2026-04-12T18:04:27.209Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_kpyr6cus7f1x_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- Python 分类服务：`/home/ai/openclaw-classifier/python-service/`\n- 向量分类器：`classifier/scene_classifier.py`\n- 规则兜底：`classifier/rule_classifier.py`\n- Flask API：`app.py`（端口 3104）\n- 启动脚本：`python-service/start.sh`\n- 场景训练数据：`classifier/data/synthetic_training_data.py`\n\n---\n\n## 八、相关文档\n\n- [[v8_scorer]] - 任务复杂度评分器（端口 3103）\n- [[task_orchestrator]] - 任务编排器（整合评分+分类+路由）\n- [[scene-classifier]] - workspace 版场景分类器（相同实现）\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776017067200}}
