{"type":"message","id":"1eace98f","parentId":"4bbce41f","timestamp":"2026-04-12T18:07:34.237Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. The AGENTS.md has the context.json rule. Now let me report to the user on the status of the LLM Wiki plan.\n\nFrom the conversation summary, the LLM Wiki plan was:\n- Step 1: Fix session memory loading (AGENTS.md updated, SOUL.md old content still there but the critical rule is in AGENTS.md)\n- Step 2: 建立 Ingest 流程（cron 驱动）— NOT DONE\n- Step 3: 建立 Lint 流程（心跳驱动）— NOT DONE  \n- Step 4: 建立 Query 入口 — NOT DONE\n\nAnd for the memory system:\n- self-improving skill: active\n\n\n- proactivity skill: active\n- LLM Wiki: entities/ has 25 files, docs/ is empty, ingest/lint/query not automated yet\n\nSo I need to clarify with the user what they actually want to tackle first—the cron jobs for ingestion and linting, or the query system—since the foundational pieces are already in place.","thinkingSignature":"efdf98e26d616964d31a4fe64e27a565269e7d5e924f8ec6db758766c674f10c"},{"type":"text","text":"有的。LLM Wiki 方案分三步走，现状如下：\n\n---\n\n**第一步：修复 session 记忆断层**\n- ✅ AGENTS.md 已更新：session 启动时读 `context.json`\n- ✅ `context.json` 注入已生效\n\n**第二步：LLM Wiki Ingest + Lint 全自动**\n- ❌ 未做 — 需要配置 cron 任务\n\n**第三步：Query 入口**\n- ❌ 未做 — 触发机制未定义\n\n---\n\n**当前记忆系统全貌**\n\n| 组件 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| `memory/` 日志 | 有（到 4/11，4/12 刚补）|\n| `MEMORY.md` 长期记忆 | 有 |\n| `self-improving/` | ✅ 激活中 |\n| `proactivity/` | ✅ 激活中 |\n| LLM Wiki `entities/` | ✅ 25个实体页 |\n| `docs/`（原始文档池）| ❌ 空 — Ingest 无内容可处理 |\n| Ingest cron | ❌ 未配置 |\n| Lint cron | ❌ 未配置 |\n\n---\n\n**结论**：第一步框架有了，第二步需要建 `docs/` + 配 cron，第三步需要定义 Query 触发规则。\n\n你想先建 `docs/` 目录然后配 Ingest cron，还是先定义 Query 入口？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":74656,"output":491,"cacheRead":17776,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92923,"cost":{"input":0.022396799999999998,"output":0.0005892,"cacheRead":0.0010665599999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0