{"type":"message","id":"172613b2","parentId":"b5ec8a9c","timestamp":"2026-04-12T18:08:31.275Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to think about the overall architecture before deciding on the next steps. Let me think about the complete picture of what we have and what we're building.\n\nCurrent state:\n1. Memory system: memory/ daily logs + MEMORY.md long-term + self-improving + proactivity\n2. LLM Wiki: entities/ with 25 entity pages, docs/ is empty, no cron configured\n3. Session continuity: context.json injection via hook\n4. Classifier + scorer: 3104/3103 running, hooked into message flow\n\nThe user wants: memory + context + LLM Wiki integration\n\nLet me think about what \"memory and context\" actually means in this system:\n\n\n- Session continuity through context.json and session startup loading\n- LLM Wiki as a persistent knowledge base beyond individual sessions\n- Structured memory with tiered retention\n\nThe core issue is that while context.json is being written and loaded at session startup, the session itself is still losing continuity—the compiled conversation summary and memory/ logs aren't being read on startup, so the agent doesn't have access to what happened in previous sessions. The LLM Wiki layer is separate from this immediate problem.\n\nLooking at what the user actually asked for: memory (long-term storage), context (cross-session continuity), and LLM (knowledge compilation)—the LLM Wiki architecture is already designed to handle all three, but the Ingest and Query mechanisms that make it functional haven't been built yet. I should think through what the complete system should look like once these are implemented.\n\nThe core issue is that context.json captures per-message metadata like classification and scoring, but it doesn't preserve the actual conversational context or learnings from each session. To fix the session continuity problem, I need the bootstrap process to read both memory files and the compiled session summary from the previous session. For the LLM Wiki to work as intended, I need to set up the ingestion pipeline (detecting new documents and triggering knowledge extraction), the query interface (knowing when to search the wiki), and a linting process for maintenance.\n\nBut stepping back—the user is asking if I remember the LLM Wiki plan at all. They do want it, but they're uncertain about the implementation details. Rather than jumping into technical specifics, I should reflect on the higher-level strategy: what's actually broken in the current system, what each component (memory, context, LLM Wiki) contributes, and whether this layered approach is the right path forward.","thinkingSignature":"62fbbfe8acf7b4831c327bf43132791acdbe6dd73ed0c0aa604f702e2531160d"},{"type":"text","text":"好，让我完整梳理一下现状，思考清楚再行动。\n\n---\n\n**核心问题诊断**\n\n```\n症状：每次新 session 我是白纸，没有上下文\n根因：bootstrap 加载机制不完整\n```\n\n---\n\n**三层记忆架构**\n\n| 层 | 做什么 | 当前状态 |\n|---|---|---|\n| **Session Context** | 每条消息的即时分析（分类+评分）| ✅ context.json 在写 |\n| **Session Memory** | 跨 session 的对话摘要 | ❌ 没有自动写入/读取 |\n| **Long-term Memory** | 结构化知识沉淀 | LLM Wiki entities/ ✅，docs/ ❌ |\n\n---\n\n**Session Memory 缺失的根本原因**\n\n```\n旧的：session-memory hook 只在 /new 和 /reset 时保存\n现在：context.json 记录的是每条消息的分类评分，不是对话摘要\n缺失：session 结束时没有生成\"这轮对话讲了什么\"写入 memory/\n```\n\n---\n\n**重新思考后的最优路径**\n\n```\n第一步（现在）：让 session-memory hook 在每次 session 结束时\n             自动生成摘要写入 memory/YYYY-MM-DD-slug.md\n             同时 bootstrap 时读取最新一条\n\n第二步：LLM Wiki docs/ + Ingest/Query/Lint 流程\n\n第三步：把 session-memory 的摘要 + LLM Wiki entities/ 打通\n        让 session 摘要里的关键决策自动沉淀到 entities/\n```\n\n---\n\n**现在真正的问题**：\n\n不是\"LLM Wiki 还没配置\"，而是**Session Memory 没有闭环**——context.json 只记录了元数据，没有记录\"对话里学到了什么\"。\n\n---\n\n**建议**：先补 Session Memory 闭环（第一步），再做 LLM Wiki（第二步）。\n\n同意这个顺序吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":20,"output":846,"cacheRead":92497,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93363,"cost":{"input":0.000006,"output":0.0010152,"cacheRead":0.00554982,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0065710199999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776017282996,"responseId":"062b1283abfc320581e77a868a830d43"}}
