{"type":"message","id":"f3814e10","parentId":"10020376","timestamp":"2026-04-12T18:09:43.675Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking whether the LLM (Large Language Model) capabilities have been improved. Let me check the current state of things related to LLM:\n\n1. The v8_classifier and v8_scorer are running\n2. The context injection via context.json is set up\n3. But the user is asking about \"LLM\" capabilities specifically\n\nLooking at the conversation history, earlier there was discussion about:\n- Memory and context systems\n- LLM Wiki system (which is about knowledge management)\n\nThe user seems to be asking: \"Is the LLM part improved/integrated?\" \n\nWhat does \"LLM\" refer to in this context? Looking at the overall architecture:\n\n\n- There's a context API (3106) running\n- There's a v8 router/proxy (3102)\n- There's a v8_scorer (3103)\n- There's a v8_classifier (3104)\n- There's a scene-classifier (3105)\n- There's a context-api (3106)\n\nThe session summary mentions that the context server has 18790 tokens of context protection, a Router reverse proxy on 3102, and the v7.0 task-orchestrator with 15 modules, auto_improve with 6 modules, and an intent_detector. So the LLM integration seems to be spread across these components rather than being a single system.\n\nLooking at what was actually completed, the classifier and scorer are running, the auto-score-classify hook is enabled, and context.json is being written during session startup. But the LLM Wiki system hasn't been built out yet, and there's no context protection mechanism in place. The user might be asking about the LLM capabilities themselves—whether there's an LLM layer that actually generates responses, or if the context server (3106) is properly integrated with the classification and scoring systems to handle context windows and prevent overflow. The context server is actually running at 3106, but there's no context window management system in place. I should be direct about what's missing rather than presenting an incomplete picture.","thinkingSignature":"87807cecef9062df8ed2a45786e93b93c3cfbaaf6596ac15b758011aaddfac82"},{"type":"text","text":"没有。LLM 层还是碎片状态。\n\n---\n\n**当前 LLM 相关组件**\n\n| 组件 | 端口 | 状态 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| v8 Router | 3102 | ✅ 运行中 | 反向代理到 LLM |\n| v8_scorer | 3103 | ✅ 运行中 | 复杂度评分 |\n| v8_classifier | 3104 | ✅ 运行中 | 意图分类 |\n| scene-classifier | 3105 | ✅ 运行中 | 场景分类（废弃？） |\n| Context API | 3106 | ✅ 运行中 | 消息队列 |\n| LLM Wiki | — | ❌ 未启动 | docs/ 空 |\n| Context 预算管理 | — | ❌ 没有 | 长 session 会溢出 |\n\n---\n\n**真正缺失的 LLM 层能力**\n\n```\n1. Context 预算管理 — session 变长后没有 token 控制\n2. LLM Wiki Query — 什么时候走 wiki 检索而不是直接 LLM？\n3. Session 摘要 — 长 session 中期压缩，提取关键信息\n4. LLM 自反思 — self-improving 技能有没有真正闭环？\n```\n\n---\n\n**LLM Wiki 里的 LLM 是用来做什么的**\n\n```\nIngest：LLM 读 docs/ 新文档 → 提取关键信息 → 更新 entities/\nQuery：  LLM 读 entities/ → 合成回答\nLint：   LLM 检查 entities/ 质量\n```\n\n这部分完全没有开始，docs/ 是空的。\n\n---\n\n**你现在想要的是哪个？**\n\n1. Context 预算管理（防止 session 溢出）\n2. LLM Wiki Ingest/Query/Lint 完整流程\n3. Session 摘要压缩\n4. 全部都要\n\n哪个优先级最高？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":785,"cacheRead":92874,"cacheWrite":1,"totalTokens":93714,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0009419999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00557244,"cacheWrite":3.75e-7,"total":0.006531015}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776017364446,"responseId":"062b12d3cdeb7737a4337c270fc0699e"}}
