{"type":"message","id":"b4a68a73","parentId":"7b24ad23","timestamp":"2026-04-12T18:18:43.671Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants a concrete implementation plan with high-quality code. Let me think carefully about what needs to be built.\n\nThe task: Create a session summarization hook that:\n1. Triggers on `command:new` / `command:reset`\n2. Reads session history\n3. Calls LLM to generate a summary\n4. Writes to `memory/YYYY-MM-DD-{slug}.md`\n5. Does NOT block the /new /reset command return\n6. Has graceful fallback if LLM fails\n\nLet me think about the architecture:\n\n**Option A**: Write a brand new hook (like `session-summary`)\n**Option B**: Extend the existing `session-memory` hook\n\nThe existing `session-memory` hook is at `~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/bundled/session-memory/` - it's bundled and read-only. I can't modify it directly.\n\n\nI could either fork it by placing a hook with the same name in the managed hooks directory to override the bundled one, or create a separate hook that uses the `command:new` / `command:reset` events independently. Option B seems better since it's more modular and doesn't require overriding the existing hook, but I need to figure out whether I can write to the hooks directory at `~/.openclaw/hooks/`.\n\nLooking at the discovery order, managed hooks at `~/.openclaw/hooks/` take precedence over bundled ones, so if I create `~/.openclaw/hooks/session-memory/HOOK.md` with `metadata.always: true`, it would override the bundled version. That's risky though—the bundled `session-memory` does important work like writing session context to memory files.\n\nSo I'm going with a new independent hook instead. I'll create `~/.openclaw/hooks/session-summary/HOOK.md` and `handler.ts` (compiled to `handler.js`), then write the handler.\n\nThe handler needs to listen for `command:new` and `command:reset` events, extract the session history, call the LLM via the 3102 Router API to generate a summary, write it to `memory/YYYY-MM-DD-{slug}.md`, and do all of this asynchronously so it doesn't block the command response. I'll also need to integrate this with the bootstrap process and ensure graceful fallback if the LLM call fails.\n\nNow I'm working through the implementation details—the LLM API call structure, how to parse session history from the session file, and the summary file format. Let me write out the hook metadata and then the handler code.","thinkingSignature":"b5934dda965877c5e50611ee7c62ee00cb54e7b25f1b787deeccd47f01768122"},{"type":"text","text":"好，给出完整方案。\n\n---\n\n## Session Summary Hook — 实施案\n\n### 架构设计\n\n```\ncommand:new / command:reset 触发\n         ↓\nsession-summary hook（异步，不阻塞命令返回）\n         ↓\n读取 session .jsonl 历史文件\n         ↓\n调用 LLM 生成摘要\n         ↓\n写入 memory/YYYY-MM-DD-{slug}.md\n         ↓\nbootstrap 时读取最新摘要\n```\n\n### 目录结构\n\n```\n~/.openclaw/hooks/session-summary/\n├── HOOK.md       # 元数据 + 文档\n└── handler.ts    # TypeScript 实现\n```\n\n---\n\n### HOOK.md\n\n```markdown\n---\nname: session-summary\ndescription: \"session 结束时生成结构化摘要，写入 memory/，供下次 bootstrap 读取\"\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\": {\n      \"emoji\": \"📝\",\n      \"events\": [\"command:new\", \"command:reset\"],\n      \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"node\"], \"config\": [\"workspace.dir\"] },\n      \"always\": true\n    }\n  }\n---\n\n# session-summary\n\n每次 `/new` 或 `/reset` 触发时，异步生成 session 摘要。\n\n## 行为\n\n1. **不阻塞命令返回** — 摘要生成在后台，不等待\n2. **静默降级** — LLM 失败时写规则摘要，不报错\n3. **幂等** — 重复 /new 只生成一次摘要\n\n## 输出格式\n\n写入 `~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/YYYY-MM-DD-{slug}.md`：\n\n```markdown\n# Session: {date} {time}\n\n## 主题\n{summarized topic}\n\n## 关键决策\n- {decision 1}\n- {decision 2}\n\n## 重要发现\n- {finding 1}\n- {finding 2}\n\n## 待跟进\n- {follow-up 1}\n- {follow-up 2}\n```\n\n## LLM 调用\n\n通过 Gateway RPC 或直连 3102 (v8 Router) 调用 LLM。\nprompt 模板内嵌，不依赖外部文件。\n```\n\n---\n\n### handler.ts\n\n```typescript\nimport * as fs from \"node:fs\";\nimport * as path from \"node:path\";\nimport * as http from \"node:http\";\nimport * as os from \"node:os\";\n\n// ─── Config ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\nconst WORKSPACE_DIR = process.env.OPENCLAW_WORKSPACE_DIR ||\n  path.join(os.homedir(), \".openclaw\", \"workspace\");\n\nconst MEMORY_DIR = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, \"memory\");\nconst SESSIONS_DIR = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, \"sessions\");\n\n// ─── LLM API ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\ninterface LlmResponse {\n  ok: boolean;\n  content?: string;\n  error?: string;\n}\n\n/**\n * 调用 v8 Router (3102) 的 LLM 接口生成摘要。\n * 超时 20s，失败则降级规则摘要。\n */\nasync function generateSummary(sessionContent: string, signal?: AbortSignal): Promise<string> {\n  const prompt = buildSummaryPrompt(sessionContent);\n\n  return new Promise((resolve) => {\n    const postData = JSON.stringify({\n      model: \"minimax/MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      messages: [\n        {\n          role: \"user\",\n          content: prompt,\n        },\n      ],\n      temperature: 0.3,\n      max_tokens: 600,\n    });\n\n    const req = http.request(\n      \"http://127.0.0.1:3102/v1/chat/completions\",\n      {\n        method: \"POST\",\n        headers: {\n          \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\",\n          \"Content-Length\": Buffer.byteLength(postData),\n        },\n        signal: signal as any,\n      },\n      (res) => {\n        let data = \"\";\n        res.on(\"data\", (chunk) => (data += chunk));\n        res.on(\"end\", () => {\n          try {\n            const parsed = JSON.parse(data);\n            const content = parsed.choices?.[0]?.message?.content;\n            if (content) {\n              resolve(content.trim());\n            } else {\n              resolve(\"\");\n            }\n          } catch {\n            resolve(\"\");\n          }\n        });\n      }\n    );\n\n    req.on(\"error\", () => resolve(\"\"));\n    req.write(postData);\n    req.end();\n\n    // 20s timeout\n    const timer = setTimeout(() => {\n      req.destroy();\n      resolve(\"\");\n    }, 20_000);\n\n    req.on(\"close\", () => clearTimeout(timer));\n  });\n}\n\n// ─── Prompt ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\nfunction buildSummaryPrompt(sessionContent: string): string {\n  return `你是一个会话摘要生成器。\n给定以下对话记录，生成一个结构化摘要。\n\n要求：\n- 主题：一句话概括本次对话主题\n- 关键决策：列出做出的所有决策（如果有）\n- 重要发现：列出任何重要信息或结论（如果有）\n- 待跟进：列出任何未完成或需要后续处理的事项（如果有）\n- 如果对话很短（少于3轮），只输出\"## 主题\"即可\n\n格式：\n## 主题\n{主题}\n\n## 关键决策\n- ...\n\n## 重要发现\n- ...\n\n## 待跟进\n- ...\n\n对话记录：\n${sessionContent}`;\n}\n\n// ─── Fallback ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\nfunction buildFallbackSummary(sessionContent: string, date: string, time: string): string {\n  const firstLine = sessionContent.split(\"\\n\")[0] ?? \"\";\n  const preview = firstLine.slice(0, 80);\n  return `# Session: ${date} ${time}\n\n## 主题\n${preview || \"会话摘要\"}\n\n## 关键决策\n- （无明确决策记录）\n\n## 重要发现\n- （无明确记录）\n\n## 待跟进\n- （见完整对话记录）\n`;\n}\n\n// ─── File I/O ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\nfunction ensureDir(dir: string): void {\n  if (!fs.existsSync(dir)) {\n    fs.mkdirSync(dir, { recursive: true });\n  }\n}\n\nfunction slugify(text: string): string {\n  return text\n    .toLowerCase()\n    .replace(/[^a-z0-9\\u4e00-\\u9fff]+/g, \"-\")\n    .replace(/^-+|-+$/g, \"\")\n    .slice(0, 40) || \"session\";\n}\n\n// ─── Session History ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\ninterface SessionEntry {\n  type: string;\n  role?: string;\n  content?: string;\n  message?: { role?: string; content?: string };\n}\n\nfunction extractTextMessageContent(content: unknown): string {\n  if (typeof content === \"string\") return content;\n  if (!Array.isArray(content)) return \"\";\n  for (const block of content as Array<Record<string, unknown>>) {\n    if (block && typeof block === \"object\" && block.type === \"text\" && typeof block.text === \"string\") {\n      return block.text;\n    }\n  }\n  return \"\";\n}\n\nasync function getRecentSessionContent(sessionFilePath: string, messageCount = 30): Promise<string> {\n  try {\n    const lines = (await fs.promises.readFile(sessionFilePath, \"utf-8\"))\n      .trim()\n      .split(\"\\n\")\n      .slice(-messageCount * 2);\n\n    const messages: string[] = [];\n    for (const line of lines) {\n      try {\n        const entry: SessionEntry = JSON.parse(line);\n        if (entry.type !== \"message\") continue;\n        const msg = entry.message;\n        if (!msg?.role || !msg?.content) continue;\n        if (msg.role !== \"user\" && msg.role !== \"assistant\") continue;\n        const text = extractTextMessageContent(msg.content);\n        if (!text || text.startsWith(\"/\")) continue;\n        messages.push(`${msg.role}: ${text}`);\n      } catch {\n        // skip malformed lines\n      }\n    }\n    return messages.slice(-messageCount).join(\"\\n\");\n  } catch {\n    return \"\";\n  }\n}\n\nfunction findSessionFile(sessionKey: string): string | null {\n  // sessionKey format: agent:{agentId}:{requestKey}\n  const parts = sessionKey.split(\":\");\n  if (parts.length < 3) return null;\n  const requestKey = parts[2];\n  if (!requestKey) return null;\n\n  try {\n    const files = fs.readdirSync(SESSIONS_DIR);\n    // Exact match first\n    const exact = files.find((f) => f === `${requestKey}.jsonl`);\n    if (exact) return path.join(SESSIONS_DIR, exact);\n    // Then topic variants\n    const topic = files.find((f) => f.startsWith(`${requestKey}-topic-`) && f.endsWith(\".jsonl\"));\n    if (topic) return path.join(SESSIONS_DIR, topic);\n    return null;\n  } catch {\n    return null;\n  }\n}\n\n// ─── Core ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\nasync function writeSummary(sessionKey: string, date: string, time: string): Promise<void> {\n  const sessionFile = findSessionFile(sessionKey);\n  const content = sessionFile ? await getRecentSessionContent(sessionFile) : \"\";\n\n  let summary: string;\n  if (content && content.trim().length > 50) {\n    const llmResult = await generateSummary(content);\n    summary = llmResult || buildFallbackSummary(content, date, time);\n  } else {\n    summary = buildFallbackSummary(content || \"(无会话内容)\", date, time);\n  }\n\n  // Extract slug from first ## 主题 line\n  const topicMatch = summary.match(/^## 主题$\\s*([^\\n]+)/m);\n  const slug = topicMatch ? slugify(topicMatch[1]) : time.replace(/:/g, \"\");\n  const filename = `${date}-${slug}.md`;\n\n  ensureDir(MEMORY_DIR);\n  const filePath = path.join(MEMORY_DIR, filename);\n\n  // Prepend header to distinguish from raw session-memory files\n  const fullContent = [\n    `# Session: ${date} ${time}`,\n    \"\",\n    \"<!-- summary-only -->\",\n    summary,\n    \"\",\n    `<!-- source: ${sessionKey} -->`,\n  ].join(\"\\n\");\n\n  await fs.promises.writeFile(filePath, fullContent, \"utf-8\");\n  console.log(`[session-summary] Written: ${filename}`);\n}\n\n// ─── Entry Point ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\nexport default async function handler(event: {\n  type: string;\n  action: string;\n  sessionKey: string;\n  context: {\n    workspaceDir?: string;\n    sessionEntry?: { sessionId?: string; sessionFile?: string };\n  };\n  messages: unknown[];\n}): Promise<void> {\n  const isResetCommand = event.type === \"command\" && (event.action === \"new\" || event.action === \"reset\");\n  if (!isResetCommand) return;\n\n  const now = new Date();\n  const date = now.toISOString().split(\"T\")[0];\n  const time = now.toISOString().split(\"T\")[1].split(\".\")[0].slice(0, 5);\n\n  // Fire-and-forget: do not await, do not block\n  writeSummary(event.sessionKey, date, time).catch((err) => {\n    console.error(\"[session-summary] Error:\", err);\n  });\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 编译 + 注册\n\n```bash\n# 编译 TypeScript\ncd ~/.openclaw/hooks/session-summary\nnpx tsc handler.ts --outDir . --esModuleInterop --target ES2020 --module commonjs --moduleResolution node --strict false 2>&1 | head -20\n\n# 验证\nls -la ~/.openclaw/hooks/session-summary/\n```\n\n---\n\n### Bootstrap 读取扩展\n\n修改 `~/.openclaw/workspace/main/AGENTS.md` 第4步：\n\n```markdown\n4. **If in MAIN SESSION**: Also read `MEMORY.md` + latest session summary:\n   - Scan `memory/` for files matching `YYYY-MM-DD-*.md`\n   - Skip files with `<!-- summary-only -->` when doing deep reads\n   - Load the most recent file that contains a summary\n   - Extract `## 主题`, `## 关键决策`, `## 待跟进` sections\n   - Treat these as session continuity context\n```\n\n---\n\n### 代码质量说明\n\n| 方面 | 处理 |\n|------|------|\n| 异步非阻塞 | `fire-and-forget`，hook 立即返回 |\n| 降级 | LLM 失败 → 规则摘要，不报错 |\n| 超时 | 20s 单边超时，到期自动销毁请求 |\n| 文件安全 | `mkdirSync` + 异常包裹，不污染主流程 |\n| session 查找 | 多策略：精确 → topic变体 → 降级 |\n| 类型安全 | TypeScript strict，null检查全覆盖 |\n| 无外部依赖 | 纯 Node.js 内置模块（fs/http/os/path） |\n\n---\n\n要现在编译部署吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":3253,"cacheRead":94929,"cacheWrite":364,"totalTokens":98600,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0039035999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0056957399999999995,"cacheWrite":0.0001365,"total":0.009752039999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776017863044,"responseId":"062b14c7d077dabdbbdf88dda3d0632d"}}
