{"type":"message","id":"1aced8b2","parentId":"0d5096fc","timestamp":"2026-04-12T18:20:20.857Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_qbv4vzmzuv1m_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/**\n * Context Hook for OpenClaw\n * \n * 监听消息事件，自动调用保护层context模块\n * \n * 支持的事件:\n * - message:receive: 用户发送消息\n * - message:send: AI 发送消息\n * - agent:response: Agent 回复\n */\n\nconst handler = async (event) => {\n  try {\n    // 检查是否有全局上下文接口\n    if (!global.openclaw || !global.openclaw.addContextMessage) {\n      // 尝试加载保护层\n      try {\n        const protection = await import(process.env.HOME + '/.openclaw/protection/index.js');\n        await protection.default.init();\n      } catch (e) {\n        console.log('[ContextHook] 保护层未加载，跳过');\n        return;\n      }\n    }\n\n    // 处理用户消息\n    if (event.type === 'message' || event.type === 'message:receive') {\n      const content = event.message?.content || event.content || '';\n      if (content) {\n        global.openclaw?.addContextMessage('user', content, event.taskId);"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":50,"aggregated":"/**\n * Context Hook for OpenClaw\n * \n * 监听消息事件，自动调用保护层context模块\n * \n * 支持的事件:\n * - message:receive: 用户发送消息\n * - message:send: AI 发送消息\n * - agent:response: Agent 回复\n */\n\nconst handler = async (event) => {\n  try {\n    // 检查是否有全局上下文接口\n    if (!global.openclaw || !global.openclaw.addContextMessage) {\n      // 尝试加载保护层\n      try {\n        const protection = await import(process.env.HOME + '/.openclaw/protection/index.js');\n        await protection.default.init();\n      } catch (e) {\n        console.log('[ContextHook] 保护层未加载，跳过');\n        return;\n      }\n    }\n\n    // 处理用户消息\n    if (event.type === 'message' || event.type === 'message:receive') {\n      const content = event.message?.content || event.content || '';\n      if (content) {\n        global.openclaw?.addContextMessage('user', content, event.taskId);","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776018020847}}
{"type":"message","id":"3ac2aa4e","parentId":"1aced8b2","timestamp":"2026-04-12T18:20:20.874Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_qbv4vzmzuv1m_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/bin/bash\n# OpenClaw Context Hook - HTTP 版本\n# 将消息发送到保护层的 HTTP 服务\n\nMESSAGE=\"${OPENCLAW_MESSAGE:-}\"\nUSER=\"${OPENCLAW_SENDER:-unknown}\"\nCHANNEL=\"${OPENCLAW_CHANNEL:-unknown}\"\nSERVER_URL=\"http://127.0.0.1:18790\"\n\nif [ -n \"$MESSAGE\" ]; then\n  # 发送到 HTTP 服务\n  curl -s -X POST \"${SERVER_URL}/api/context/add\" \\\n    -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n    -d \"{\\\"role\\\":\\\"user\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"$(echo \"$MESSAGE\" | jq -Rs .)\\\",\\\"user\\\":\\\"$USER\\\",\\\"channel\\\":\\\"$CHANNEL\\\"}\" \\\n    > /dev/null 2>&1 || true\nfi"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":68,"aggregated":"#!/bin/bash\n# OpenClaw Context Hook - HTTP 版本\n# 将消息发送到保护层的 HTTP 服务\n\nMESSAGE=\"${OPENCLAW_MESSAGE:-}\"\nUSER=\"${OPENCLAW_SENDER:-unknown}\"\nCHANNEL=\"${OPENCLAW_CHANNEL:-unknown}\"\nSERVER_URL=\"http://127.0.0.1:18790\"\n\nif [ -n \"$MESSAGE\" ]; then\n  # 发送到 HTTP 服务\n  curl -s -X POST \"${SERVER_URL}/api/context/add\" \\\n    -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n    -d \"{\\\"role\\\":\\\"user\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"$(echo \"$MESSAGE\" | jq -Rs .)\\\",\\\"user\\\":\\\"$USER\\\",\\\"channel\\\":\\\"$CHANNEL\\\"}\" \\\n    > /dev/null 2>&1 || true\nfi","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776018020865}}
{"type":"message","id":"70e4c862","parentId":"3ac2aa4e","timestamp":"2026-04-12T18:20:25.426Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see - the hooks directory has both `.js` (ESM) and `.sh` files. Let me check the `on-command-error.sh` and also understand the full picture.\n\nNow let me understand: the auto-score-classify hook I wrote earlier uses TypeScript (handler.ts) + compiled JavaScript (handler.js). Let me check how it's actually being executed.\n\nLet me look at the actual handler.js that gets used.","thinkingSignature":"885351962645ed0fbff0edc9ca39ba70ad4d00973f3bc1b2c68a69a533728312"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_enayotx3e0h9_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"head -20 ~/.openclaw/hooks/auto-score-classify/handler.js 2>/dev/null","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":81506,"output":144,"cacheRead":17776,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99426,"cost":{"input":0.0244518,"output":0.0001728,"cacheRead":0.0010665599999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02569116}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776018020879,"responseId":"062b156494f9c4c2b2ba690eaa568c24"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6e37f2f6","parentId":"70e4c862","timestamp":"2026-04-12T18:20:25.520Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_enayotx3e0h9_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// auto-score-classify hook\n// Concurrent classification (3104) + scoring (3103) on every inbound message\n\nimport fs from \"node:fs\";\nimport path from \"node:path\";\nimport http from \"node:http\";\n\nasync function fetchJSON(url, body, timeoutMs = 3000) {\n  return new Promise((resolve) => {\n    const postData = JSON.stringify(body);\n    const req = http.request(\n      url,\n      {\n        method: \"POST\",\n        headers: { \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\", \"Content-Length\": Buffer.byteLength(postData) },\n      },\n      (res) => {\n        let data = \"\";\n        res.on(\"data\", (chunk) => (data += chunk));\n        res.on(\"end\", () => {"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":57,"aggregated":"// auto-score-classify hook\n// Concurrent classification (3104) + scoring (3103) on every inbound message\n\nimport fs from \"node:fs\";\nimport path from \"node:path\";\nimport http from \"node:http\";\n\nasync function fetchJSON(url, body, timeoutMs = 3000) {\n  return new Promise((resolve) => {\n    const postData = JSON.stringify(body);\n    const req = http.request(\n      url,\n      {\n        method: \"POST\",\n        headers: { \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\", \"Content-Length\": Buffer.byteLength(postData) },\n      },\n      (res) => {\n        let data = \"\";\n        res.on(\"data\", (chunk) => (data += chunk));\n        res.on(\"end\", () => {","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776018025511}}
{"type":"message","id":"b97dfa1e","parentId":"6e37f2f6","timestamp":"2026-04-12T18:20:34.390Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good - the auto-score-classify/handler.js uses ESM import syntax. This means OpenClaw's hook runner supports ESM. The handler.js is directly written in ESM format, not compiled from TypeScript.\n\nSo for the session-summary hook, I can either:\n1. Write directly as ESM JavaScript (simpler)\n2. Write as TypeScript and compile\n\nSince I'm writing code quality要高, let me think about which approach is better.\n\nActually, since the user wants code quality to be high, TypeScript with strict mode is better. But I need to compile it first. Let me check if there's a tsc available.","thinkingSignature":"da47086fbeca7d9569d66c9df01d8a4fa1a5912fc47adbeb608358cbd1b96bd6"},{"type":"text","text":"**Step 1 结论**：现有 hook 有两种格式：\n\n| 格式 | 示例 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 目录 + `handler.js` | `auto-score-classify/` | ESM 模块，OpenClaw 直接加载 |\n| 单文件 `.js` | `context-hook.js` | CommonJS/ESM 混合 |\n\n`auto-score-classify` 的 `handler.js` 是 ESM，直接用 `import`。\n\n---\n\n**Step 2：确认 TypeScript 编译环境**\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hzqs70t4a1xd_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"which tsc 2>/dev/null || which npx 2>/dev/null || echo \"no tsc\"","timeout":5}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hzqs70t4a1xd_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node --input-type=module --eval \"import fs from 'node:fs'; console.log('ESM ok')\" 2>/dev/null","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":81827,"output":355,"cacheRead":17776,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99958,"cost":{"input":0.0245481,"output":0.000426,"cacheRead":0.0010665599999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02604066}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776018025523,"responseId":"062b1569033c84cc874ef858a1490f0b"}}
