{"type":"message","id":"cefcafb4","parentId":"625b7082","timestamp":"2026-04-12T18:24:35.750Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the module imports correctly and has a default export function. The hook is ready.Now let me do a final verification summary for the user.","thinkingSignature":"2577e07e78645a715387e1713f10fe1e910d7129186ab76a2b7b29ceb319bf3c"},{"type":"text","text":"**全部完成 ✅**\n\n---\n\n**实施总结**\n\n| 步骤 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| HOOK.md 元数据 | ✅ |\n| handler.js (ESM, 9509字节) | ✅ |\n| 语法验证 | ✅ |\n| OpenClaw 发现 (7/7 ready) | ✅ |\n| systemd hook 启用 | ✅ |\n| AGENTS.md bootstrap 读摘要 | ✅ |\n\n---\n\n**handler.js 代码质量说明**\n\n| 方面 | 实现 |\n|------|------|\n| 异步非阻塞 | `fire-and-forget`，立即返回 |\n| 降级 | LLM 失败 → 规则摘要，不报错 |\n| 超时保护 | 20s 单边超时 + `req.destroy()` |\n| session 查找 | previousSessionEntry → sessionEntry → 文件搜索，三层降级 |\n| 文件安全 | `mkdirSync` + 异常捕获，不污染主流程 |\n| 类型安全 | JSDoc `@param` / `@returns` 标注 |\n| 无外部依赖 | 纯 Node.js 内置模块 |\n\n---\n\n**验证方式**：发 `/new` 或 `/reset` 命令，hook 触发后检查 `memory/` 目录是否有新的摘要文件生成。\n\n需要我测试一下吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":93780,"output":289,"cacheRead":17776,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111845,"cost":{"input":0.028134,"output":0.00034679999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0010665599999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02954736}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776018268021,"responseId":"062b165b826248a1ee5401c4d858edb5"}}
