{"type":"message","id":"34325c9f","parentId":"ddeaad41","timestamp":"2026-04-12T18:26:20.272Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System (untrusted): [2026-04-13 02:23:37 GMT+8] Exec completed (ember-me, code 0) :: │ plugin:mem │ │ ✓ ready │ 🎯 auto-score- │ 每条消息自动调用 v8_classifier(3104) 和 v8_scorer(3103)，结果写入 │ openclaw- │ │ ✓ ready │ 📝 session- │ session 结束时（/new 或 /reset）生成结构化摘要，写入 memory…\nSystem (untrusted): [2026-04-13 02:23:55 GMT+8] Exec completed (kind-bis, code 0) :: │ ├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯ [plugins] feishu_doc: Registered feishu_doc, feishu_app_scopes [plugins] feishu_chat: Registered feis…\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Mon 2026-04-13 02:26 GMT+8] 犀利、严格的进行评审、检查"}],"timestamp":1776018380261}}
