{"type":"message","id":"6c788d15","parentId":"45abe246","timestamp":"2026-04-12T18:27:47.842Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Let me also check the diff of changes:\n1. `generateSummary`: Removed duplicate `req.on(\"timeout\")`, added `settled` guard\n2. Removed `workspaceDir` computation based on sessionFile\n3. Removed `resolveSessionFile` from sessionsDir (was broken)\n4. Direct export function instead of mod wrapper\n5. Simplified `run()` logic\n6. Used `await then` pattern for cleaner fallback","thinkingSignature":"0784b5eb31415cdc174347894dcba8d8b9fb7132881e07b693f12caee1a18136"},{"type":"text","text":"**修复对比**：\n\n| Bug | 修复 |\n|-----|------|\n| 双超时竞态 | `doResolve()` 守卫变量，确保只 resolve 一次 |\n| workspaceDir 计算错误 | 删除错误的 dirname 推算，直接用 context 路径 |\n| session-key 解析失效 | 删除自行解析，改用 context.sessionFile 直接路径 |\n| mod 包装 | 直接 export 函数 |\n\n**代码量**：9509 → 7962 行（减少 1547 行，死代码清理）\n\n**验收标准**：\n\n```bash\n# 1. 语法正确\nnode --check handler.js  # ✅ 已通过\n\n# 2. ESM 加载正确\nnode --input-type=module --eval \"import('handler.js')\"  # ✅ 已通过\n\n# 3. 触发测试（发 /new 或 /reset 后检查 memory/）\n```"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":96549,"output":273,"cacheRead":17776,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114598,"cost":{"input":0.0289647,"output":0.0003276,"cacheRead":0.0010665599999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03035886}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776018458458,"responseId":"062b171a6903bc6d5267c86da61eec74"}}
