{"type":"message","id":"863cd5f5","parentId":"5624101e","timestamp":"2026-04-12T18:33:15.153Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The most recent file is `2026-04-12.md` at 23:12. The hook was deployed and enabled, but it only triggers on `/new` or `/reset`. Since no one has issued those commands after the restart, no new summary files have been generated yet. That's expected.\n\nThe hook is working - it's just waiting for the trigger.","thinkingSignature":"2d9e0dd1e76a6219f2182c58cf51acb398ab037ed20b26c56d16f22ad83453b5"},{"type":"text","text":"**状态正常**：\n\n- Gateway 运行中 ✅\n- Hook 7/7 ready ✅\n- `session-summary` 启用 ✅\n\nmemory/ 里最新文件是 `2026-04-12 23:12`，是重启前的记录。Hook 在等待 `/new` 或 `/reset` 触发，没有新摘要是正常的（还没有人发过这两个命令）。\n\n---\n\n**验证方式**：发 `/new` 或 `/reset`，然后检查 `memory/` 是否有新的 `<!-- summary-only -->` 文件生成。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":98328,"output":185,"cacheRead":17846,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":116359,"cost":{"input":0.029498399999999998,"output":0.000222,"cacheRead":0.0010707599999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.030791159999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776018789896,"responseId":"062b1865c6cd5f5050ab8fe172989c69"}}
