{"type":"message","id":"e5fec6b7","parentId":"5167a390","timestamp":"2026-04-12T18:35:42.114Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"3100 is listening but has no associated process. This is a zombie socket. The process that opened it has exited but the kernel hasn't released the port.\n\nFor 3105 - let me check if there's supposed to be a service running there.\n\nLet me now compile the framework review findings:\n\n**Port Status:**\n\n| Port | Service | Status |\n|------|---------|--------|\n| 3100 | Unknown | ⚠️ ZOMBIE - no owning process |\n| 3101 | Context API (express) | ✅ Running |\n| 3102 | OpenClaw Gateway | ✅ Running |\n| 3103 | v8_scorer | ✅ Running |\n\n\n| 3104 | Scene Classifier (Flask) | ✅ Running |\n| 3105 | scene-classifier | ❌ DOWN |\n| 3106 | openclaw-listener (Feishu) | ✅ Running |\n\nThe framework review is revealing some critical gaps. I never actually verified the context.json read path in bootstrap even though I added it to AGENTS.md, and there's no confirmation the hook is being called at the right lifecycle stage. The docs directory for LLM Wiki is empty so there's nothing to process, the session summary file doesn't integrate with entities for automatic updates, and I'm realizing the scoring and classification hooks are only being called on preprocessed messages—not at actual message boundaries. I need to dig deeper into these architectural issues.","thinkingSignature":"f14e01f8f52fed34398edaf376074a8c7bdf2aa9eb5c7d4ef43dfc390e977cde"},{"type":"text","text":"**第一轮发现：端口状态**\n\n| 端口 | 服务 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 3100 | 未知 | ⚠️ **僵尸端口** — 无持有进程 |\n| 3101 | Context API (express) | ✅ |\n| 3102 | OpenClaw Gateway | ✅ |\n| 3103 | v8_scorer | ✅ |\n| 3104 | Scene Classifier (Flask) | ✅ |\n| 3105 | scene-classifier | ❌ **DOWN** |\n| 3106 | openclaw-listener (Feishu) | ✅ |\n\n---\n\n**第二轮：Hook 与 Bootstrap 的关键问题**\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4gwmvzjyqod7_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"context.json\\|session context\\|session.*summary\" ~/.openclaw/workspace/main/AGENTS.md | head -10","timeout":5}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4gwmvzjyqod7_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/hooks/auto-score-classify/handler.js | grep -n \"event.type\\|event.action\\|message\" | head -15","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":101616,"output":546,"cacheRead":17846,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":120008,"cost":{"input":0.0304848,"output":0.0006552,"cacheRead":0.0010707599999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03221076}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776018928033,"responseId":"062b18efade1bb02a42cf6a625aaf6e6"}}
{"type":"message","id":"7cb86050","parentId":"e5fec6b7","timestamp":"2026-04-12T18:35:42.233Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_4gwmvzjyqod7_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"17:5. Read session context: look for `~/.openclaw/sessions/main@*/context.json` (most recent modified if multiple exist). If found, treat its `classification` and `scoring` fields as the current message's pre-analysis — factor them into your response strategy.\n18:6. Read the most recent session summary: scan `memory/` for files with `<!-- summary-only -->`, pick the latest by filename date, extract `## 主题`, `## 关键决策`, `## 待跟进` sections. This is the continuity from the previous session — treat it as context, not as a task list to execute."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":56,"aggregated":"17:5. Read session context: look for `~/.openclaw/sessions/main@*/context.json` (most recent modified if multiple exist). If found, treat its `classification` and `scoring` fields as the current message's pre-analysis — factor them into your response strategy.\n18:6. Read the most recent session summary: scan `memory/` for files with `<!-- summary-only -->`, pick the latest by filename date, extract `## 主题`, `## 关键决策`, `## 待跟进` sections. This is the continuity from the previous session — treat it as context, not as a task list to execute.","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776018942221}}
