{"type":"message","id":"5d315615","parentId":"2241f12d","timestamp":"2026-04-12T18:36:38.128Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting. There are two AGENTS.md files:\n- `~/.openclaw/workspace/AGENTS.md` — workspace root\n- `~/.openclaw/workspace/main/AGENTS.md` — main workspace subdirectory\n\nThe root AGENTS.md says \"OpenClaw Workspace\" and has preprocessing rules. The main AGENTS.md says \"This folder is home.\" and has the Session Startup rules including reading SOUL.md, USER.md, memory/, MEMORY.md, context.json, and session summary.\n\nWhich one is actually used? The OpenClaw workspace config must specify which workspace is \"main\". Let me check.","thinkingSignature":"f070e9d8dfe3c75becdfef71dc42611935c31988a166f795e95605ad63d667e8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bnf67sqjuk2f_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json 2>/dev/null | python3 -m json.tool 2>/dev/null | grep -A5 \"workspace\\|dir\\|agent\"","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":104501,"output":196,"cacheRead":17846,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122543,"cost":{"input":0.0313503,"output":0.0002352,"cacheRead":0.0010707599999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03265625999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776018993077,"responseId":"062b193042c316f19d7d4a60764df746"}}
{"type":"message","id":"508666ec","parentId":"5d315615","timestamp":"2026-04-12T18:36:38.226Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_bnf67sqjuk2f_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"agents\": {\n        \"list\": [\n            {\n                \"id\": \"fast_agent\",\n                \"name\": \"Fast Agent\",\n                \"workspace\": \"/home/ai/.openclaw/agents/fast\"\n            },\n            {\n                \"id\": \"deep_agent\",\n                \"name\": \"Deep Agent\",\n                \"workspace\": \"/home/ai/.openclaw/agents/deep\"\n            }\n        ],\n        \"defaults\": {\n            \"model\": {\n                \"primary\": \"minimax/MiniMax-M2.7\",\n--\n            \"workspace\": \"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace\",\n            \"compaction\": {\n                \"mode\": \"safeguard\"\n            }\n        }\n    },\n--\n            \"agentId\": \"main\",\n            \"match\": {\n                \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n                \"accountId\": \"default\"\n            }\n        }"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":50,"aggregated":"\"agents\": {\n        \"list\": [\n            {\n                \"id\": \"fast_agent\",\n                \"name\": \"Fast Agent\",\n                \"workspace\": \"/home/ai/.openclaw/agents/fast\"\n            },\n            {\n                \"id\": \"deep_agent\",\n                \"name\": \"Deep Agent\",\n                \"workspace\": \"/home/ai/.openclaw/agents/deep\"\n            }\n        ],\n        \"defaults\": {\n            \"model\": {\n                \"primary\": \"minimax/MiniMax-M2.7\",\n--\n            \"workspace\": \"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace\",\n            \"compaction\": {\n                \"mode\": \"safeguard\"\n            }\n        }\n    },\n--\n            \"agentId\": \"main\",\n            \"match\": {\n                \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n                \"accountId\": \"de