{"type":"message","id":"105a69d3","parentId":"0be40e73","timestamp":"2026-04-12T18:42:48.104Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found it! Session files are stored in `~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/` not in `~/.openclaw/sessions/agent:main:main/`.\n\nAnd the files are named like UUIDs: `122589c7-91b3-43f3-93c5-2d5af138e58c.jsonl`\n\nSo the session file path would be something like:\n`/home/ai/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/122589c7-91b3-43f3-93c5-2d5af138e58c.jsonl`\n\n\nThe `agent:main:main` directory under `~/.openclaw/sessions/` is just for hook context data like `context.json`, not for the actual session history files. My handler was looking in the wrong place. I need to update it to reference `~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/` instead.","thinkingSignature":"ce64c11bb1064fc4f8d88aaec0d8e84c6d66f207c0d6b786257dbda0262be4e6"},{"type":"text","text":"**找到根因**：session 文件在 `~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/`（UUID 格式），不是 `~/.openclaw/sessions/agent:main:main/`。\n\nhandler 的 session 文件路径解析是错的。需要修复：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_q17komauzg84_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/hooks/session-summary/handler.js","offset":42,"limit":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":108805,"output":292,"cacheRead":17846,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126943,"cost":{"input":0.0326415,"output":0.0003504,"cacheRead":0.0010707599999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.034062659999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776019361428,"responseId":"062b1aa111650ca0568fdcf87844aa94"}}
{"type":"message","id":"950c4c37","parentId":"105a69d3","timestamp":"2026-04-12T18:42:48.177Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_q17komauzg84_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":" * @param {HookContext} context\n * @returns {string|null}\n */\nfunction resolveSessionFile(context) {\n  const prev = context?.previousSessionEntry;\n  if (prev?.sessionFile) return prev.sessionFile;\n\n  const curr = context?.sessionEntry;\n  if (curr?.sessionFile) return curr.sessionFile;\n\n  return null;\n}\n\n// ─── Message Extraction ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\n/**\n * @param {unknown} content\n * @returns {string}\n */\nfunction extractTextFromBlocks(content) {\n  if (Array.isArray(content)) {\n    for (const block of content) {\n      if (\n        block &&\n        typeof block === \"object\" &&\n        block.type === \"text\" &&\n        typeof block.text === \"string\"\n      ) {\n        return block.text;\n      }\n\n[252 more lines in file. Use offset=72 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776019368167}}
