{"type":"message","id":"779232ea","parentId":"e527116b","timestamp":"2026-04-12T18:43:20.130Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The content is a list (blocks), not a string. My `extractTextFromBlocks` function handles this case:\n\n```javascript\nconst text =\n  typeof msg.content === \"string\"\n    ? msg.content\n    : extractTextFromBlocks(msg.content);\n```\n\nSo the message extraction should work correctly.\n\nNow let me verify by manually reading one of the session files and running the extract logic:","thinkingSignature":"048e9b993a86950f0b865e82af02b0f6cf336318f959e96257435ea715800c94"},{"type":"text","text":"session 文件格式确认：content 是 blocks 数组（非字符串），handler 的 `extractTextFromBlocks` 已处理这种情况 ✅\n\n---\n\n**现在验证 handler 对真实 session 文件的提取效果**：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5g8a6refixq5_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node --input-type=module --eval \"\nimport fs from 'node:fs';\n\nfunction extractTextFromBlocks(content) {\n  if (Array.isArray(content)) {\n    for (const block of content) {\n      if (block && typeof block === 'object' && block.type === 'text' && typeof block.text === 'string') {\n        return block.text;\n      }\n    }\n  }\n  return '';\n}\n\nasync function extractMessages(filePath, messageCount = 10) {\n  const content = await fs.promises.readFile(filePath, 'utf-8');\n  const lines = content.trim().split('\\n').slice(-messageCount * 2);\n  const messages = [];\n  for (const line of lines) {\n    if (!line.trim()) continue;\n    try {\n      const entry = JSON.parse(line);\n      if (entry.type !== 'message') continue;\n      const msg = entry.message;\n      if (!msg?.role || !msg?.content) continue;\n      if (msg.role !== 'user' && msg.role !== 'assistant') continue;\n      const text = typeof msg.content === 'string' ? msg.content : extractTextFromBlocks(msg.content);\n      if (!text || text.startsWith('/')) continue;\n      messages.push(msg.role + ': ' + text.slice(0, 80));\n    } catch {}\n  }\n  return messages.slice(-messageCount).join('\\n');\n}\n\nconst sessionFile = '/home/ai/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/2d625705-5c75-484e-bcf0-29f5034c6b20.jsonl';\nextractMessages(sessionFile, 6).then(r => {\n  console.log('=== Last 6 messages ===');\n  console.log(r || '(empty)');\n}).catch(e => console.log('Error:', e.message));\n\" 2>/dev/null","timeout":8}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":110507,"output":537,"cacheRead":17846,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":128890,"cost":{"input":0.0331521,"output":0.0006443999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0010707599999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03486726}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776019389054,"responseId":"062b1abc742532e0bdfc99191a3e22d0"}}
