{"type":"message","id":"366eebb1","parentId":"678cae51","timestamp":"2026-04-12T18:45:17.708Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting! `docs/` has 9 files (all Claude-related reports) - these are raw sources for LLM Wiki Ingest. The LLM Wiki has 31 entity pages including `ingest.md`, `lint.md`, `log.md` which means the Ingest/Lint process docs exist in entities/ but the actual cron triggers haven't been configured.\n\nNow let me check what the ingest and lint entities say, and if there are any cron jobs set up.","thinkingSignature":"bcdc0ceb6c169494a444fa2b1a8f41a8ed66bd4d166994ed6e56f837ad8bc0fc"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_sa7lci2awhdq_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/ingest.md 2>/dev/null | head -40","timeout":5}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_sa7lci2awhdq_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/openclaw cron list 2>/dev/null | head -20","timeout":8}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":110734,"output":206,"cacheRead":17846,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":128786,"cost":{"input":0.0332202,"output":0.0002472,"cacheRead":0.0010707599999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03453816}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776019512484,"responseId":"062b1b37752232d8bdee1d8bace753f8"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d00e2422","parentId":"366eebb1","timestamp":"2026-04-12T18:45:17.819Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_sa7lci2awhdq_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\ntitle: Ingest\ntype: entity\nstatus: active\ntags: [ingest, workflow]\n---\n\n# Ingest\n\n> 获取新知识的工作流，根据 LLM Wiki 原文实现\n\n## 原文定义\n\n> \"You drop a new source into the raw collection and tell the LLM to process it.\"\n\n## 完整流程 (6步)\n\n### 1. 准备 Source\n将新文档放入 docs/ 或 raw-sources/\n\n### 2. 分析 Source\nLLM 读取并理解内容\n\n### 3. 提取知识\n识别关键概念、实体、关系\n\n### 4. 更新 Wiki\n影响 10-15 个相关页面：\n- 创建/更新主 entity 页面\n- 更新相关概念页面\n- 添加链接和引用\n\n### 5. 更新 Index\n添加到 memory.md 索引\n\n### 6. 记录 Log\n追加到 log.md 时间线\n\n## 质量标准"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":54,"aggregated":"---\ntitle: Ingest\ntype: entity\nstatus: active\ntags: [ingest, workflow]\n---\n\n# Ingest\n\n> 获取新知识的工作流，根据 LLM Wiki 原文实现\n\n## 原文定义\n\n> \"You drop a new source into the raw collection and tell the LLM to process it.\"\n\n## 完整流程 (6步)\n\n### 1. 准备 Source\n将新文档放入 docs/ 或 raw-sources/\n\n### 2. 分析 Source\nLLM 读取并理解内容\n\n### 3. 提取知识\n识别关键概念、实体、关系\n\n### 4. 更新 Wiki\n影响 10-15 个相关页面：\n- 创建/更新主 entity 页面\n- 更新相关概念页面\n- 添加链接和引用\n\n### 5. 更新 Index\n添加到 memory.md 索引\n\n### 6. 记录 Log\n追加到 log.md 时间线\n\n## 质量标准","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776019517807}}
