{"type":"message","id":"cf83ae15","parentId":"49e68744","timestamp":"2026-04-12T18:45:47.613Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so there are 3 cron jobs:\n1. `memory-maintain` - daily at 3am\n2. `memory-keeper` - daily at 4am  \n3. `Memory Dreaming Promotion` - daily at 3am\n\nNow let me check what the heartbeat is actually doing. Looking at the HEARTBEAT.md, it mentions checking things, but I need to see what's actually in the heartbeat configuration.\n\nLet me now compile the comprehensive gap analysis.","thinkingSignature":"a7ad2ea46c630d6c0257c43c031b825549cf1637e4940b3ce1dde7f7f3dcb178"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vfw1cu0abmz6_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md 2>/dev/null; echo \"---\"; cat ~/.openclaw/workspace/main/HEARTBEAT.md 2>/dev/null | head -20","timeout":5}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vfw1cu0abmz6_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.openclaw/workspace/main/ 2>/dev/null","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":112279,"output":218,"cacheRead":17846,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":130343,"cost":{"input":0.0336837,"output":0.00026159999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0010707599999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.035016059999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776019543233,"responseId":"062b1b5603c3567c2dcc3bb7715fd480"}}
{"type":"message","id":"37e55e09","parentId":"cf83ae15","timestamp":"2026-04-12T18:45:47.718Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_vfw1cu0abmz6_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Heartbeat Configuration\n\n## 心跳规则\n\n### 任务进度上报格式\n```\n[PROGRESS] <percent>% | <step>/<total> | <description>\n```\n\n### 心跳间隔\n- 默认: 30秒\n- 最小: 10秒\n- 最大: 300秒\n\n### 超时处理\n| 情况 | 处理 |\n|------|------|\n| 30秒无输出 | 发送\"仍在运行\"提示 |\n| 60秒无产出 | 警告用户 |\n| 超时前5秒 | 发送即将超时警告 |\n\n### 环境变量\n- `SUBAGENT_MEMORY_LIMIT_MB`: 子代理内存限制 (默认 2048)\n- `PROGRESS_MIN_INTERVAL_MS`: 进度上报最小间隔 (默认 1000)\n\n### 注意事项\n- 长时间任务需定期输出进度\n- 关键里程碑应立即上报\n- 错误信息立即上报，不等待心跳---\n# HEARTBEAT.md Template\n\n```markdown\n# Keep this file empty (or with only comments) to skip heartbeat API calls.\n\n# Add tasks below when you want the agent to check something periodically.\n```"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":49,"aggregated":"# Heartbeat Configuration\n\n## 心跳规则\n\n### 任务进度上报格式\n```\n[PROGRESS] <percent>% | <step>/<total> | <description>\n```\n\n### 心跳间隔\n- 默认: 30秒\n- 最小: 10秒\n- 最大: 300秒\n\n### 超时处理\n| 情况 | 处理 |\n|------|------|\n| 30秒无输出 | 发送\"仍在运行\"提示 |\n| 60秒无产出 | 警告用户 |\n| 超时前5秒 | 发送即将超时警告 |\n\n### 环境变量\n- `SUBAGENT_MEMORY_LIMIT_MB`: 子代理内存限制 (默认 2048)\n- `PROGRESS_MIN_INTERVAL_MS`: 进度上报最小间隔 (默认 1000)\n\n### 注意事项\n- 长时间任务需定期输出进度\n- 关键里程碑应立即上报\n- 错误信息立即上报，不等待心跳---\n# HEARTBEAT.md Template\n\n```markdown\n# Keep this file empty (or with only comments) to skip heartbeat API calls.\n\n# Add tasks below when you want the agent to check something periodically.\n```","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776019547706}}
